\id EXO
\h Potdohbu
\toc1 Potdohbu
\toc2 Potdohbu
\toc3 Potdohbu
\mt3 Mose Lekhabu Nina
\mt1 POTDOHBU
\mt3 Potdohbu sung thu umdan
\ip Pathen'in Israel nampi alhunna ding'u mun akomu pehna Potdohbu ahin akimun ahi. Israel mite kicha pum'a akijot nau le akidel khum nauva kon thusim saotah chuleh ahangsan nau jong akimu in ahi. Pathen'in Israel te asoh chan nauva kon'in ahuhdoh jingin hinlah amaho chu Pathen'a kitah tah in ading jouji pouvin, tahsan nan ana lhasam jiuve tijong akimun ahi. Hijeh chun atahsan nau lhahsam jia kon'in kihilna thei tampi aum'e ti muchet ahi: Mi lhasam hon jong Pathen akimu theiyun, chule Pathen'in amaho lungsetna bukimsel'in angailu jin ahi.
\ip Potdohbu hi nia akihom khen'in ahi. Bung khat apat som le ko chan ahin Israel mite asohchan nauva kon akilha ong nau aseijin, chule Bung somni apat somli chan ahin Dan ajui uva Pathen kin abol diu aseijin ahi. Potdohbu a kon'in bannei chan Pathen thaneina, loupina chule ngaidamna le lungsetna lhingsel'a Anatoh ho akilangin ahi.
\ip Potdohbu hin Pathen le mihemte kah a thusim chedol avetsah in, Pathen ngailu jouse Aman kidangtah in alhunna ding mun alhunsah teiyin angailu in ahi. Ajeh chu Pathen'in Mose angailu in akithopin ahile Mose chu Israel mite chung'a lamkai pipu in ahung pang tan ahi. Pakai, Pathen hi mihemte alhahsam nauva kon'a kivengpha ho chung'a alunglhai jin ahi. Ajeh chu Pathen tailou kinepna ding dang umlou ahi.
\is1 Lekhabu jihpa chule akijih kum
\ip Potdoh bu hi Mose in 1440 BC vel'a anajih ahi.
\c 1
\s1 Israel mite apunnau le kihen ohna
\p 
\v 1 Israel mite (hichu, Jacob chapa te), ama insung mi cheh hin kipuija Egypt gamsung'a apau toh kitollut ho min chu: \x + \xo 1:1 \xt Semtilbu 46:8-27\x*
\v 2 Reuben, simeon, Levi, Judah,
\v 3 Issachar, Zebulun, Benjamin,
\v 4 Dan, Naphtali, Gad chule Asher amaho cheng hi ahiuve.
\v 5 Abonchauvin, Egypt gamsung'a Jacob chilhah chengse chu som sagi alhing'un chule Joseph vang agamsung'a ana um jingsa ahitai.
\v 6 Phat chomkhat jouvin, Joseph le asopi chengse athigam tauvin, hiche khang mite se chu akichai tan ahi.
\v 7 Ahinlah ason achilhah teu, Israel chate chun tu le cha tampi anei tauvin apung lheh jengun, ahung hatdoh cheh cheh un gamsung pumpi ahin lodim tauve. \x + \xo 1:7 \xt Act 7:17\x*
\v 8 Achainan, Egypt gamsunga chun Joseph chung chang thu le anatoh ho hephalou leng thah khat thaneina ahung chang tan ahi. \x + \xo 1:8 \xt Act 7:18\x*
\v 9 Amapa chun amite henga thu aseijin, “Vetem'un, Israel mite hi eiho sang'in apung'un chule eiho sang'in ahat lheh jeng tauve.
\v 10 Amaho hi apunbe louna diuvin, tohgon khat nei tau hite. Achuti louva ahile hung hatdoh untin, chule gal hung um taleh, imelma teu ahin panpi diu eihin dou uva gamsunga kon'a jamdoh ding ahiuve,” ati. \x + \xo 1:10 \xt Act 7:19\x*
\v 11 Hijeh chun Egypt miten Israel chate jouse soh in amangcha tauvin, achung uva tohvaihom mikhanse tah tah ho apansah un, chutobang bolgimna soh natoh a kon'a chu suhnem ding akinem'un, hunam chang'in lengpa thil kholna ding Pithom leh Rameses khopi chu asah sah uvin ahi.
\v 12 Ahinlah Egypt mite'n amaho asuhgim chan'un apunbe uvin akithejal cheh jo tauvin ahi, Egypt mite chu kichat nan aum jo tauvin ahi.
\v 13 Chutah chun Egypt miten Israel mite chu ngailutna beihel'in thohgim hahsa athohsah uvin na atohsah un ahi.
\v 14 Aki manchahna jouse uva gimna alhun sah un, bon ngan achilsah un, leilhang asemsah un, loujaova natoh jouse atohsah un, atoh nalam jouseuva gimbolna achansah tauvin ahi.
\v 15 Chuin Pharaoh, Egypt lengpan Hebrew mi nao dom teni Shiphrah leh Puah henga hiche thupeh hi aneiyin:
\v 16 “Hebrew numei hon nao anei uva nao dom'a napan teng lhon le, hichu phatah in vechil lhonin lang, naosen chu pasal ahileh natha lhon ding; numei ahile vang na hinghoi lhon ding ahi,” ati.
\v 17 Amavang naodom teni chun Pathen agin lhon jeh chun, lengpa thupeh chu anahsah lhon tapon, naosen pasal'a hungpeng lha ho jong chu ahinghoi lhon tan ahi.
\v 18 Chuin lengpan naodom teni chu aheng'a akouvin, “Ipi jeh a hiche hi nabol lhon hitam?” tin adong'in, chule “Ipi jeh a naosen pasal ho chu, nahinghoi lhon ham?” tin ajah lhon'a aseiyin ahi.
\v 19 Naodom tenin adonbut in “Hebrew numei ho hi Egypt numei hotoh abang pouve, amaho hi athohhat un aheng'u akilhun masang'in amaho le amaho bailam tah in ana kidoplhah jitauvin aphatchan kalapji lhonpoi,” tin asei lhon'e.
\v 20 Pathen chu naodom teni din aphalheh jengin, Israel te chu apunbe cheh cheh tauvin ahile, athanei nau jong ahung hatdoh cheh cheh jeng tan ahi.
\v 21 Naodom teni in Pathen agin lhon jeh chun, Pathen'in amani chu ama ama ding cheh insung asem dohpeh lhon'in ahi.
\v 22 Chuin Pharaoh in amite jouse hiche thupeh hi aneiyin: “Hebrew naosen'a penglha pasal kiti phot chu Nile Vadung lam'a na pailhah jeng diu, ahinlah numeiya hung peng chengse vang chu hing hoiyun,” ati. \x + \xo 1:22 \xt Act 7:19\x*
\c 2
\s1 Mose Pen
\p 
\v 1 Hiche phatlai hin, Levi insung'a kon pasal khat leh Levi insungmi numei khat ma akicheng lhon tan ahi.
\v 2 Numeinu chu ahung gaijin chapa khat ahing tai. Amanun achapa chu aven ahile lunglhai umtah naosen ahin, lhathum sung'in asel tan ahi. \x + \xo 2:2 \xt Act 7:20; Heb 11:23\x*
\v 3 Ahivang'in amanun achapa chu asel joulou phat in, sinkhup Papyrus naang'a kisa khat agalan twilutna lou dingin avonglai jouse ahuhbit sohkeiye. Chuin sinkhup sung'a naocha chu akhum'in Nile Vadung pang phaipheng lah achun alha lut tai.
\v 4 Chuin naosen a unu jong gamla thim'a kon'in adingin naosen chu i-atidem tin agalvet in ahi.
\v 5 Chujouvin Pharaoh chanu vadung'a kisil dingin ahung suh tan, asottolle ho jong vadung pang achun avahle uvin ahi. Chuin amanun phaipheng phung lah a sinkhup chu ahin mudoh tan, aga ladin asohnu chu asol tan ahi.
\v 6 Lengpa chanun jong sinkhup chu ahongdoh in ahile, naocha chu amu in ahi. Chuin naocha chu akap in, amanun jong naocha chu avoujang natpi lheh in, “Hiche hi Hebrew mite cha khat hitei ding ahi,” ati.
\v 7 Hichun naosen sopinun jong lengpa chanu heng ahin naije. “Keima kache a Hebrew numei khat naosen don ding kagahol peh ding ham?” tin adong'e.
\v 8 Lengpa chanu in jong, “Henge, gapui jin!” tin adonbut in, numeinu jong ache in naosen hingnu mama chu aga puiye.
\v 9 Chuin lengpa chanu'n jong naosen hingnu jah a aseijin. “Naosen hi lanlang neidon peh in, Keiman nadon man kapeh ding nahi,” ati. Chuin numeinu in jong naosen chu a-inlam'a adom'in amapa chu adon tan ahi.
\v 10 Khonung'in, chapang pa jong akhanglen tan ahile, anu in amapa chu Pharaoh chanu henga ahung thahkit tan, achapa mong mong dingin Lengpa chanun amapa chu amin Mose asah tai, ajeh chu amanun aseijin, “Keiman amapa hi twi lah a kon kaloidoh ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 2:10 \xt Act 7:21\x*
\s1 Median Gam'a Mose Ajamlut
\p 
\v 11 \x + \xo 2:11 \xt Heb 11:24\x*Kum phabep ache nungin, Mose jong ahung khanglen tan, amapa jong asopiho vil din achetou tan, aman jong asopi Hebrew mite hunam'a na atohsah nau aga mudoh tai. Agavil pet chun, Egypt mikhat in asopi Hebrew mikhat chung'a akhut alha chu amupaijin ahi. \x + \xo 2:11 \xt Act 7:23-28\x*
\v 12 Akimvel avet a koiman eivepoi, ti aphot chen phat in, Mose'n Egypt mipa chu athat in neldi lah a asel tan ahi.
\v 13 Ajing nikho in, asopi ho vildin Mose apotdoh kit tan ahile, Hebrew mini akinah lhon aga amun ahi. “Ipi jeh a nagolpa navoh ham?” tin kinah hin panpa heng'a chun Mose'n aseiye.
\v 14 Amapan adonbut in, “Koiham nangma keiho chunga leng'a na pansah le thutan dinga thaneina nape? Janhi a Egypt mipa natha banga chu keima jong tha ding neigot ham?” tin aseiyin ahileh, Mose jong akichan “Ka thilbol mijousen ahetai,” tin angaiton ahi.”
\v 15 Mose thilbol chu Pharaoh in ahin jadoh tahbeh tan, chuin Mose chu tha ding ago tan ahi. Ahivang'in Mose jong Pharaoh angsung'a kon'in ajam'in Median gamsung'a cheng din achetai. Median alhun chun Mose jong twikul pang'a atou tan ahi. \x + \xo 2:15 \xt Act 7:29; Heb 11:27\x*
\v 16 Tun Median thempupa chun chanu sagi aneiyin amaho chengse chu apau ganchahon ho dingin twi kongho chu athal ngai bang'un ahung thal dim'un ahi.
\v 17 Ahinlah kelngoi ching midang phabep ahung uvin amaho chu anodoh un ahi. Hichun Mose jong achomdoh jengin kelngoi ching hoa kon chun numei chapang ho chu ahuhdoh tan ahi. Chuin amapan amaho ganchate a ding twi chu athal peh tan ahi.
\v 18 Numei chapang ho chu apau Reuel heng ale lhun uchun, amapan adongun, “Ipi jeh a tuni nahung kimale uham?” atin ahile,
\v 19 ama hon jong adonbut uvin, “Egypt mi khat in kelngoi ching hoa kon'a eihuhdoh uva, chule amapa chun keiho ding le igancha hon houva ding twi eithal peh jeh u ahi,” atiuve.
\v 20 “Ahile amapa hoiba ham?” tin apauvin adong'in, “Ipi dinga amapa chu chukom'a chu nahin dalhah uham? Ahung'a ankong isokhom diuvin gakouvun,” ati.
\v 21 Mose'n jong akounau chu asanpeh in, thempupa toh chun hiva chun acheng khom tan ahi. Hiche phatlai chun, Reuel in achanu Zipporah chu Mose ji dingin ape tan ahi.
\v 22 Phat chomkhat jouvin, amanun chapa khat ahing'in, Mose'n Gershom asah tai “Ajeh chu keima hi gamchom beh a khopem kahi,” tina ahi.
\v 23 Kum phabep ache nungin, Egypt lengpa athitan ahi. Hinlah Israel te chu soh a kihen ohna noiya pohgih poa khoisa jing nalai ahiuve. Panpi ngaiyin akap un, aka awgin'u chu Pathen angsung alhung tan ahi.
\v 24 Akhoisat nau Pathen'in aja tan, chuin Abraham, Isaac leh Jacob heng'a akitepna ahin geldoh tan ahi. \x + \xo 2:24 \xt Semtilbu 15:13,14\x*
\v 25 Aman Israel mite chu avesuh in, chuin tunvang toh phat ahitai ti chu ahe tan ahi.
\c 3
\s1 Mose chule Hamboh kong
\p 
\v 1 Mose’n nikhat anupa pa Midian thempu pa Jethro kelngoi achin laijin, kelngoi hon chu gamla tah gamthip lam'a apuiyin, Pathen molsang, Sinai mol lam'a chun ahung tan ahi.
\v 2 Hiche laimun'a chun Pathen vantil meikong in hamboh lah a ahung kilah in, Mose in lungdong tah in aven ahi. Hamboh chu akong jengin hinlah akavam deh pon ahi.
\v 3 Chuin Mose ama leh ama akihoulim in, “Hiche hi datmah umtah thil ahiye, ipi jeh pentah a hiche hamboh khu kavam lou ahidem? kache a kavet tei angaiye” ati.
\v 4 Hichu vedingin Mose’n hilam chu anailut jep jep e ti Pakaiyin amu phat in, Pathen'in hamboh lailunga kon'in, “Mose! Mose!” tin akouvin ahile, Mose in jong adonbut in “Keima hiva kaum'e,” ati.
\v 5 “Hin nailut hihbeh in” tin Pakaiyin agih tan ahi. “Nakeng chot kisut in, ajeh chu nangma muntheng'a ding nahi.
\v 6 Keima napa dinga a Pathen kahi - Abraham Pathen, Isaac Pathen, leh Jacob Pathen kahi,” ati. Hichu Mose in ajah phat in amai akhutai, ajeh chu Pathen avet ngamlou ahi.
\v 7 Chuphat in Pakaiyin ahenga aseijin, “Egypt a kamite kibol gimna ka muchen tai. Achung uva tohvai hom hon asuhgim nau aka awgin'u kaja tan ahi. Heng'e, athohgim nau abonchan ka hechen tai, ati.
\v 8 Hijeh a chu Egypt mite thaneina noiya kon'a amaho huhdoh ding le Egypt gam'a kon'a gampha tah, khoiju le bongnoi lonna gam hichu - Canaan mite, Hit mite, Amor mite, Periz mite, Hivi mite chule Jebus mite tua achenna'u gam'a puilut dinga Keima hikom'a hung kumlha kahi, ati.
\v 9 Vetan! Israel chate ka awgin ka angsung ahunglhung tai, chule Egypt miten asuhgim nau kichen tah in kamutai.
\v 10 Tun che jengin, ajeh chu Keiman nang hi Pharaoh henga kasol nahiye. Kami Israel te Egypt gam'a konna nahin puidoh ding ahi,” ati.
\v 11 Hinlah Mose Pathen heng'ah akiphin in, “Kei koi kahia Pharaoh henga kaga kilah ding ham? Kei koi ka hia Israel te Egypt gam'a kon'a ka hin puidoh ding ham?” ati.
\v 12 Pathen'in adonbut in, “Keiman kaumpi jing ding nahiye. Keiman kasol nahina nangma dinga melchihna hiche hi ahi: Nangman miho chu Egypt gam'a kon'a nahin puidoh tengleh, hiche mol tah a hi Pathen nahou ding'u ahi,” ati.
\v 13 Ahivang'in Mose akiphin'in, “Keima Israel chate henga kachea ajah uva, ‘Napu napa teu Pathen'in na heng uva eihinsol ahi,’ tin sei leng ‘Amin ipi ham?’ tia eidoh diu ahi, chuteng amaho chu iti ka donbut ding ham?,” ati.
\v 14 Pathen'in Mose adonbut in, “KEIMA HI KEI,A KAHI JENG'E. Hiche hi Israel te heng'a seipeh in: Keima chun naheng uva eihinsol ahi,” tin ati.
\v 15 Pathen'in jong Mose heng'a aseiyin, “Hiche hi Israel te heng'a seipeh in: Yahweh,* napu napa teu Pathen - Abraham Pathen, Isaac Pathen, chule Jacob Pathen'in - naheng uva eihin sol ahi. Hiche hi ka tonsot min ahi, akhang akhang'a nageldoh jing diu kamin ahi.
\v 16 “Tun chenlang Israel sung'a upaho gakou khom tan. Aheng uva seipeh in 'Yahweh, napu napa teu Pathen - Abraham, Isaac, chule Jacob Pathen - kahenga akilah in ahi. Aman kajah a aseiyin, “Keiman naichan kanave jing'un, chule Egypt miten na engbol nau keiman kamui.
\v 17 Keiman nangho Egypt a na genthei thoh nauva kon'a huhdoh dinga kakitep ahi. Keiman khoiju leh bongnoi lonna gam'a chu kapuilut ding nahiuve - hichu Canaan mite, Hit mite, Amor mite, Periz mite, Hivi mite chule Jebus mite tua achen nau gam khu ahi,” ati.
\v 18 “Israel upahon nathusei angai diu ahi. Chuteng nang leh Israel upa chengse Egypt lengpa heng'a nache tei uva, ‘Pakai, Hebrew mite Pathen chun, eikimupi uve. Hijeh chun lungset tah in nithum sung'a gamthip lam'a kakhol jin uva Pakai ka Pathen'u henga kilhaina kasem dingu ahi” tia aheng'a nagasei diu ahi.
\v 19 “Amavang Egypt lengpa chu khut thahat in ano kahse a nahin soldoh lou diu keiman kahei,” ati.
\v 20 “Hijeh a chu Keiman kakhut ka lhan a, chule Egypt mite kajep ding, alah uva thil kidang jouse kabol ding ahi. Ajona le Aman nahin soldoh ding'u ahi.
\v 21 Chule keiman Egypt mite mitvet a khotona kahin chan sah ding nahiuve. Ama hon thilpeh nahin peh dingu chuteng khut goh keova na dalhah lou diu ahiye. \x + \xo 3:21 \xt Potdohbu 12:35,36\x*
\v 22 Israel numei jousen akinaipiu Egypt mite leh a in'uva um gamchom numei ho kom'a sana leh dangka chule ponsil akithum cheh ding'u ahi. Na chanu teu leh na chapa teu hiche ho chu navon peh dingu, Egypt mite haosatna jouse na holhah peh dingu ahi,” ati.
\c 4
\s1 Pakai thahatna melchihna ho
\p 
\v 1 Hinlah Mose avel'in akiphin kit in, “Ei tahsanlel uhenlang ka thusei ngai hih uleh iti tantem? 'Nangma heng'a Pakai akilah kha him him poi' tiu leh iti tantem?”
\v 2 Chuin Pakaiyin ajah a, “Nakhut a nachoi chu ipi ham?” tia adoh le, Mose’n adonbut in “Tenggol ahi,” ati.
\v 3 Pakaiyin ajah a, “Tol'ah seplhan,” ati. Hichun Mose’n tenggol chu tol'ah asep lhan, chuin gul ahung kisoh tan! Mose anung chop jengin ahi.
\v 4 Chuin Pakaiyin aheng'a, “Nakhut lhangdoh inlang ameiyin man tem'in” ati. Hichun Mose’n akhut alhaangdoh in aman in ahile, akhut ah kelngoi chinna tenggol ahung kinung sodoh kit tan ahi.
\v 5 Pakaiyin ajah a, “Hiche melchihna hi nabol ding ahi. Chuteng apu apateu Pathen - Abraham Pathen, Isaac Pathen chuleh Jacob Pathen chu nangma heng'ah akilah mong'e ti ahin tahsan dingu ahi,” ati.
\v 6 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'ah, “Tun nakhut chu na sangkholchol sunga nadip a chun koiyin,” atile, Mose'n jong akhut chu asangkholchol sunga akoiyin, akhut chu alah doh kit a ahile, akhut chu aphah in buhbang bangin abang jengin ahi.
\v 7 Pakaiyin, “Tun nakhut chu na sangkholchol sunga nadip'a avel'in koikit tem in,” atin ahi. Hijeh chun Mose in jong akhut chu anung koilut kit in, chuin ala doh kit in ahile atidang bangin atahsa adamsel tan ahi.
\v 8 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Ijem tia nangma na tahsan lou uva chule melchihna masapen jeng'a jong atahsan theilou uva ahile, melchihna ani channa a atahsan diu ahitai.
\v 9 Chule hiche melchihna teni jeng'a jong atahsan thei lou uva ahile, Nile Vadunga kon'in twi themkhat la inlang tolgo laiya sung lhan. Hichu nabol teng, Nile Vadung twi chu tolgo laiya thisan kisoh ding ahi,” ati.
\v 10 Ahin Mose Pakai heng'a ataovin, “O Pakai, keima thusei them kahipoi. Achesa phat hihen, chule tujengin jong, kahenga thu nasei nung hijongleh, kalei a-oh jin, chule ka thusei angongkai jie,” ati.
\v 11 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose adong paijin, “Koiham mihem kam sem? Koi ham mihem apaothei ahilouleh apaomo, kho jathei ahilouleh ana ngong, kho muthei ahilouleh mitcho umsah nadia gellhuhna sem ji? Hichu Keima, na Pakai kahi hilou ham?
\v 12 Tun chen! na paodohna chan'a Ka umpi ding, chule na thuseina chan'a Keiman kalamhil ding nahi,” ati.
\v 13 Ahinlah Mose avel in Pakai heng'a ataovin, “Pakai, lungset tah in! Midang khattou sol tan,” ati.
\v 14 Chuin Pakai Mose chung'a alunghang tan, “Aphai,” ati. “Na sopipa Levi mi Aaron um'a hilou ham? Aman lei kileh pel'in thu aseitheiye ti keiman kahei. Chule vetan! Tun nang toh kimuto dingin ahung tai. Nang toh kimu ding lung thanopna a dim ahi,” ati.
\v 15 Ama chu houlim pin lang, thu ho hi akamsung'a mop in. Keiman na paodohna chan lhon'a kaumpi ding, na ni lhon'a na thilbolna chan lhon'a nalamhil lhon nang'e, ati.
\v 16 “Aaron hi nangma dinga miho lah a thuseija pang ding ahi. Nangma dinga nakam sung'a pang ding chule ama ding’a nangma hi Pathen khel’a nadin ding, aman ipi asei ding nahil ding ahi,” ati.
\v 17 Na kelngoi tenggol hi kichoiyin lang, melchihna bol dinga ka thumop chengse bolna dingin mang chan,” ati.
\s1 Mose Egypt lam akile
\p 
\v 18 Hijeh chun Mose inlam'a anu-pa-pa Jethro henga akile tan ahi. “Lungset tah in kasopi ho heng lam Egypt gam'a kile tange,” tin Mose’n aseiyin, “Hing nalaiyu hinauvam tijong hepha lou kahi,” ati in ahile, Jethro in “Lungmong in chen,” tin adonbut in ahi.
\v 19 Mose in Median adalhah masang'in Pakaiyin aheng'a aseiyin, “Egypt a kile tan, ijeh-inem itileh nangma nathat nom ho abonchauvin athigam tauve,” ati.
\v 20 Hijeh chun Mose in ajinu leh achate akipuiyin, sangan chunga atousah in, chuin Egypt gam'a akile tauvin ahi. Akhut a Pathen tenggol chu achoiyin ahi.
\v 21 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseiyin, “Egypt gamsung na lelhun teng, Pharaoh henga chen lang keiman bol dinga thuneina kapeh bangin thil kidang ho jouse abonchan gabol'in, ati. Ahinlah Keiman alungthim kasuh tah ding chuteng miho chedoh ding aphal louding ahi.”
\v 22 Chuteng nangman aheng'a nasei ding, 'Hiche hi Pakai thusei ahiye: Israel hi keima chapa peng masapen ahi.
\v 23 Keiman thu kapeh nahi, “Ka chapa soldoh tan, chuti leh aman keima eihou thei ding ahi.” Ahivanga nangman nahsah louva nakoi jeh in, tua hi keiman na chapa amasapen katha ding ahitai!”' ati. \x + \xo 4:23 \xt Potdohbu 12:29\x*
\s1 Mose Egypt gam akile
\p 
\v 24 Egypt gam ajot laiyun Mose leh a insung mite jan geh din ngahmun khat a akinga tauvin, Pakaiyin amapa chu akimaitopin, amapa chu atha pai ding ahitai.
\v 25 Amavang Mose jinu Zipporah in songgiel chem alan achapa chep atanpeh in ahi. Amanun chep chu amapa keng atohkhah sah in hiti hin aseiye, “Tua hi nangma hiche thisan jal'a kei dia moulang nahitai,” ati.
\v 26 (Amanun “thisan jal'a moulang” tia asei chu chep tan chu aseina ahi.) Chujou chun Pakaiyin amapa chu adalhatai.
\v 27 Tun Pakaiyin Aaron henga, “Mose kimupi din gamthip lam'a khun chedoh in,” ati. Hijeh chun Aaron Pathen molsang lam'a achen Mose aga kimupi in, a angkoiyin ahi.
\v 28 Hichun Mose in jong Aaron jah a Pakaiyin sei dinga athupeh jouse ajah a aseipeh tan ahi. Chule bol dinga athupeh thil kidang melchihna ho chung chang ho chu aseipeh tan ahi.
\v 29 Chuin Mose le Aaron Egypt gam ahung kile lhon'in Israel upa jouse abonchan akoukhom lhon tan ahi.
\v 30 Aaron in Pakaiyin Mose athumop chengse chu abonchan amaho jah a aseipeh sohkeiyin, Chule Mose in melchihna thil kidang ho chu aheng uvah abol in avetsah sohkei uve.
\v 31 Hichun Israel miten Mose leh Aaron chu Pathen'in ahin sol mong ahi ti atahsan tauve. Pakaiyin amaho chung chang agelkhoh in agim hesoh nau amutai ti ajahdoh phat un, abohkhup uvin ahou tauvin ahi.
\c 5
\s1 Pharaoh henga Mose le Aron in thu asei lhon
\p 
\v 1 Hicheng jouse chu Israel upaho leh lamkai chengse heng'a aseipeh chai lhon phat in, Pharaoh heng'a Mose le Aaron achelhonin aga sei lhon tai. “Hiche hi ahi Israel te Pakai, Pathen'in asei chu: Gamthip noiya kami Israel ten keima jabolna a kut abolna diuvin sol tauvin,” tin amapa henga asei lhon tai.
\v 2 Pharaoh in ale donbut in, “Hichu hi mong ham? Pakai kitipa chu koiham? Keiman ipi jeh a ama thu kangaiya Israel te chu ka soldoh ding ham? Pakai kitipa chu keiman kahe khapoi, chule keiman Israel te ka soldoh louding ahi,” ati.
\v 3 Ahinlah Aaron leh Mose apang tinten lhonin, “Hebrew mite Pathen chun eikimupi lhon ahi,” tin aphongdoh lhon'e. “Hijeh chun ni thum sung'a gamthip a kache uva Pakai ka Pathen'u henga kilhaina kaga semna diuvin neisol tauvin. Achuti louva ahile, Pakaiyin gamna hise ahinlan sah ding ahilouleh chemjam'a eitha gam diu ahi,” ati lhon'e.
\v 4 Pharaoh in adonbut in, “Mose leh Aaron, ipi dinga mipite anatoh nauva konna alungu nalahmang lhon'a nasuhboi lhon ham? Na kitoh kit tauvin!
\v 5 Ven, “Gamsung'a namite hi tampi ahiuvin, ahin nangnin amaho hi anatohnau natansah lhon tai,” ati.
\s1 Changphol jaolouva chehlhang kisem
\p 
\v 6 Hiche nikho mama chun Pharaoh in Egypt mite dinga soh natong vaipo ho leh Israel lamkai ho chu hiche thupeh hi apetan ahi:
\v 7 “Chehlhang semna dingin changpol pe tahih un. Ama ama cheh kihol sah tauvin!
\v 8 Ahivang'a masang'a nabol sah ngai bang uva chehlhang nasem sah jat u kibanga nasem sah dingu ahi. Achanvou u lhom jong lhom sah hih un. Athase gam tauve. Hijeh a chu ama hon, 'Cheu hitin I-Pathen'u henga kilhaina gasem tau hite,' tia asap jengu ahi, ati.
\v 9 Achung uva natoh hahsa cheh koibe peh un. A-ulsau lonsah un! Hichun jou thu angaisah louna diuva ahil dingu ahi!” ati.
\v 10 Hichun soh natong vaipo ho leh natong lamkai ho chu acheuvin mipi ho heng'a aseipeh tauvin: “Pharaoh in asei hiche hi ahi: Tu apat changpol kapeh talou ding'u nahi.
\v 11 Cheuvin lang nangma nangman gakipoh uvin. Hoilai mun hijongleh namu thei chan'un gakihol tauvin. Ahinlah masanga chehlhang jat mama semdoh dingu ahi,” ati.
\v 12 Hijeh chun mipi jong Egypt gamtin'ah changpol holnan akithe cheh tauvin ahi.
\v 13 Chomkhat jouvin, Egypt natong vaipo hon gahtah in aboljom nalaiyun, “Changpol kapeh laiyuva nasem bang uva, niseh leh chehlhang nasem doh ding jat u nasuh bulhit tei ding'u ahi” tin ngehna aneiyuve.
\v 14 Chuin Israel natong lamkaiya anganse hou chu ajep uvin, “Ipi dinga janhia chule tunia jong na tohdoh diu jat na tohdoh louvu ham? tin ngehna aneiyuvin ahi.
\v 15 Chuphat in Israel natong lamkai cheng Pharaoh heng'a ache un chule atao uvin, “Lungset tah in nasohte hi hitin neibol hih un,” tin athum un ahi.
\v 16 “Changpol la neipe pouvin, ahinlah soh vaipo hon angeh nalaiyun “chehlhang sem'un!” tin eivo jing'un, ahinlah hiche hi keiho themmo ahipoi! Nangma mite ho mama ngoh ding ahijoi!” tin asei uve.
\v 17 Ahivang'in Pharaoh apeng jah jengin, Thase! Nangho thase nahiuve! Hijeh a chu hitia hi naseiyu ahi, 'Cheu hitin chule I-Pakaiyu heng'a kilhaina gatoh doh ute natiu ahi.'
\v 18 “Tun natong din kileuvin! Nangho changpol na kipelou diu, ahivang'a chehlhang nasem doh diu jat lhingset a nasem doh teitei ding'u ahi,” ati.
\v 19 “Niseh a chehlhang nasem jat u nakemsuh sah theilou ding'u ahi,” ati jeh uchun Israel natong lamkai hon nasa tah a bolgim'a aum'u chu amu tauvin ahi.”
\v 20 Pharaoh thutanna insung ahin dalhah phat un, pam lang'a amaho ana ngah Mose leh Aaron chu akimupi uvin ahi.
\v 21 Chuin natong lamkai ho chun ajah lhon'ah, “Pakaiyin nachung chang thu lhon tan henlang gotna nape lhon hen, ijeh inem itileh Pharaoh leh alhacha ho angsung'a nei suh namset u ahi. Nangnin amaho khut a chemjam na koipeh lhonin, nei thagam sah kigot un ahi!” ati lhon e.
\s1 Mose taona
\p 
\v 22 Chuin Mose Pakai heng'a akile in akiphin tai, “Ipi dinga namite chung'a hitobang gimna hi nalhun sah hitam, Pakai? Ipi dinga keima nei sol ham?”
\v 23 Nangma thalheng'a thusei dinga Pharaoh heng kahunga kipat namite chunga akhanse cheh cheh jon ahi. Hinlah nangman amaho huhdohna din ima nabolpoi!”
\c 6
\s1 Pathen'in amaho Huhdohna dinga Kitepna asem
\p 
\v 1 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose henga aseiyin, “Tua hi keiman Pharaoh chung'a ipi ka bol'am namu ding ahi. Aman kaban thahatna ahin hetdoh teng, aman mipi ho chu ahin soldoh ding ahi. Dihtah a, aman hunam a agamsung dalha dinga ahin soldoh ding'u ahi!”
\v 2 Chule Pathen'in Mose henga aseiyin, “Keima Yahweh - 'Pakai' kahi. \x + \xo 6:2 \xt Semtilbu 17:1; 28:3; 35:11; Potdohbu 3:13-15\x*
\v 3 Abraham henga, Isaac henga, chule Jacob henga El-Shaddai - 'Hatchungnung Pathen' - aheng uva ka kilah in ahi, hinlah kamin, Yahweh, ahi ti amaho heng'a kaphong doh poi.
\v 4 Chule kholjin miho banga achen nau gam, Canaan gam peh dinga kakitepna keiman amaho toh avel'in namdetna kanei kit in ahi.
\v 5 Israel mite, tua Egypt mite soh a pang ho thohgimna kaja nai ti hi naginchat mong thei ahi. Chule amaho toh ka kitepna jong phatah in kahe jing nai.
\v 6 “Hijeh chun, Israel mite henga seiyin: 'Keima Pakai kahi. Egypt gam'a nasoh tan nauva kon'a ka huhdoh ding chule na thohgim nauva kon'a kalha ong ding nahiuve. Keiman nangho ban thahat tah le thutanna gimnei tah a kalhatdam ding nahiuve.
\v 7 Keima mite nahi mong uve tia kachu dingu, chule na Pathen'u kahi ding ahi. Chuteng keima hi nangho Pakai na Pathen'u Egypt gam'a na thohgim nauva kon'a nahin lha ong pau chu kahi nahin hetdoh dingu ahi.
\v 8 Keiman Abraham, Isaac, chuleh Jacob heng'a kaki hahselna gam'a chu ka puilut ding nahiuve. Nangho goulo ding mong monga kapeh ding nahiuve. Keima Pakai kahi!'”
\v 9 Pakaiyin asei bangin Mose in jong Israel mite heng'a aseipeh in, ahinlah ama hon avel'in angainom tapouvin ahi. Ajeh chu amaho asoh chan nauva aki suhgim'u chun alungphatmo sah val tauvin ahi.
\v 10 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseiyin,
\v 11 “Egypt lengpa Pharaoh heng'a leche inlang, Israel miten na gamsung dalha tauhen tin aheng'a gaseiyin.”
\v 12 “Ahinlah Pakai!” Mose anompon, “Ka miten ka thusei eingaipeh tapouvin tin. Iti Pharaoh in ka thu ngai mong nante tia kakinep ding ham? Keima mipaomo kahi.”
\v 13 Ahivangin Pakaiyin Mose leh Aaron heng'a thu aseiyin Israel te ding leh Egypt lengpa Pharaoh dinga abol lhon ding ho ape lhon'in, Pakaiyin Israel te Egypt akon puidoh dingin Mose leh Aaron thupeh anei tan ahi.
\s1 Mose leh Aaron Khanggui
\p 
\v 14 Hichengse hi apu apateu khang chedol'a Israel insung upaho ahi: Israel insung'a apeng masapen Reuben chapa te se chu: Hanoch, Pallu, Hezron, chule Carmi. Amaho chilhahse hi Reuben insung kon ahi tauve.
\v 15 Simeon chapa te se chu: Jemuel, Jamin, Ohad, Jakin, Zohar leh Shaul ahiuve. (Shaul hingnu vang chu Canaan numei ahi.) Amaho chilhahse hi Simeon insung kon ahi tauve.
\v 16 Levi chilhah te se amaho insung minbu dungjuiya achapa te chu: Gershon, Kohath leh Merari. (Levi chu kum ja le somthum le sagi ana hing'e). \x + \xo 6:16 \xt Minbu 3:17-20; 26:57,58; 1 Thusimbu 6:16-19\x*
\v 17 Gershon chihahte chu Libni leh Shimei ahi lhonne. Anigel lhonin insung khangguiyin akisim lhon tan ahi.
\v 18 Kohath chilhah te chu Amram, Izhar, Hebron leh Uzziel ahi. (Kohath chu kum ja le somthum le thum ana hing'e.)
\v 19 Merari chilhah te chu Mahli leh Mushi ahi lhon'e. Ama ho chengse hi Levi insung chedol minbua amin cheh uchu ahi.
\v 20 Amram chun apa sopinu Jochebed chu jin aneiyin, amanun chapa ahin peh in, Aaron leh Mose ahi lhon'e. (Amram chu kum ja le somthum le sagi ana hing'e.)
\v 21 Izhar chapa te chu Korah, Nepheg leh Zicri ahiuve.
\v 22 Uzziel chapa te chu Mishael, Elzaphan leh Sithri ahiuve.
\v 23 Aaron in Elisheba aki chenpin, ama chu Amminadab chanu chule Nahson dinga asopinu ahi. Amanun chapa ahindoh ho chu Nadab, Abihu, Eleazar leh Ithamar ahiuve.
\v 24 Korah chapa te ho chu Assir, Elkanah leh Abiasaph ahiuvin, amaho chilhah hi Korah insung mi ahi tauve.
\v 25 Aaron chapa Eleazar chun Putiel chanute lah a khat ji in aneiyin, chuin amanun chapa khat ahing'in Phinehas ahi. Amaho cheng hi Levi insung'a pu le pate ho insung bahkai dungjuiya chengse chu ahiuve.
\v 26 Aaron leh Mose hiche laiya kiminphah teni mama hi ahi lhon'e Pakaiyin ajah lhon'a, “Israel mite chu Egypt gam'a kon'in sepoyte bangin hin lamkai lhonin,” tia asei chu.
\v 27 Egypt lengpa, Pharaoh kom'a Israel mite Egypt gam'a konna puidoh dinga thu sei chu, Mose leh Aaron ahi lhon'e.
\s1 Mose Khel'a Aaron'in Thu Aseina
\p 
\v 28 Egypt gam'a Pakaiyin Mose ahoulimpi achun,
\v 29 aheng'a aseiyin, “Keima Pakai kahi! Egypt lengpa, Pharaoh henga seiyin, keiman naheng'a kasei jouse chu.”
\v 30 Ahinlah Mose in Pakai akinel pin, aseiyin, “Hichu ka bolthei louding ahi! Ajeh chu keima mipaomo kahi! Ipi jeh a Pharaoh in ka thusei angai ding ham?” ati.
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 Hijeh chun Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseiyin, “Hiche hi phate chan ngaiyin. Pharaoh lengpa kom'a Pathen tobang'a kasem ding nahiye, chule na sopipa, Aaron, hi nang dia themgaova pang ding ahi.
\v 2 Ka thupeh jouse hi Aaron jah a seijin lang, Aaron in Pharaoh heng'a Israel mite agamsung'a kon'a asol dohna dinga thu apeh tei ding ahi.
\v 3 Ahinlah Keiman Pharaoh lungthim ka suhtah ding, chuteng melchihna le thil kidang tampi Egypt gamsung'a kapun sah ding ahi. \x + \xo 7:3 \xt Act 7:36\x*
\v 4 Hiche a jong chu Pharaoh in na thu angai loulai ding ahi. Keiman Egypt gamsung'a ka khut kahin lhanjah ding. Keiman ka thaneina a kon - kamite, Israel te Egypt gam'a kon thutanna gimnei tah pum'a ka huhdoh ding ahiuve.
\v 5 Keiman kaban thahat kahin lhan'a Israel te kahin puidoh teng, Egypt miten Keima hi Pakai kahi ahin hetdoh diu ahitai.”
\v 6 Chuin Pakai thupeh bangin Mose leh Aaron injong abol lhon tan ahi.
\v 7 Pharaoh heng'a ngehna aganei lai lhon chun Mose kum somget ahitan, chule Aaron chu kum som get leh kum thum ahitai.
\s1 Tenggol Gul Kisoh
\p 
\v 8 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose leh Aaron heng'ah thu aseiyin,
\v 9 “Pharaoh in ngehna ahin nei ding, ‘Thil kidang nei vetsah lhonin.' Hitobang ahinsei teng, Aaron henga seiyin ‘Na tenggol chu la inlang Pharaoh masang laiya chun sep lhan, chuteng gul hung kisoh ding ahi.”
\v 10 Chuin Mose leh Aaron jong Pharaoh heng'a ache lhonin Pakai thupeh bangin abol lhon tai. Aaron in tenggol chu Pharaoh le avaipipo te ho angsung'a chun asep lhan ahile, gul ahung kisoh tai!
\v 11 Hichun Pharaoh in ama miching ho le doithem ho akou khomin, Egypt gam'a mitphel doithem hon jong chuche tobang chu abol'un ahi.
\v 12 Atenggol'u tol'a aseplha cheh uvin ahile, amahoa jong gul akisoh tai! Ahinlah Aaron tenggol chun amaho tenggol ho chu avallhum soh tai.
\v 13 Hicheng nung jeng jong hin Pakaiyin asei masat bang chun Pharaoh lungthim chu atah jing nalaiyin, thu ima ngaisah in anei hih laiye.
\s1 Twi Thisan Kisoh
\p 
\v 14 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseiyin, “Pharaoh lungchang atah in, chule aman mipi ho soldoh ding anom naipoi.
\v 15 Hijeh chun jingkah teng Pharaoh vadung lam'a ahung suh teng nangma na che ding. Nile vadung pam'a nadin ding, hikom'a chu nakimupi ding ahi. Na tenggol gul kisoh chu kichoi teiyin.
\v 16 Chuteng akom'a hiti hin seiyin, 'Pakai, Hebrew mite Pathen'in nakom'a thuseiya eihin sol ahi, “Kamiten keima eihouna ding uvin gamthip noiya soldoh tan.” Tugeiyin, nangman ama thusei iman na ngaisah poi.
\v 17 Hijeh a chu hiche hi Pakaiyin asei ahi: “Keima Pakai kahina ka kilah sah ding ahi.” Vetan! Ka khut a um tenngol hi mangcha a Nile twi kajep ding, chuteng vadung hi thisan kisoh ding ahi. \x + \xo 7:17 \xt Rev 16:4\x*
\v 18 Asung'a nga jouse thi ding, chule vadung uilhahel ding, Egypt miten Nile vadung'a kon twi adon thei louhel diu ahitai,” ati.
\v 19 Chujongleh Pakaiyin Mose heng ah aseiyin: “Aaron jah a seiyin, 'Na tenggol kimat inlang Egypt gam'a twi jouse chunga na khut jah inlang - vadung jouse, twinah jouse, luikhuh jouse chunga twi jouse thisan sosah tan. Egypt gam muntin'a twi jouse, thingtwikong le songkong jouse sunga twi jouse geiya thisan soh ding ahi.'”
\v 20 Chuin Mose leh Aaron in jong Pakai thupeh bangin abol lhon tan ahi. Pharaoh le athunei vaihomte hon avet laiyun, Aaron in jong atenggol ajahdoh in Nile luidung chu ajep jeng tan ahi. Phulou helouvin, vadung twi apumpin thisan akisoh hel tan ahi.
\v 21 Luidunga nga jouse athisohhel tan, chule twi anen behseh phat chun Egypt miten adon thei tapouvin ahi. Egypt gamsung pumpi mun jouse thisan dim ahitai.
\v 22 Ahivang'in Egypt gam'a mitphel doithem hon jong adoiyu mangchan ama hon jong twi thisan asosah uvin ahi. Hijeh chun Pharaoh lungthim chu atah jing nalaiye. Pakaiyin asei bangin Mose leh Aaron thusei chu nahsah in anei hih laiye.
\v 23 Pharaoh jong aleng inpi lam'ah akilen, hicheng thilsoh ho jouse chu alungthim'a gelkham asa hih laiye.
\v 24 Ahin Egypt mite jousen luipang dung alai thuh un twi akihol le tauvin ahi, ajeh chu ama hon Nile luidunga twi chu adonthei tah louvu ahi.
\v 25 Pakaiyin Nile luidung ajep kal nisagi alhing tan ahi.
\c 8
\s1 Egypt Gamsung'a Ukengte
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Pharaoh heng ah chen lang hiti hin gasei kit temin, “Hiche hi Pakai thusei ahi: Kamite soldoh jeng tan, chutileh ama hon keima kin abol ding'u ahiye.”
\v 2 “Nahsah moa amaho na soldoh louva ahileh, na gamsung pumpia ukeng kahin lansah ding ahi.”
\v 3 “Nile luidung jong ukeng dimlha jeng ding ahi. Na insung leh na lupna channa hung kaldoh diu! Na mite leh na nungjui ho jouse kom channa lhung ding, na changlhah meh nau jouse'a jong hung lut dimset ding ahiuve.”
\v 4 “Ukengte chung leh nanung juiho jouse chung'a chom le ding'u ahi.”
\v 5 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Aaron jah a seijin lang, ‘Egypt gamsung pumpi ukeng ten ahin lodimna dingin, na tenggol jah in, twinah jouse, twilam jouse leh luidung jouse chu jeptan! Ukeng ten Egypt gam pumpi hin lodim tante, tin seipeh in,” ati.
\v 6 Aaron'in jong Egypt gamsung twi chung'a akhut ajah in ajep tan ahile, ukengte ahung potdoh un Egypt gamsung pumpi alodim jeng tai!
\v 7 Ahinlah Egypt gam'a mitphel doithem hon jong hitobang chun abolthei uve. Ukengte chu gamsung'a alhalut thei un ahile gam pumpi chu ukengte adimlha tai.
\v 8 Chuphat in Pharaoh in Mose leh Aaron akouvin hiti hin aseije, “Pakai heng'a tao lhon tan, ajeh chu keima le ka mite jouse'a konna ukengte alahdohna dingin, chuteng keiman namite'u ka soldoh ding, amaho che uva Pakai kin agabol diu ahi,” ati.
\v 9 Mose'n adonbut in, “Nang le na sohte, chule namite dinga itih phat a katao ding nei seipeh in ati. Chuteng na in dung jouse'a ukengte Nile vadung lam'a kitol ding ahitai,” ati.
\v 10 Pharaoh in adonbut in ajah a, “Jing teng bol in,” ati. Mose'n henge, “Nasei bang bang hita hen. Chuti leh nangman keiho Pakai, Pathen tailou dang aumpoi ti nahin hetdoh ding ahi,” ati.
\v 11 “Ukeng ten nangma leh na nungjui ho jouse le namite naboncha uva na dalhah diu, Nile luidunga bou umden diu ahi,” ati.
\v 12 Chuin Mose leh Aaron jong Pharaoh angsung'a kon'in achedoh lhonin, Mose chu Pakai lam sang'in kap pum in ataovin, Pharaoh le amite a kon'in ukengte ladoh tan ati.
\v 13 Pakaiyin Mose taona chu asanpeh tan, indung jouse, loujao leh gamsung'a ukeng jouse asumang hel tan ahi.
\v 14 Egypt miten ukeng thisa ho chu aloh khom'un ahile gamsung pumpi a uilha jeng tan ahi.
\v 15 Ahinlah Pharaoh in dinmun ahung oldom tai ti ahin hetdoh phat in, angaija bangin alungthim atah kittai. Pakaiyin aseidohsa bangin Mose leh Aaron thusei chu anahsah kit tapoi.
\s1 Egypt Gamsung'a Thousi-Vaibong
\p 
\v 16 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Aaron heng'a seijin lang, ‘Na tenggol jandoh in tollhang jep temin. Egypt gamsung pumpia vut chu vaisi kisoh ding ahi,” ati.
\v 17 Pakai thupeh bangin Mose leh Aaron'in jong abol lhon tai. Aaron'in jong akhut ajah in atenggol'a tol lham chu ajep a ahile, vaisi tamtah in Egypt gam pumpi le agamcha jouseu alodim jeng tai. Egypt gamsunga vut jouse chu vaisi asoh tan ahi.
\v 18 Pharaoh doithem hon atobang bang abolthei jing vang uvin, tunvang alosam tauvin abolthei tapouvin ahi. Vaisi in mipi ho leh gamsung'a gancha jouse atomlha tauvin ahi.
\v 19 Hiti chun doithem hon jong Pharaoh heng'a aseiyun, “Hiche hi Pathen khutjung ahi!” ati tauve. Ahinlah Pharaoh lungthim chu angaija bangin atah jing nalaiye. Pakaiyin aseidoh sa bangin Pharaoh in jong amaho thusei chu anahsah dehpon ahi. \x + \xo 8:19 \xt Lk 11:20\x*
\v 20 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga hiti hin aseikit tai, “Jingkah teng Nile vadung lam'a Pharaoh hung ding chuteng nangman nakimupi ding ahi. Ajah a Pakaiyin hiti hin asei je, 'Kamite soldoh tan, ajeh chu ama hon keima kin abol ding'u ahi.
\v 21 Na soldoh louva ahile, Keiman namite, nanung juiho chule na insung jousea thousi kahin lansah ding ahi. Egypt mite in jouse thousin atomlhah jeng ding, gam leiset pumpi jong dimlha jeng ding ahi, ati.
\v 22 Ahinlah kamite chenna Goshen achom beh a kahoidoh ding ahi. Thousi khatcha lenglut louhel ding ahi. Chuteng leiset pumpin keima hi Pakai kitipa chu kahi ti nahin hetdoh diu ahi, ati.
\v 23 Keiman kamite leh na mite kah a kikhenna ka semdoh ding, Hiche thil kidang meilchihna hi jing nikho teng soh ding ahi,'” ati.
\v 24 Pakaiyin aseidoh bangin aboltan. “Thousi te chun Pharaoh insung, anungjui ho insung leh gamsung in jousea alenglut tauvin adimlha jeng tai.” Thousi ahon honin Egypt gamsung'a ahung kitol lut tan ahile gamsung pumpi chu athimlha jeng tan ahi.
\v 25 Chuphat in Pharaoh in Mose leh Aaron aga kouvin, hiti hin aseije, “Apha tai! Cheuvin lang Pakai maicham gasem tauvin, ati.” Aman aseijin, “Hichu Egypt gamsung'a nabol ding'u ahi,” ati.
\v 26 Mose'n adonbut in hitin aseije, “Hichu adih theipoi. Keihon Ka-Pakaiyu le Ka Pathen'u angsung'a kilhaina maicham kasem diu chu, hiche lai Egypt mite adia thil kitoh ahiye. Ven! Hitobang thil ho pi chu bol taleng'u Egypt miten song'a eiselih gam ding'u ahi,” ati.
\v 27 “Ka Pakaiyu leh ka Pathen'u angsung'a kilhaina hi nithum sung hitei ding ahi, hichu Pakaiyin keima ho dia aseidohsa ahi, ati.”
\v 28 Pharaoh in adonbut in ajah a hiti hin aseije, “Apha tai, che tauvin.” Keiman nangho gamthip noija na Pakaiyu kinbol dingin kaphal tai, amavang nache gamlat louhel ding'u ahi. “Tun cheuvin lang keima dingin nei taopeh un,” ati.
\v 29 Mose'n adonbut in, “Na angsung'a konna ka potdoh ding, jing nikho tengleh nangma akon leh namite chule na insung jouse uva konna thousi apotdohna dinga katao tei ding ahi, kagihna ahiye nangma Pharaoh in jong nei joulhep da uvin lang Israel miten jong Pakai dia kilhaina hi boldau hen nati loubeh ding ahi,” ati.
\v 30 Pharaoh angsung'a kon'in Mose apotdoh tan, thousi jouse akitolmang helna dingin aga tao tan ahi.
\v 31 Pakaiyin Mose taona asanpeh tan, Pharaoh akon, anungjui ho leh amite ho jousea kon'in, thousi vaibong abonchan akitolmang tan, khatcha jeng jong akimudoh tapon ahi.
\v 32 Ahinlah angaiya bangin Pharaoh lungthim atah kit tan ahileh, Israel mipi asoldoh deh tapoi.
\c 9
\s1 Egypt Mite Gancha Thigamna
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose thupeh aneijin,“Pharaoh heng'a chekit inlang ajah a hiti hin seijin. Hiche hi ahi Hebrew mite Pakai, Pathen'in asei chu: Kamite che'u henlang, Keima kin gabol uhen.
\v 2 Na soldoh louva Israel mite hi na umsah jing dinga ahile,
\v 3 na loujaova na gancha jouse na sakolte, sangante, sangongsao te, gancha hon, kelngoite leh na kelchate chung'a gamna hise kahin lansah ding thigam kei ding ahiuve, ati.
\v 4 Ahinlah Pakaiyin Isrrael te gancha ho leh Egypt mite gancha ho chung'a chom khenna ahin sem ding, Israel mite ganchaho vang chu khatcha jong thilou ding ahi!
\v 5 “Pakaiyin hiche gamna hise ahin lansah ding ahitai. Aman aseije jing nikho teng gamsung pumpia ahin lansah ding ahi.”
\v 6 Pakaiyin aseidoh bangin aboltai. Ajing jingkah in Egypt mite gancha athigam hel tan, ahinlah Israel mite gancha vang chu khatcha jong athi hihbeh jeng'e.
\v 7 Thilsoh umchan dol khol chil dingin Pharaoh in asohte ho chu asoltan ahile, Israel mite gancha ho chu khat cha jeng jong athi pon ahi! Amavang Pharaoh lung thim chu angaiya bangin atah jing nalaiyin* aman mipi ho chu asol doh dehpon ahi.
\s1 Egypt Gamsung'a Uilut Natna
\p 
\v 8 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose leh Aaron heng'a aseijin, “Lhum sung'a kon'in vutdi tampi kiham lhon'in, hichu Pharaoh mitmu chang tah a Mose'n vanlam'a athe tou ding ahi,” ati.
\v 9 “Egypt gamsung pumpi chu vutvai nelsel chun alodim jeng ding, chuteng mihem chung hile gancha chung hile uilut natna huoisen alhunden jeng diu ahi,” ati.
\v 10 “Chuin amanin jong lhumsung'a kon'in vutdi akiham lhonin, Pharaoh angsung'a ading lhon tai,” Pharaoh in avet jing laiyin, Mose'n vutdi chengse chu vanlam angan athetou le, vutdi nel chun gampumpi alodim jeng tan mihem le gancha ho chung’a uilut natna hoise alang tai. \x + \xo 9:10 \xt Rev 16:2\x*
\v 11 Egypt gam’a doichoiya thilbol ho chung'a jong achutan Mose angsung'a ading ngam tapouve, ajeh chu uilut natna hoise chun amaho leh Egypt mite jouse alhun den jeng ahitai.
\v 12 Ahinlah Pakaiyin Pharaoh lungthim asutah nalaijin, “Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseidohsa bangin, Pharaoh in ngai nahsah in anei hih laiye.”
\s1 Egypt Gamsung'a Gielchang
\p 
\v 13 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Jingkah matah in thouvin Pharaoh angsung'a ga dingin lang, ajah a seijin. Hebrew mite Pakai Pathen'in hiti hin aseije: “Kamite soldoh tan, keima kin agabol na ding uvin.”
\v 14 “Na soldoh louva ahile, keiman natna hoise kahin lansah be nahlai ding nangma le nanung juiho chule namite chung'a kahin lansah cheh ding, chuteng nangman keima Pakai tailou leiset a Pathen dang aumpoi ti nahin hetdoh ding ahi,” ati.
\v 15 “Tu jenga jong keiman ka khut kalhan jah a nangma le namite chung'a gamna hoise ka lansah a leiset chung'a hi ka suhmang hel jeng thei nahiye.”
\v 16 “Ahinlah keiman leiset pumpia ka thaneina ka musah bou nahin hichu leiset pumpia kithe jal ding ahi.” \x + \xo 9:16 \xt Rm 9:17\x*
\v 17 “Ahinlah hicheng jouse nungin jong nangma leh nangma na kichoisang gunset in, kamite na soldoh hih laiye.”
\v 18 “Jing nikho tuphat dontah le keiman gelchang nasatah Egypt gamsung'a imatih channa analha khaloulai chu kahin lhahsah ding ahiye.”
\v 19 “Kino tan! Na loujaova gancha ho jouse hoitup dingin namite sol loijin, achuti louva ahile hitobang gelchang ahung kheh teng loujaova mihem hihen gancha hijongleh aki dalha chan chu gelchang'in ase a thi jeng ding ahi,” ati.
\v 20 Pharaoh nungjuiho mi phabep chu Pakaiyin hitia asei jeh chun akicha tauve. Amaho acheloi jun loujaova gancha ho leh asohte ho'u chu aga puilut tauvin ahi.
\v 21 Ahinlah Pakai thusei ija sep louse vang chun aloujao dung uva kihong tah in gancha alha thang nalai uve.
\v 22 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Egypt gamsung loujao tin cheng'a gelchang ahung kheh a mihem ahin gancha ahin chule loujaova thingphung jouse hihen lang, Egypt gamsung pumpia thil um jouse ase khahna dingin vanlam nganlang na khut lhang jah tan,” tin aseitai.
\v 23 Chuin Mose'n jong vanlam asang'in atenggol chu agah jahdoh jeng le, Pakaiyin vanthamjol aki thinsah in gelchang ahung khetan, leiset chung geijin meikong ahung lenglha tan, Egypt gam pumpia Pakaiyin gelchang goju toh kibangchet in akhehsah tan ahi.
\v 24 Imatih chan a jong hitobang gelchang chu Egypt gamsunga ana khe khalou lai ahin, tanglou hel'in gelchang chu akhe tan meikou apahlha jengin ahi. \x + \xo 9:24 \xt Rev 8:7; 16:21\x*
\v 25 Hitobang gelchang chun Egypt gamsung pumpi alodim lhajeng tan chule loujaova umphot gancha hihen mihem hijongleh aum jouse chu asep lhu jeng tan, gamsunga thingphung jouse jong asep thang deh tan ahi.
\v 26 Goshen mun Israel mite chenna mun bou chu ahoidoh tan ahi.
\v 27 Hitia thil aso phat chun, Pharaoh in jong mi asol loijin Mose leh Aaron agakou sah tan hiti hin aseiye, “Tun vang keima chonse kahitai,” tin kilhanna aneiyin “Pakai hi thudih tanpa ahin, keima le kamite kadih tapouve,” ati.
\v 28 Pakai henga nei taopeh lhon tan, ajeh chu vanthamjol aging jeng jung'e! Gelchang nasatah in akhe jing nalaijin ahi. Ka gimval tauve. Keiman na soldoh tauving'e; um jong umsot tahih un, ati.
\v 29 Mose'n adonbut in, “Ahi le aphai.” Khopi sung hi ka dalhah lhah leh keima jong Pakai heng'a ka tao ding ahi. Vanthamjol gin hung thip ding, gelchang khe jong hung tang jeng ding, nangman jong leiset pumpi hi Pakaiya ahi ti nahet doh ding ahi,” ati.
\v 30 “Ahinlah keiman kahe jing nalaije, nangma leh nasoh ten tuchan'in Pakai na ging hih lai uve,” ati.
\v 31 Hiti chun gamsung'a Phaipheng jouse leh sakol chang abonchan amangthah hel jeng tai, sakol chang chu avui ado laitah ahin chule phaipheng chu ahung don doh laitah ahiye.
\v 32 Hiche lah achun suhlou chang leh butun chang vang ahoidoh nai, ajeh chu suhlou chang leh butun chang chu aduo aum loulai phat ana hiye.
\v 33 Chuin Mose jong Pharaoh angsung khopi dalhan achetai. Pakai lam asang'in ataovin ahile, vanthamjol kithin le gelchang khe chu atang jeng tan, leiset pumpia gojuh jeng jong atang hel tan ahi.
\v 34 Pharaoh in jong gojuh, van kithin, leh gelchang kheh akitang tai ti ahin hetdoh phat in ama le anungjui ho achonse kit tauvin, angaiya bangin Pharaoh lungthim atah kit tai.
\v 35 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a ana seidoh sa bangin Pharaoh lungthim angaiya bangin atah kittan, Pharaoh in jong Israel mite asoldoh deh poi.
\c 10
\s1 Egypt Gamsung'a Khaokho te
\p 
\v 1 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Pharaoh heng'a chekit inlang, ga seikit tan. Keiman ama leh asohte ho lungthim ka suhtah ahin, melchihna hicheng jouse hi kakilah sah ding ahi,” ati.
\v 2 “Chule nangman jong na chapa te leh natupate jah a ichan geija kagim sah uva chule melchihna tampi kamu sah uve ti na jahsah theina diuva kasei ahiye. Nangho jengin jong keima hi Pakai kitipa chu kahi ti nahet doh jeng diu ahi,” ati.
\v 3 Mose leh Aaron jong Pharaoh heng'a ache lhonin asei lhon tai, “Hebrew mite Pakai, Pathen'in hiti hin aseiye: Itih chan ka-angsung'a kun ding da nahi tam? Keima kin agabolna ding uvin, kamite soldoh tan.
\v 4 Nanop louva ahile, vetan! Jing nikho tengleh na gamsung'a khaokho te kahin lansah ding ahi.
\v 5 Gam pumpi alodim soh uva tol lham jong na muthei louding ahi. Gelchang'in akhehlih lou amoh chengse khaokho ten aneh gamhel diu, loujaova keh thingphung ho jouse jong anehchai kei ding'u ahiye.
\v 6 Nangma insung hihen nasohte insung hijongleh Egypt gam insung jouse ahin lodim sohhel jeng diu, hiche tobang thilsoh gimnei hi napu napateu khang'a pat na gamsung uva anaum khalou lai ahi, tin ahenga agasei lhon tai, chuin Mose jong Pharaoh angsung'a kon'in apotdoh tan ahi.
\v 7 Pharaoh sohte ho jong ahung uvin Pharaoh heng'a asei tauve. “Amapa hin itih chan lom lom eiho dinga hahsatna alhunsah ding hitam? Mipi ho hi che uva a Pathen kin abolna diuvin soltan! Egypt mite pihi jou le nal'a mangthah gam ding ahi tauve ti na hetdoh hih laiyem?”
\v 8 Chuin Mose leh Aaron chu Pharaoh heng'a dingin ahin puilut kit tauvin. Pharaoh in jong amani jah a aseiyin, “cheuvin lang na Pakai leh na Pathen kin gabol tauvin. Ahile koipen mong hi nahiuvem ache ding?” tin amani chu adong tan ahi.
\v 9 Mose'n adonbut in, “Ateh akhang, ka chapa te hou ahin ka chanute hou jaona a khatcha kidalha louding kahiuve. Ka kelngoi jouseu leh gancha jouse aboncha kapui sohkei diu, chule keihon kut chu alouthei louva kagabol teitei ding'u ahi,” ati.
\v 10 Pharaoh in jong aseijin, “Keiman nangho nacha sen gei uva ka soldoh tha ngei ngeija ahile Pakai umpina chu chang un! Na lungthim sung lhkonna lungthim phalou na keng lhon'e.
\v 11 Hiche vang chu hithei louhel ding ahi! Nangho lah a Pasal chengse cheuvin lang na Pakaiyu kin gabol tauvin, hichu natup tenten uva hilou ham?” Chuin Pharaoh in aleng in a konin ahin nodoh lhon tan ahi.
\s1 Khaokhopite Alan
\p 
\v 12 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Egypt gamsung pumpia khaokhopite alanna dingin na khut jahdoh jeng tan. Egypt gamsung'a hamphung gelchang in akhehlih moh chengse aboncha aneh gamset diu ahi,” ati.
\v 13 Mose’n atenggol chu Egypt gamsung pumpi chungvum a ajahdoh jeng tan ahile, hiche nikho chun Pakaiyin Egypt gamsung pumpi nilhum kei leh khovah hel'in huiphalou solama kon'in tanglouvin anun sah tai. Jingkah in solam akon huijin khaokho te ahon hon'in ahin polut tauvin ahi.
\v 14 Chule Egypt gam pumpi chu khaokho ten alosoh hel jeng tan, hitobang'a gamsunga khaokho te chu imatih channa ana um kha loulai ahiye. \x + \xo 10:14 \xt Rev 9:2,3\x*
\v 15 Khaokho ten gamsung pumpi alodimlha tauvin ahile mu athimlha jeng tai. Gelchang in akheh moh chengse gam leiset a thingphung jouse jong anemang hel tauvin, Egypt gamsung pumpi thingphung chule hamphung abonchan ado khat jeng cha jong um louvin khaokho ten anechai hel jeng tauve.
\v 16 Chuphat in Pharaoh in jong asohte ho asol loiyin, Mose leh Aaron aga kousah un, hiti hin aseiye. “Keiman na Pakai leh nangni chung'a chonset phat louna kabol khatai,” ati.
\v 17 “Ka chonsetna nei ngaidam lhon'in, Pakai heng'a nei taopeh teitei lhon tan, hiche thigamna hoise hi keima angsung'a kon'in tolmang jeng lhon tan,” ati.
\v 18 Mose jong Pharaoh angsung'a kon'in a kondoh in Pakai heng'a aga tao tai,
\v 19 Pakaiyin nisolam a kon'in hui hattah ahin nunsah in ahile, hiche huipi chun khaokho te jouse twikhanglen dung laiya alhoh lut sohhel jeng tai. Egypt gamsung pumpia khaokho te chu khat jeng cha jong aum tahih hel jengin ahi.
\v 20 Ahinlah Pakaiyin Pharaoh lungthim asutah jing nalaijin, Pharaoh in jong mipi ho chu asol doh hih laiye.
\s1 Egypt Gamsunga Muthim
\p 
\v 21 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Nakhut jah inlang vanlam sang tem in, Egypt gamsung pumpi muthim'in alo sohhel jeng ding ahi,” ati.
\v 22 Mose'n jong Pakaiyin athupeh bangin vanlam asan jeng'a ahile, Egypt gamsung pumpi nithum sung mu athim lha jeng tan, ahi. \x + \xo 10:22 \xt Labu 105:28; Rev 16:10\x*
\v 23 Hiche phat sung chun khat le khat akimu thei tapouvin, koimacha jeng jong pot le theilou ahitai. Ahinlah Israel chate chenna mun vang chu khovah in aumpi jing uve.
\v 24 Ajonan, Pharaoh in jong Mose akoukit tai. “Cheuvin lang Pakai kin gabol tauvin,” ati. “Na chate'u kipui jun lang, ahinlah na kelngoi hon teu vang na dalhah ding'u ahi,” ati.
\v 25 Mose'n adonbut in, “Hichu hithei him him ponte. Ka gancha te'u chu nei puisah tei teiju angaije, ajeh chu ka Pakai uleh ka Pathen angsung'a kilhaina a ka manchah ding'u ahi, ati.”
\v 26 “Ka gancha teu aboncha, ka pui teitei diu ahiye; khat jeng cha jong ka dalhah thei louhel diu ahi. Ajeh chu ka ganchate'u lah a konna hi keihon Pakai angsung'a kilhaina'a katdoh dinga ka lhendoh cheh cheh diu ahi. Chule amun ka lhun kahse uva itilam dol'a Pakai kin kabol diu ham ti kahe chen nai pouve,” ati.
\v 27 Ahinlah Pakaiyin Pharaoh lungthim chu khatvei asutah kit nalaijin, Pharaoh in jong mipi ho chu asoldoh hih laiye.
\v 28 Chuin Pharaoh jong apeng jah jeng tan, Mose henga aseiyin, “Ka angsunga kon'in potdoh jengin!” ati. “Keiman nangma ka gih nahiye. Avel'a nei hung kinung mupi kitthei louhel ding ahi! Nei kimupi kit ngai ngaiya ahile hiche nikhoa chu nathi jeng ding ahi,” ati.
\v 29 Mose'n adonbut in, “Apha jenge,” “Avella ka kimaitopi tah louding nahiye,” ati.
\c 11
\s1 Egypt Gamsung'a Gamna Hoise Achaina
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Keiman Egypt gamsung leh Pharaoh chung'a ka hin lhunsah ding hoise khat akivat nalaije. Hiche hi aso chai chai tengleh, Pharaoh in agamsung dalha dinga nahin no jeng ding'u ahitai,” ati.
\v 2 “Israel mite heng'a seipeh inlang, ama ama cheh in aheng akom Egypt mite sana dangka akijepna ding uvin kithum cheh tauhen,” ati.
\v 3 (Tun Pakaiyin Israel chate chu Egypt mite mitmun lunglhaina achansah tai. Chule Mose chu Egypt gamsung pumpia amin akithang in, Pharaoh mitmu chang leh mipite mitmun amin che lheh jeng tan ahi.)
\v 4 Chuin Mose'n Pharaoh heng'a aseijin, “Hiche hi Pakaiyin aseiye: “Keiman jankim tah le Egypt mite lungthim kahin suhthou ding ahi.
\v 5 Egypt gamsung'a chapang peng masa jouse, Pharaoh chapa peng masapen ahin, alaltouna a peng masa penpa ahin, a sumbuh laiya changbong goija pang asohnu chapa chan geija abonchauva thigam kei ding, gancha peng masa jouse jong aboncha thisoh hel ding ahiye, ati.
\v 6 Chuteng Egypt gamsung pumpia ka le mao kithong lha ding, ajeh chu hitobang thilsoh gimnei hi imatih channa anaum khalou laiya ahin, avella hung kilah kit talou ding chu ahi.
\v 7 Ahinlah Israel mite vang chu lungmon nan aumpi jing diu, uicha jeng jong hampoh louding ahi. Chuteng Pakaiyin Egypt mite leh Israel mite kikah a ijakai datkhenna asemdoh tai, hichu nang hon na hetdoh cheh ding'u ahi, ati.
\v 8 Chuteng Egypt gam'a na nungjui ho leh nasohte abonchauva keima lam'a hung kipelut ding'u hitia hi asei diu ahi, khaiye! 'Nangma leh nanung juiho abonchauvin hikom'a kon hin potdoh tauvin!' tin aseije atipeh tai. Chuin Mose jong lungphamo tah in Pharaoh angsung'a kon'in achedoh tan ahi.
\v 9 Tun Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Pharaoh in nangma thusei ahin ngailou ding, ahinlah keiman Egypt gamsung'a thil kidang melchihna ka bolbe nahlai ding ahi,” ati.
\v 10 Mose leh Aaron'in jong Egypt gam Pharaoh angsung'a thil kidang melchihna tampi aki lahsah lhon'in, ahinlah Pakaiyin Pharaoh lungthim chu kidang tah in asutah jing nalaijin ahile, Pharaoh in Israel mite chu Egypt gamsung a kon'in ana soldoh hih laiye.
\c 12
\s1 Kalchuh Kut
\p 
\v 1 Israel mite Egypt gam'a aum jing laijun, Pakaiyin Mose leh Aaron heng'a hicheng hi thupeh aneiye: \x + \xo 12:1 \xt Thempu Dan 23:5; Minbu 9:1-5; 28:16; Danbu Ni Na 16:1,2\x*
\v 2 “Tu apat hiche lha hi nangho dinga lha kipatna ahin, kumkhat adia lha kipatna a kisim ding ahitai.
\v 3 Israel te kikhop khomna munpi jouse ah ga seipeh lhon tan. Hiche lhasung nisom alhinni tengleh ama ama cheh in apu apateu insung kai lhah apat, insung khat cheh akon kelngoi khat cheh katdoh dinga ahin kai diu ahiye.
\v 4 Kelngoinou khat kitha dinga insung khat a mijat chu alhom khah a ahile, inneipu le aheng akom'a pa kinopto ding kelngoi nou adol ding chabep khat chu aga kimat lhon ding, amichan cheh in aneh khopset ding kelngoinou khat ding mijat chu phatecha nasim toh lhon ding ahi.
\v 5 “Kelngoinou chu nolna beihel hi ding, kumkhat lhingsa hitei ding, hiche kelngoinou chu kelngoi honlah a konna hihen kelcha honnlah konna hijongleh athah beh mong mong'a na kimat ding'u ahi.”
\v 6 “Hichea manchah ding kelngoinou chu hiche lha nisom leh nili lhinni geija nahen cheh diug'u hichu nilhum lam tengleh Israel kikhom pumpi chun ama ama cheh adia akitha ding'u ahiye.”
\v 7 Gancha kithat thisan chu phabep asodoh diu, hichu kelngoinou thisan a chu in kotpi phung le inkam'a aloinat cheh cheh diu ahi.
\v 8 Hicheni jan teng chule kelngoinou sa chu meiya akihul min uva aneh cheh diu, hichu cholsolou changlhah leh anchekha toh ametha cheh cheh diu ahiye.
\v 9 Hiche sa chu asel puma hihen twija kihonminsa hijongleh koima chan naneh thei louhel diu ahi. Sa pumpi aluchang le akeng chule asung jouse jaona meiya na kihulmin tho uva naneh cheh diu ahi.
\v 10 Sa amoh neocha jong jingkah channa na khovah sah louhel diu ahi. Akinelou taphot chu jingkah masanga meiya na govam jeng ding'u ahiye.”
\v 11 “Hicheng hi sa naneh teng ule najui cheh ding'u ahiye: nangma cheh na kivon lhingsel uva, nakeng chot ho'u na kisi cheh diu, chule nakhut uva tenggol na kiphu sohkei ding'u ahi. Chuteng naneh khom sohkei diu hichu Pakaiya dia Kalchuh Kut ahiye.
\v 12 Hiche jan teng chule keiman Egypt gamsung kahin jotpa a mihem leh gancha aboncha apeng lha masa jouse kasuh gamhel ding ahi. Chule Egypt gamsung'a milim doi kisemthu jouse chung'a jong thu katan ding ahiye, ajeh chu keima Pakai kahi!.
\v 13 Ahinlah nangho jouse dinga hiche thisan kiso chu melchihna hung kilah tading, keiman Egypt gam pumpi kahin suhmang ding, hiche thisan chu kahin mudoh jiteng keiman nangho jouse chung'a natna hoise hung lang thei jouse a konna kaven doh ding nahiuve.
\v 14 Hiche nikho hi nangho dinga hetjingna nikhoa pang jeng ding ahitai. Hichu kumsih chule akhang akhang'a Pakaiya dia kut nikho ahi ti na geldoh jing ding'u ahiye. Na khang lhumkei uva chonna dan hitia nanit jing diu ahitai. \x + \xo 12:14 \xt Potdohbu 23:15; 34:18; Thempu Dan 23:6-8; Minbu 28:17-25; Danbu Ni Na 16:3-8\x*
\v 15 Nisagi sung'a cholsolou changlhah jeng naneh ding'u ahi. Nisagi alhinni tengleh nangma insung cheh a chol um jouse pamlamma na paidoh sohkei ding'u ahi. Nalah uva koi tobang khat chun hiche cholsolou changlhah, nisagi lhinnia pat naneh khah ngeingei uva ahile, ama chu Israel mite lah a konna kisumang jeng ding ahi.
\v 16 Kut kipat nikho masa penni teng khompi len khat nanei uva, nisagi alhinni teng jongleh khompilen theng khatma nanei diu ahi. Hiche nikho teni hi atumbeh a nanit cheh diu, amichan'in aneh khop ding nabol peh teitei ding'u ahi.
\v 17 “Hiche hi Cholsolou changlhah kut a naman diu ahiye, ajeh chu hiche nikhoa hi keiman nangho Egypt gamsung'a konna kahin puidoh nau na geldoh jing diu, nakhang lhumkei uva nangho jousen hiche nikho chu chonna dan ahi tia nanit jom jing ding'u ahi,” ati.
\v 18 Lhamasa nisom le nili lhin nikho nilhah lam tengleh na boncha uva hiche cholsolou changlhah chu naneh pan diu ahi
\v 19 Nisagi sungse'a vang chu nangma nangma insung cheh a, chol sosa changlhah khat jeng cha jong kilah louding ahiye. Kholjin mi ahin agamsung cheng den miho hijongleu chun cholsosa changlhah nekha tapou chu, Israel khompi a konna kisumang jeng ding ahi.
\v 20 Hiche phatsung hin amitakip in cholsosa changlhah kiti phot naneh louhel ding'u ahiye. Ajeh chu cholsolou changlhah jeng naneh diu ahi.”
\v 21 Chuin Mose'n jong Israel sung'a upaho jouse akou khom in aheng uvah aseipeh tai, “Cheuvin, nangma cheh insung ding kelngoinou gaki kaiyun lang, chule Kalchuh Kut a dingin kithauvin.”
\v 22 “Khutsilna kong'a gan thisan chu koiyun. Chule hichu hyssop nado phabep lauvin lang dekot uvin. Hyssop chu lauvin lang thisan achun kotpi khom teni ahin kotpi chunglah inkam a chun loinat sohkei uvin. Jing khovah kahsea koima chan hichu akallhah thei louding ahi.
\v 23 Ajeh chu Pakaiyin Egypt mite jouse sugam'a hung ding kahi, chuteng Pakaiyin kotpi chung lah a thisan kiloinat ho chu amu ding, hitia chu asuhgam ding hojal a chu hiche insung chu apeldoh ding ahiye.” \x + \xo 12:23 \xt Heb 11:28\x*
\v 24 “Geldoh jing'un, thupeh hichengse hi nangho jouse ding leh nachateu khang geija chonna dan ahi tia najui jing ding'u ahi.
\v 25 Pakaiyin nangho peh dinga akitepna sa gamsung nalhun teng ujongleh hiche chonna dan hi najui jing diu ahi.
\v 26 Chule hiche chonna hi na chate uvin 'Ipi dinga kibol ham?' ti nahin doh ding'u ahi.
\v 27 Nang hon jong na donbut uva, “Hiche chonna dan hi Pakaiyaa dia gantha kilhaina ahin chule Pakaiyin Egypt mite ana thagam lai chun Aman Israel mite in ho chu ana kalchuhji e,'” tia na seipeh ding'u ahi. Chuin Mose'n thupeh hichengse chu achai phat in mipi jouse Pakai angsung'a akunlha sohkei uvin chibai aboh tauve.
\v 28 Pakaiyin Mose leh Aaron athupeh bangin Israel mite'n jong abol tauvin ahi.
\s1 Potdoh Kipatna
\p 
\v 29 Chule hiche Jan khangkim chun Pakaiyin Egypt gamsung'a naocha peng masa jouse, Pharaoh chapa apeng masapen alaltouna toupa a kipat, akimvella cheng asohpa chapa peng masapen ahin, chule gancha peng masa jouse athat gamhel tan ahi. \x + \xo 12:29 \xt Potdohbu 4:22,23\x*
\v 30 Jankim laijin Pharaoh, asohte ho chule Egypt mite abonchauvin athou doh tauvin, Egypt gamsung pumpia ka le mao awgin akithong sohhel tai. Ajeh chu intin cheng'a mi thina lou umlouva ahitai.
\v 31 Jankim laijin Pharaoh in Mose le Aaron aga kousah tauvin, “Ka mite dalhan che tauvin chule Israel mite kipuijin che tauvin! Nei tepna bangun cheuvin lang Pakai kin chu gabol jeng tauvin.
\v 32 Na seima bangin na kelngoi jouseu leh na gancha jouse'u abonchan kipui unlang, che tauvin, nei dalhah ding tah jeh un keima jong phatthei neichan lhon ding ahiye,” ati.
\v 33 Egypt miten abonchauvin Israel te dingin akisaboi lheh jeng tauvin, Egypt gamsung'a konna Israel mite soldoh loiding lunggel akeng tauvin, ama hon “Keiho ka boncha uva thigam ding kahi tauve!” tin asei uve.
\v 34 Israel mite'n jong changbong neldi anei jouse'u aki hamkhom tauvin. Changbong ameh nau lhengkam jouse jao nan poh dingin akigot cheh tauvin ahi.
\v 35 Mose'n athupeh bang bang uvin, Israel mite'n jong abol tauvin ahi; Egypt mite a kon'in sana le dangka kijepna ding jouse akithum doh gam tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 12:35 \xt Potdohbu 3:21,22\x*
\v 36 Pakaiyin Israel mite chu Egypt mite mitmun alunglhai sah sohkeijun ahile, Egypt miten jong anei chasun uchu itcha louhel lin ana pesohkei uve. Egypt mite haona jouse toh akon tauvin ahi!
\v 37 Hiche jan chun Israel mite Rameses khopia kon'in Succoth lam'a dingin akipat doh tauvin ahi. Numei chapang simtha louvin keng lamma che pasal jat mong chu sang jagup alhing uve.
\v 38 Amaho ahiuvin chule miphuh miphah, gancha ho, kelngoi hon tampi le gancha hon tampi jaonan aki tol tauve.
\v 39 Egypt gamsung'a aum lai uva kisem changbong chu alhon lhon'in akiken jiuvin ahi. Egypt gam'a kino tah a kisoldoh ahijeh uvin ama hon changlhah chu chol aso man tah louvu, chule ama cheh neh ding jeng jong ana kigon man tapouve.
\v 40 Israel mite chu Egypt gamsung'a kum jali le kum somthum ana cheng uve. \x + \xo 12:40 \xt Semtilbu 15:13; Gal 3:17\x*
\s1 Kelchuh Kut Dan
\p 
\v 41 Chuin, Kum jali le kum somthum lhinin Pakai thaneijin Israel mite chu Egypt gam'a kon'in ahin puidoh tauvin ahi.
\v 42 Hiche jan chun Pakaiyin Israel mite Egypt gam'a konna ahin puidoh ding kitepna aneiyin ahi. Hiche jan hi Pakai dinga mong ahin, hijeh a chu Israel mite'n akhang akhang uva anit jing diu ahiye.
\v 43 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose le Aaron heng'a aseijin, “Hichengse hi Kalchuh Kut kibol ding dan ahi. Kalchuh Kut ankong hi kholjin min anehthei louhel ding ahi.
\v 44 Amavang hiche mihem chu sum'a kichodohsa le cheptan sa ahile aneh jeng thei ahinai.
\v 45 Kholjin maimai le tha a kila a kigoi mihon aneh louding ahi.
\v 46 Insung cheh a Kalchuh Kut an chu kine ding ahi. Inpolam'a naneh theilou diu chule agu jong khatcha na suhboh lou diu ahi. \x + \xo 12:46 \xt Minbu 9:12; Jn 19:36\x*
\v 47 Hiche hi Isreal khompi jousen phatecha anit cheh diu ahi.
\v 48 “Gamdang mikhat tou ahung kholjin khah a Pakai Kalchuh Kut a ajaonom'a ahile pasal kiti phot chun achep kitan cheh uhen, chuteng Kalchuh Kut chu anailut uva aneh thei ding chuteng amaho chu Israel mite bang'a lhathei ding ahiye.
\v 49 Hiche thupeh hi amitakip ading ahin, agammi Israel te hihen gamdang mi hijongleh dan khat a um cheh ding ahi,” ati.
\v 50 Pakaiyin Mose le Aaron athupeh bangin Israel mite'n jong abol sohkei uve.
\v 51 Hiche nikho chun Pakaiyin Israel mite Egypt gamsung a kon'in galsat sepaite bangi nahin puidoh tauvin ahi.
\c 13
\s1 Naopeng Masa Thensona
\p 
\v 1 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin,
\v 2 “Israel mite lah a apeng lhamasa phot kaheng'a na todoh dingu ahi. Mihem hihen gancha hijongleh aboncha keija ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 13:2 \xt Minbu 3:13; Lk 2:23\x*
\v 3 “Mose'n mipi ho heng'a aseijin, “Hiche nikho hi imatih channa geldoh jing uvin Egypt gam'a nasoh chan nauva konna nahung kitoldoh nikhou chu ahiye. Tunin Pakaiyin aban thahat panin nahin puidoh tauve. (Geldoh jingun, cholsolou changlhah jeng naneh ding'u ahi),” ati.
\v 4 Hiche nikho hi phalbi matah hichu Abid* nikhoa hi na boncha uva chamlhat tah a na potdoh sohkei ding'u ahiye.
\v 5 Pakaiyin nangho chan dia napu napa teu heng'a akitepna Canaan gam mite, Hit mite, Amor mite, Hivi mite chule Jebus mite chenna (khoiju le bongnoi lonna gamsung'a nahin puilut tengu leh hiche lhasung'a chu nangman jong hiche chonna dan chu nabol ding ahi), ati.
\v 6 Nisagi sung'a cholsolou changlhah jeng naneh diu ahi. Nisagi lhinni tengleh vang Pakai heng'a kut khat nabol diu ahi.
\v 7 Nisagi sung'a cholsolou changlhah jeng bou naneh thei diu ahi. Tahbeh in hiche nikho sagi sungsea hi na gamsung kimvel'u aboncha koiman cholsosa changlhah kiti toh naum khom louhel diu ahi.”
\v 8 “Nisagi lhinni tengleh na chate hou heng'a nasei uva, ‘Egypt gamsung'a keima kaum laiya Pakaiyin hiche melchihna hi eibol peh ahiye,’ nati ding ahi.
\v 9 “Hiche golvahna hi melchihna khat a pang jing ding, chule namit jeng a jong hetjingna a pang ding, hiche kihilna hi na kamsung'a navop jing ding ahi: Pakaiyin nangma aban thahat pan'a Egypt gamsung'a konna nahin puidoh ahi,” ati.
\v 10 Hijeh chun hiche golvahna hi kumseh angai ngaija bang'a nabol jing dingu ahi.
\v 11 “Hiche chonna dan hi Pakaiyin khangluija pat a kitepna anei bang'a hichu aguilhun kahsea nabol jom jing diu, nanghon Canaan mite chenna nalhun teng uleh nabol diu,
\v 12 hijeh a chu Israel sung'a konna pasal pengdoh masapen mihem hihen gancha hijongleh Pakaiya dia napeh doh jing diu ahi, hichu Pakaiya ahi. \x + \xo 13:12 \xt Potdohbu 34:19,20; Lk 2:23\x*
\v 13 Hiti achu sangan nou penglha masa chan chu kelngoi nouva nalhat diu, nalhat tah lou ujong le sangan nou ho chu angong chang na hekelep diu ahi. Chule na chapa te lah a apeng masa chan nale lhatdoh cheh cheh diu ahi.”
\v 14 “Chule khonung teng, na chapan thil umchan dol nahin doh ding, 'Hiche ho jouse hi ipi jeh pentah a kibol ham?' Nangman hitia hi na donbut ding, 'Egypt gam'a soh ichan lai uva Pakaiyin aban thahat panna mipi jouse leh gancha aboncha eihin puidoh u ahiye, nati diu ahi, ati.
\v 15 Pharaoh ana lungtah lheh jengin ahile, Egypt gam'a konna ipotdoh diu chu ana phal tapon, ajonan Pakaiyin Egypt gamsung'a pasal peng masa jouse leh gancha jouse abonchan athat chaikeiye. Hijeh a chu tua hi keiman Pakaiya dia kilhaina kasem ahin hibang'a chu keiman ka chapa te lah a apeng masa pen chan chu lhatdohna kaneiji ahi.' tia na seipeh ding ahi, ati.
\v 16 Hiche chondan hi nakhut teni ahin, namit teni chule na nahlhong geija melchihna thil'a navop jing ding ahiye. Hichu Pakaiyin aban thahat panna Egypt gam'a konna nahin puidoh hetjingna ahi.”
\s1 Twisan Dung Agalkaiju
\p 
\v 17 Ajonan Pharaoh in Israel mite ahin soldoh tan ahile, gamtepna lam lhunna naicha ahi vang chun, Pathen'in Philistine galbol ho jeh chun lampia ahinpui pouvin ahi. Pathen'in aseiye, “Kamite hon gal tohkha ta le alung heikhao vintin Egypt lam'a kile ding ahiuve,” ati.
\v 18 Pathen'in amaho chu gamthip lah a ahinpui leuvin, Twipi San* lam mun chu ahin jon tauvin ahi. Israel mite chu galsat mi bangin ahung kitol tauvin ahi.
\v 19 Mose'n jong Joseph gu le chang ahin pon, ajeh chu Joseph in hiche thulhahna hi ana neijin, hiti hin aseiye, “Pathen nangho kithopia hung jing ding ahi. Aman nangho nahin panpi teng ule, hiche kagu kachang hi nahin poh ding'u ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 13:19 \xt Semtilbu 50:25; Joshua 24:32\x*
\v 20 Israel miten Succoth mun ahin dalha uvin gamthip lah Etham kiti mun ahunglhung tauvin hiche mun a chun ngahmun akisem tauve.
\v 21 Pakaiyin amite chu malam'a alhonpi jingin, Sunteng meibol khompi bangin alhonpi uvin, jan teng meivah khompi bangin alhonpi jiuve.
\v 22 Pakaiyin amite dalha louvin meilhang meivah in aumpi jing uve.
\c 14
\s1 Twipi Sen Apal Galkai
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a thupeh hicheng hi aneijin:
\v 2 “Israel mite heng'a seiyin nung lam'a akihei uva Pi-hahiroth le Migdol kikah san-dung chule Baalzephon gal lamma ngahmun asem nai diuvin aheng uvah seipeh un.
\v 3 Chutileh Pharaoh in hitia hi angaito ding, 'Israel mite alungdong tauvin, suhna ding helouvin gamthip noija akitol le tauve!' ati ding ahi.
\v 4 “Hitia chu keiman avel'a Pharaoh lungthim ka suhtah ding, aman nangho nung ahin del ding ahi.* Ajeh chu keiman ka gontupsa ahitai, Pharaoh le agalsat mite chung'a ka loupina kakilah sah ding ahi. Chuteng Egypt mite'n keima Pakai kahi ahin hetdoh diu ahitai!” Aheng uva kiseipeh bangin Israel mite'n hiche munna chun ngahmun akisem tauvin ahi.
\v 5 Pharaoh lengpa le asohte ho heng'a Israel mite ajam tauve tithu alhun phat in, Pharaoh leh asohte lungthim akikhel kit tan, “Ipi khat ibol uva Israel mite asoh chan nauva konna jam gam'u hitam?” tin asei uve.
\v 6 Pharaoh in jong agalsat miho le sakol kangtalai ho chu agontup sah loijin ahi.
\v 7 Pharaoh in sakol-kangtalai hatcheh jagup le Egypt gamsung'a sakol kangtalai dang ho jouse abonchan vaihom mitampi chu atou tauvin ahi.
\v 8 Pakaiyin Pharaoh kiti Egypt lengpa lungthim asutah nalaijin ahile, aman jong Egypt gamsung dalha a jam Israel mite nung chu adel tan ahi.
\v 9 Egypt mite'n jong Israel te chu Pharaoh in galsat miho thaneina lhingset apen anung adel tauvin a sakol jouseu leh sakol-kangtalai jouse, sakol touthem jouse le agalsat mijouse abonchauvin adimlha tauvin ahi.
\v 10 Pharaoh in jong Israel mite umna lam anailut jep phat in ama hon Pharaoh lam chu avetou uvin, hichun ama hon anunglam uva Egypt mite ahung kitol chu amu tauve. Abonchauvin Pakai heng'a atao uvin,
\v 11 Mose heng'a aseiyun, “Ipi dinga gamthip noija hi thigam dinga neihin puidoh u hitam? Egypt a chu keiho dinga lhanmun lhingset uma hilou ham? Ka chung uva hi ipi nabola nahi hitam? Ipi dinga Egypt nei dalhah sah uham?
\v 12 Egypt gamsung kaum lai uva chu hitobang hi soh tei ding ahi tia ka seiju hilou ham? 'Nei dalha jeng tauvin! Egypt mite khut noija soh in umkit tau vinge. Hiche lai munna ka thigam sang uvin Egypt mite khut noija soh a kaum'u apha joi!'” tin asei tauve.
\v 13 Ahinlah Mose'n mipi heng'a aseijin, “Kicha hihhel un, dingdet jingun veuvin, tunia hi Pakaiyin na huhdoh diu ahiye. Chule tunia kipat avel'a Egypt mite namukit tah lou diu ahi.
\v 14 Pakai ama tah in nangho gal asat ding ahi. Nangho umthim beh un,” ati.
\v 15 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “ Ipi dinga kaheng’a kap a nahim? Mipiho malamma akitolna diuvin seijin!
\v 16 Na tenggol jan doh tem in twikhanglen chung vum achun domin. Twipi chu sukhen'in chutileh Israel mite twikhanglen lailung tolgo lah a chu kijot ding'u ahi.
\v 17 Chule keiman Egypt mite lungthim kasuh tah ding, ama hon Israel mite thagamna ding angaito diu ahi, chuteng asakol kangtalai jouseu, asakol tounau nangho that gam dinga hungkon ahiuvin, abonchauva keiman ka thaneina aheng uva kakilah sah ding ahi.
\v 18 Egypt mite ma-sang'a kaloupina kakimusah ding ahijoi, chuteng keima Pakai kahi ahin hetdoh diu ahi!” ati.
\v 19 Chuin Pakai vantil'in Israel mite ahin lhonpi'n, mipi masang lam'a meilom chu nunglam joh a ahung tan ahi.
\v 20 Chuin meilom chu Israel mite le Egypt mite kah a ahung umtai. Mu athimlha jeng tan, meilom jong meikong akisoh in kho ahung thim tan ahile, jan khovah keijin Israel mite chu Egypt miten ahin delpha tapouvin ahi.
\v 21 Chuin Mose'n atenggol chu Twipi San dung vumma ajah doh jeng'a ahile, chuin Pakaiyin twikhanglen dung chu solama kon hui ahung nungin ahin semhoh tan ahi. Jan khovah keijin huijin twikhanglen chu asemin, twikhanglen jong aki khen'in tol lham golai ahung umdoh tan ahi.
\v 22 Chuphat in Israel mite abonchauvin tolgo laiya chun akitol'un alang alang'a bang bangin twi chu akiting tan ahi! \x + \xo 14:22 \xt 1 Crth 10:1,2; Heb 11:29\x*
\v 23 Chuin Egypt mite Pharaoh galsat sakol jouse, sakol kangtalai jouse chule sakol touthem jouse jaona'n twikhanglen lailung'a kitol Israel mite chu adel tauvin ahi.
\v 24 Jingpi ahi phat in Pakaiyin Egypt mite chu meikong leh meilom mangchan ahin vesuh tauvin ahile, chuin Egypt galsat miho chu abonchauvin suhna ding beijin anoh gam tauvin ahi.
\v 25 Pakaiyin akangtalai jouseu abonchan atuhtang gam tan ahile, kangtalai ho chu abonchan akitang den gamtai. Egypt miten jong asei tauvin! “Israel mite angsung'a kon'in jamdoh loiju hite!” ajeh chu “Pakaiyin Israel mite apan pin Egypt mite chung'a gal asat tai!” atiuve.
\v 26 Israel mite agalkai phat uvin, Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Egypt mite twijin ale lonkhum na dingin na tenggol jahdoh kit in, ati.”
\v 27 Nisa ahung sodoh toh ki lhon'in, Pakaiyin athupeh bangin Mose'n twipi chung vumma akhut ajah tan ahile, twipi jong angaija bangin ahung um doh kit tai. Egypt miten hoidoh agouvin, hinlah Pakaijin dillen lah a atollut tauve.
\v 28 Chuin Twi akitol mat kittan, Israel mite nung hindel a Egypt galsat miho le sakol touthem jouse, kangtalai jouse abonchauvin twijin achup gamhel tauvin khat jeng cha jong asohcha tapouvin ahi.
\v 29 Ahinlah Israel mite chu dillen lailung'a tolgo achun akitol uvin, dillen jeng jong ajet aveija bang bangin akisong den jengin ahi.
\v 30 Chu che nikho chun Pakaiyin Israel mite chu Egypt mite khut a konna Israel te ahuhdoh dan chu ahi. Chule Israel mite'n Egypt mite Dillen in achup ho chu amu tauvin ahi.
\v 31 Egypt miten Isreal mite douna anei uva Pakai thahat le natoh kidang amuchen tauvin ahile, Israel mite'n Pakai chu aging tauve. Pakai le alhachapa Mose jong aging tauvin ahi.
\c 15
\s1 Mose Labol
\p 
\v 1 Chuin Mose le Israel mite'n Pakai avahchoijun la asa uve: “Keiman Pakai vahchoila ka sah ding, ajeh chu aman loupitah in gal ajou tai; sakol ahin achung toupa Pakaiyin twikhanglen lailunga aseplut tan ahi.” \x + \xo 15:1 \xt Rev 15:3\x*
\v 2 “Pakai hi kei dinga, ka thahat na le ka vahchoi dinga lomtah ahi; ajeh chu aman galjona eipetai.” Ama hi ka Pathen, ka vahchoi ding ahi, chule kapau Pathen ahin, choiat dinga lom Ama bou ahi! \x + \xo 15:2 \xt Labu 118:14; Isa 12:2\x*
\v 3 “Pakai hi galhattah ahin, ajeh chu amin jong Pakai ahiye!”.
\v 4 “Pharaoh kangtalai jouse le agalsat jouse, Pakaiyin twikhanglen lailunga aseplut tauvin; Pharaoh deitum le alhentum ho abonchauvin Twipi San dunga aseplut gam tauvin ahi”.
\v 5 Twikhanglen kinong in achup gamsoh hel jeng uvin; abonchauvin songtum bangin twinoi lamma a lhalhum gam tauve.
\v 6 “O Pakai nakhut jetlam hi loupi le thahat chungnung ahi. Melmate jeng jong asugam hel tan ahi.
\v 7 Na lalna leh na loupina jalin na melmate na lehkhup jeng e, na lunghanna nasatah in nahin tahlang jitan ahile; abonchauvin meijin changpol akah vamkei bangin akavam sohhel tauve.
\v 8 Nangma husan a kon'in twipi kinong jeng jong alhuh den in ahile atang jeng tai. Chule twikhanglen lailung'a twi kitang jong chu ale chupsoh hel jengin ahi.”
\v 9 “Chuin Melmapa chun hitin aseiye, 'Keiman anung kadel ding ka phah tei ding ahi. Thil kiladoh kale lah ding chule ka deichat bangtah a kakile lah ding ahiye; ka chemjam ka sadoh ding, abonchauva kasat chap jeng ding ahiuve.'
\v 10 Ahinlah nangman na haikhum in ahile, abonchauvin twikhanglen in achup tauve. Twipi hattah lailung'a alhum gam tauvin ahi.
\v 11 “O Pakai, Pathen dang ho jouse lah jeng'a jong koimacha nang kal lhah aumpon, amaho chu imacha toh akite thei deh pouvin, nangma kala koimacha thenna chang ding aum hih e. Loupina leh tijat umtah a thilbol a koiham?
\v 12 Nangman nakhut jetlam na jahdoh in ahile, hichun leiset a melmate avallhum gam tauve.”
\v 13 “Na lungsetna long louvin, na lhatdohsa mite aumpi jingin ahi. Na chena mun geijin na mite nahin puilhung tai.
\v 14 Mitin vaipin hichu ahin jasoh tauvin ahile; Philistine gamsung'a cheng jouse din nat hesoh achang tauve.
\v 15 Edom gamsung'a lamkai kiti phot alung thomhao gamtan; Moab gam'a lamkai jouse jong akithing sohhel tauve. Canaaan gam'a cheng jouse jong alungthoi gam tauve.
\v 17 Nangman namite nahin puilut ding nangma molsang chungvum a chu na tundoh ding ahiye; ajeh chu nangman hiche laimun chu na chenna dinga na tundohsa ahitai, O Pakai nangman mun theng lai jeng jong chu na khut tenia na tundoh ahitai.
\v 18 Pakai hi tonsot tonsot a chungnung chang ahitai!”
\v 19 Ajeh chu Pharaoh sakol kangtalai jouse twikhanglen lailung'a atollut in, Pakai thahat chun achungvum uvah twikhanglen chu alechup sah gam ahitai. Ahinlah Israel chate abonchauvin twikhanglen lailung tolgo lah achun akijot galkai sah tauvin ahi.
\v 20 Chuin Aaron sopinu, themgao Miriam chun akhut a sum-eng behging akilah in numei jouse alamkaijin, behging abengun alam tauve.
\v 21 Chule Miriam chun hiche jaila hi a-oijin ahi: “Pakai vahchoila sau hite, Aman loupitah in gal asat in ajou tai; sakol chung'a toupa le akangtalai jeng jong twikhanglen lailung'a aleh hup jeng tai.”
\s1 Mara Munna Twi-Kha
\p 
\v 22 Mose'n jong Twipi San a kon'in Israel te chu ahin pui nalaiyun, chuin Shur kiti neldi gam'a akitol lut tauvin ahi. twidon ding thei louvin nithum sung'in akitol tauve.
\v 23 Marah mun ahunggei tauvin ahile hiche mun a twi chu akha'n don thei ahi tapoi. Hijeh chun hiche lai mun chu Marah asah tauvin ahi (hichu akha tina ahi).
\v 24 Chuin mipi chun Mose dounan “Ipi kadon diu hitam?” atiuve.
\v 25 Mose jong Pakai lam sang'in kap pumin atao tai. Pakaiyin thing lhon neokhat avetsah in hichu asat doh in twi lah a chu akholut a ahile twi chu donthei ahung sohdoh tan ahi. Chuin Pakaiyin hiche Marah munna chun Israel te dingin chonna dan khat asempeh in Ama a akitah jingna diuvin jong hilchetna aneiyin ahi.
\v 26 “Aman hiti hin aseije, “Nangman ching thei tah in na Pakai na Pathen thusei ngaijin, Ama mitmua thudih jeng'a na chon ding, athupeh jouse nanit ding, hitia chu Egypt mite chung'a gamna hoise ka lansah chu nangho chung'a ka lansah louhel ding ahiye, ajeh chu keima na damsah na Pakai chu kahi,” ati.
\v 27 Marah mun adalhah phat uvin Israel mite jong Elim kiti twiko som le ni putdohna mun tomthing somsagi kena munna twipang achun ngahmun akisem tauvin ahi.
\c 16
\s1 Vamim Le Manna Kipe
\p 
\v 1 Elim a kon'in Israel mipi akitol uvin Sin* kiti gammang lam hichu Elim le Sinai Mol kahlah ahiye. Hiche mun chu Egypt gamsung'a konna ahung potdoh kal'u lhani alhing tan, hiche lhasung nisom le ninga lhinin ahunglhung tauvin ahi.
\v 2 Hiche mun jenga jong chun Isreal mite Mose le Aaron heng'a aphunchel tauvin ahi.
\v 3 Ama hon aseiyun, “Kada tangei uve! Egypt gamsunga kana um laiyun saneh ding hihen changlhah hijongleh adimlha jeng jin, tun nangman hiche gamthip noiya hi kelthohsah a thigam sah ding nei got u hitam,” atiuve.
\v 4 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Vetan! Van’a konna keiman nangho ding ann kahin juhsah ding ahi. Nisim niseh a aneh diu adeichan'u aga kilo ding'u ahi. Hiche a hi amahon kathu angai angailou u kapatep diu ahi. \x + \xo 16:4 \xt Jn 6:31\x*
\v 5 Nigup lhinni teng keiman aneh khopset diuva anneh kahin peh ding ahiuve, hichu anehkhopset diu ajatnia tam hi ding ahi.”
\v 6 Chuin Mose le Aaron in jong Israel mite heng'a aseipeh lhon tan, “Nilhah lam teng Egypt gamsung’a konna nahin puidoh pau chu koi ahi nahetdoh dingu ahi.
\v 7 “Chule jingkah lamteng Pakai loupina namu diu ahi, ajeh chu nangho nakiphin nau awgin Aman ajasoh tai, hichu Ama dia doumah um ahin, hichu keini chung'a doumahna neijin phun hihhel un, ati lhon'e.”
\v 8 Mose'n asei aseikit in, “Pakaiyin nilhah lamma naneh diu sa nahin peh diu, jingkah lama naneh diu changlhah nahin peh diu ahi, ajeh chu Pakaiyin nangho na phunchel uva ama douna thu na seinau aja soh tai. Keini a kon ipi jeh a na kiphin'nu ham? Henge, na phunchel nau chu keini douna hilouvin, Pathen douna ahijoi,” ati lhonne.
\v 9 Chuin Mose'n jong Aaron heng'a aseijin, “Israel mite jouse heng'a seipeh tem in: 'Nangma cheh Pakai angsung'a kipelut uvin, ajeh chu Aman nangho phunchelna ajahsoh ahitai, tin seiyin,'” ati.
\v 10 Aaron in jong Isreal mite jouse heng'a aseiyin ahile, ama hon gammang lah chu avele tauvin ahi. Ama hon Pathen loupina thil chu vanlam'a amu tauvin ahi.
\v 11 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin,
\v 12 “Keiman Israel mite phunchelna ka jasoh tan ahi. Tun nangman aheng uvah seijin, 'Nilhah lamteng naneh diuva sa kahin peh ding nahiuvin chule jingkah lamteng naneh diuva changlhah kahin peh ding nahiuve. Chuteng nang hon keima hi na Pakai ule na Pathen'u kahi na hetdoh ding'u ahi,'” ati.
\v 13 Hiche nilhah lam chun vamimte ahung kitol tauvin ahile ngahmun chu alo dimlha jeng tauve. Jingkah khovah ma chun ngahmun kimvel lah jouse chu daitwi jin ana chup in ahi.
\v 14 Chuin daitwi ho chu ahung kihoh dohtan ahile, gammang lah akon chun thilpha tah khat alomlom chan ahung um tan, hichu abeh beh a kigol'in anaum'in ahi.
\v 15 Israel miten jong hichu ahin mudoh tauvin ahile, amaho akidongto cheh un, “Hiche hi ipi ahidem?” Ama hon ipi ahi chu ahedoh jou pouvin ahi. Chuin Mose'n ahilchen un, “Hiche hi neh ding'a Pakaiyin napeh u ahi, ati. \x + \xo 16:15 \xt 1 Crth 10:3\x*
\v 16 Hicheng hi Pakaiyin aseije: Nangma insung cheh in naneh khopset diu kilah unlang, chule mikhat in vamim jatnia tamjo naponbuh sung uvah kichoi lut un,” ati.
\v 17 Pakaiyin athupeh bangin Israel mite'n jong abol tauvin ahi, kimkhat in tampi akichoiyun, akim khatma chun achoi khambep cheh akichoi uve.
\v 18 Ahinlah atetoh uvin ahileh, tamtah hin kilah ho ahin chule ama ding khambep hin kilah ho jong hiti chun, kitam lah chom leh kilhom lah chom um louvin; abonchauvin kitohchet chet in akihom uvin aki choiyuve. \x + \xo 16:18 \xt 2 Crth 8:15\x*
\v 19 Chuin Mose'n aheng uvah aseiyin, “Jingkah khovah lhah channa ahalsi cha jeng jong nakoi lou diu ahi,” ati.
\v 20 Kimkhat chun angaisah pouvin changlhah aneh moh uchu jingkah lam chanin akoiyun ahile, changlhah akoi den hou chu than achutan a uilha gamtai. Mose jong achung uva chun alunghang lheh tan ahi.
\v 21 Jingkah sih in mipiho chun aneh khop cheh diu changlhah chu aga kilo jiuvin, nisa ahungsat doh tengleh vang changlhah ho chu ajunmang jitan ahi.
\v 22 Nigup lhinni tengleh changlhah chu achan jatbep cheh diuvin akilo uvin ahi. Khoppi lamkai ho ahungun ahilchen diuvin Mose adongun ahi.
\v 23 Aman aheng uvah aseiyin, “Pakaiyin hiti hin aseije: Jing nikho teng nangho nakicholdo diu ahi, ajeh chu Pakaiya dia Sabbath nikho theng ahi. Changlhah nakisem thei jat chan'u tunin kisem unlang, hiche ho chu jinglam'a ding jong kikoi doh tauvin,” ati. \x + \xo 16:23 \xt Potdohbu 20:8-11\x*
\v 24 Mose'n athupeh bang'un changlhah phabep chu achomin jingkah khovah chanin akoiyun ahi. Jingkah in changlhah ho chu ima ati tapon than jong chulouvin hoitah in ana um'e.
\v 25 Mose'n aseijin, “Hiche changlhah hi tunin neuvin, ajeh chu tunikho hi Pakaiya dia Sabbath ahi. Ajeh chu tollhamma changlhah umlou ding ahiye,” ati.
\v 26 Nigup sung'a changlhah nakilo cheh diu, ahin nisagi ni chu Sabbath ahi. Hiche nikho a chu an umlou ding ahi,” ati.
\v 27 Kim khat chu Sabbath nikhon changlhah kilo din acheuvin, hinlah changlhah khat jeng cha jong amu tapouve.
\v 28 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Hiche mite hin itih chan ka thupeh apalkeh diu hitam?
\v 29 Ama hon ageldoh diu chu Sabbath nikho hi Pakaiya kon ahin Aman eipeh u ahiye. Hijeh a chu Pakajin nigup sung'in changlhah neh ding na peuvin, nigup lhinni man nini sung'a neh ding changlhah na peuve. Nalah uva koi hijongleu chun na umna cheh uva umthim beh jeng uvin lang,’ nisagi lhinni teng koimacha achenna munna kon'in pamlama potda jeng tahen,” ati.
\v 30 Chuti chun nisagi lhinni’n koiman an agaloh tapouvin ahi.
\v 31 Israel miten changlhah chu Manna asah tauvin ahi. Hichu muchi mu tobang bang ahin, atui dan jong khoiju tobang ahiye. \x + \xo 16:31 \xt Minbu 11:7,8\x*
\v 32 Mose'n asei in, “Pakai thupeh chu hiche hi ahiye: Nakhang lhumkei uva um jing dingin manna kihamdoh cheh uvin, hichu nakhang lhumkei uva mite hon Egypt gamsung'a konna kahin pui uva gamthip lah a manna a kahin vah nau ahidan ahetdoh thei ding'u ahi,” ati.
\v 33 Mose'n jong Aaron heng'a aseijin, “Belneo khat latem'in asung'a chun manna phabep khat khum'in. Hichu akhang akhang'a um jing dia Pakai ansung munthenga nagakoi ding ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 16:33 \xt Heb 9:4\x*
\v 34 Pakaiyin Mose athupeh bangin Aaron in jong aboltan ahi. Pakai angsunga akhang akhang'a hettohsah a pang dingin kitepna thingkong maiya chun akoi tan ahi.
\v 35 Israel mite'n jong achenna diu mun ahin phah kahseuvin, kum somli sung sen manna jeng ahin neuvin, Canaan gam ahung lhun kahse uva dingin manna jeng chu ahin netauvin ahi. \x + \xo 16:35 \xt Joshua 5:12\x*
\v 36 Manna Omer dimkhat chu Ephah khat seh hopsom'a hop khat toh aki bangin ahi.
\c 17
\s1 Songpi Akon Twi
\p 
\v 1 Pakai thupeh bangin Israel chate abonchauvin Sin* gammang a kon'in akitol uvin mun khat akon mun chom khat a akitol leuvin ahi. Rephidim kiti mun a ngahmun akisem uvin hinlah hiche lai mun a chun twidon ding aum tapon ahi. \x + \xo 17:1 \xt Minbu 20:2-13\x*
\v 2 Mipi jong Mose heng'a avellin a phunchel kit tauvin, “Don ding twi neipe uvin,” ati tauve. Mose'n adonbut in ajah uva, “Ipi dinga kei kom'a kiphin'a nahiuvem? Chule ipi dinga nang hon Pakai na patep uham?”
\v 3 Mipi hon twi angaicha jing uvin Mose dounan thu aseijun akiphin gam tauvin, “Ipi dinga Egypt gamsung'a konna neihin puidoh mong mong'u hitam? Nangman keiho le, ka chate'u chule ka gancha teu ka boncha uva dangchah a thigam sah ding nei got uva hitam?” tin asei uve.
\v 4 Chuin Mose jong Pathen heng'a kap pum'in ataovin, “Hiche mite ho dinga ipi kabol ding hitam? Song'a selih ding eigo tauve!” ati.
\v 5 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Mipiho masanga kon chun kikhindoh tan. Nile vadung najepna tenggol chu kichoiyin lang Israel upaho phabep kipuijin.
\v 6 Keiman Sinai mol a songpi chung’a ka dinpi ding nahiye. Songpi chu jep lechun twi hung kikho doh jeng ding ahi. Israel miten adon thei diu ahitai,” ati. Chuin Mosen songpi chu akiseipeh bangin ajep in, chule upa hon avet laitah un twi chu ahung kikhodoh tan ahi.
\v 7 Mose'n jong hiche mun chu Massah asah tan ahi (hichu ‘patepna’ tina ahi) chule Meribah (hichu “nelkal” tina ahi) ajeh chu Isreal mite Mose heng'a phunchel pumin Pakai patepna aseidoh uvin, “Pakaiyin hikom'a hi eiumpiu ham eiumpilou uham?” atiuvin ahi.
\s1 Amalek Mite Sat Gamna
\p 
\v 8 Israel mite Rephidim mun aum jing laiyun, Amalek mite ahung kon uvin akisatpi tauve.
\v 9 Chuin Mose'n jong Joshua heng'a thupeh aneiyin, “Amalek mite toh kisat ding pasal galsat ding phabep khat lheng doh tem'in. Jing nikho le keima gamlah molsang'a kadin ding hichea chu Pathen ban thahat kadopsang'a kapan ding ahi,” ati.
\v 10 Mose thupeh bangin Joshua'n jong galsat ding pasal phabep alheng doh tan Amalek mite chu gal akisatpi tauvin ahi. Chuin Mose, Aaron leh Hur amaho cheng chu gam lah molsang lam'a akal tou tauvin ahi.
\v 11 Mose'n akhut teni adopsang chanin Israel mite ahat be cheh jiuvin, chule akhut teni akham tengleh vang Amalek mite ahatji tauvin ahi.
\v 12 Mose khut teni chu ahung kham tan ahile aman jong adomsang jou tapon chuin Aaron le Hur in jong akhut ngapna dingin song ahol le lhon tan, akhut teni chu song chung'a angam lhan toumun in nilhum keijin akhut chu chol louhel in adomsang thei lhon tan ahi.
\v 13 Ajonan Joshua le agalsat mihon Amalek mite chu ajou tauvin ahi.
\v 14 Gal ajo phat uvin, Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Het jingna dingin lekhajol khat lan lang hiche gal kisat chung chang thu hi sunlut inlang Joshua jah din gingtah in simin: Keiman vannoiya Amalek kihetna kiti ka suhmang hel ahitai,” ati. \x + \xo 17:14 \xt Danbu Ni Na 25:17-19; 1 Samuel 15:2-9\x*
\v 15 Mose'n jong hiche lai mun achun maicham asemin, Yaweh-Nissi (“Pakai chu ka ponlop ahi”) tin asah tai.
\v 16 Aman aseijin, “Amahon Pakai laltouna douvin khuttum adomun, tua pat akhang akhanga Pakaiyin Amalek mite akidintepi ding ahitai,” ati.
\c 18
\s1 Jethro'n Ahung Vilna
\p 
\v 1 Mose dinga anupa pa, Jethro Midian thempupa'n Mose le asopi Israel mite chung'a Pakai natoh thil kidang abol ho ajadoh tai. Amapan jong Pakaiyin Israel mite Egypt gama konna ahin lhatdoh chu kidang asaval jengin ahi.
\v 2 Mose'n jong anupa pa, Jethro heng'a ajinu Zipporah le achapa teni chu asol'in, chuin ama hon insung'a apuilut uvin ahi. \x + \xo 18:2 \xt Potdohbu 2:21,22\x*
\v 3 (Mose chapa apeng masa min chu Gershom ahin*, achapa apen lhah chun Mose'n hiti hin aseiye. “Mi gamsung'a khosa kahi,” tia ana minsah chu ahi. \x + \xo 18:3 \xt Act 7:29\x*
\v 4 Ani channa achapa min chu Eliezer* asah in, Mose'n hiti hin aseije, “Keima khanglui laiya pat ka Pathen chun Pharaoh chemjam akon eihuhhing ahi,” tia asah ahi.)
\v 5 Mose nupa pa, Jethro chu Mose villin gammang lam'a ahung tan ahile aman ajinu le achapa teni chu ahin puijin, Mose le amiten gamthip lah a Pathen molsang kom'a ngahmun akisem nau mun ahinpha tauvin ahi.
\v 6 Jethro in jong Mose chu thu athot tan, “Keima Jethro nanupa pa kahin, keima nangma vil'a najinu le na chapa teni toh hung kahi,” ati.
\v 7 Mose jong pamlam'a aga chedoh in anupa pa chu aga kimupi tai. Ama jong akum lhan abeng achop peh tan ahi. Hiti chun khat le khat akilem touvin Mose chenna ponbuh sunga alut tauvin ahi.
\v 8 Mose'n jong anupa pa heng'a Pakaiyin ichan geiya Egypt gam'a konna Israel mite chung'a na ahintoh ham ti thudol'a aseipeh in ahi. Chule lamkah jousea thohgim hahsa athoh nau le agentheina jouseu abonchan anupa pa henga aseipeh in ahi.
\v 9 Pakaiyin Israel te ichan geiya Egypt mite khut a kon ahin panpi hitam tithu le ahin huhdohna thudol phatah a ahet chet phat in alungthim akipah lheh jengin ahi.
\v 10 Jethro'n hiti hin aseiye, “Pathen thangvah in umhen.” “Ajeh chu Aman Pharaoh le Egypt mite a konna nahin huhdoh jal in. Henge, Pakai bou chu ahiye Egypt mite thaneina a konna na huhdoh uva!” ati.
\v 11 “Tun keiman ka hechen sel taije, Pakai hi pakai jouse lah a thanei chungnungpen Pakai ahiye. Ajeh chu Aman aban thahat apanin Egypt mite akiletsah nauva konna Amite ahin huhdoh ahi,” ati.
\v 12 Chuin Jethro, Mose dinga anupa pan jong Pathen angsung'a pumgo thilto kilhaina asemin ahi. Aaron le Israel sung'a upaho ahung uvin Pathen angsung'a kilhaina ankong chu asoh khom uve.
\v 13 Ajing nikhon Mose'n jong atouna a konin mipi ho thutan dingin ahung doh tan ahile, mipi ho jong chu nilhum keijin ading tauve.
\v 14 Mose nupa pan, hitia mipi ho chung'a athilbol amudoh phat in aman Mose heng'a aseijin, “Hiche lai mun a hi ipi mong mong tongdoh inge nati ham? Ipi bol mong inge natia jingkah a kipat nilhah chan geiya mipi ho hi nahiti dinsah hitam?” ati.
\v 15 Mose’n adonbut in, “Ajeh chu mipi ho hi kaheng’a hung uva Pathen akon vaihopna hi akilah got u ahi.
\v 16 Amaho hi ahung kinah komu le kaheng ahin jonlut jiuvin, chuteng keiman thu katan peh jiuvin, Pathen akon nun leh khan dan toh kitoh a Pathen phatsah bang'a ka hilchen jiu ahiye,” ati.
\v 17 Chuin Mose nupa pan “Na thilbol hi adih poije!” ati.
\v 18 “Mipi ahin nangma nahin nabon uva na gimna diuva ahi bouve ajeh chu na thilbol hi abaipon ahi. Nangma changseh adin thil hahsa tah khat ahiye.
\v 19 Tun keiman kahil nahiye, ajeh chu keiman kultah a kahil nahi ngaijin lang Pathen'in naumpi jing hen. Mipiho jouse khella hi Pathen ansung'a ding jing nahin, akibaotam nau jouse Pathen angsung'a na selhah ding ahijoi.
\v 20 Mipiho hi Pathen akon chonna Dan ho le phatsahna ho hilchen inlang, hichu abolteina diuvin thumop in. Hinkho hi iti man ham ti vetsah in.
\v 21 Ahinlah mipi ho lah a konna thilbol thei mi mantam, Pathen ging, nehguh chah guh beija natong thei ding nalhen doh ding ahi. Amaho chun mi sangkhat lah hihen, jakhat lah, somnga lah, somkhat lah hijongleh aloi loija vaihom'a na pansah ding ahiye.
\v 22 Phat tinna mipi thutan a napan sah diu, thupi deuva thutanna ding aum vang le nangma heng'a hinpuiyun tin, thuneo ho jouse vang chu ama hon ama cham a atanlhah jeng theiyu ahi. Nangma dia jong agom lam hijo ding chule ama hon jong nangma nahin kithopi nau jong ahi.
\v 23 Hichengse hi najuiya ahile, nangma chunga Pathen'in toh ding nahin peh teng doujouna tha nanei joh ding chule mipi hon jong lungmoung sella ama ama in cheh akile jot thei diu ahi.”
\v 24 Mose'n jong anupa pa Jethro thusei chu angaijin, aman asei bang bangin aboltan ahi.
\v 25 Israel mite lah a kon'in thilbol thei mi mantam cheh alheng doh tai. Amaho chengse chu Israel mite lah a lamkaija pang ding hichu mi sangkhat, jakhat, somnga, somkhat chung'a vaihomin apansah sohkei uve.
\v 26 Amaho chun kiphunna le baotamna neiho chu Mose heng'a ahin lhut jiuvin ahi. Thuneo boina ho vang chu ama hon acham'un asulham jiuvin ahi.
\v 27 Hiche ho jouse nung hin, Mose'n anupa pa availhah in, ama jong agam langa akile tan ahi.
\c 19
\s1 Sinai Mun
\p 
\v 1 Israel miten Egypt gamsung* ahin dalhah kalseu lhani lhin'in Sinai mun gamthip ahunglhung tauvin ahi.
\v 2 Rephidim ngahmun ahin dalhah nung uvin Sinai gamthip noi ahin jot un Sinai Mol kom'a chun abusa tauvin ahi.
\v 3 Mose molchunga akaltou tan Pakai toh aga kimuton ahile, Pakaiyin molchung'a kon'in ahin kouvin aseije, “Thupeh hiche ho hi Jacob insung le Israel mite heng'a seipeh tauvin:
\v 4 'Egypt mite chung'a ipi ti lamdol'a na katoh nang hon namu sohkei uve. Keiman nangho muvanlai lhaving'a kahin pui uve ti namu chenset tauvin ahi.
\v 5 \x + \xo 19:5 \xt Danbu Ni Na 4:20; 7:6; 14:2; 26:18; Tit 2:14\x*Chule tua hi kathu nangai uva kakitepna nakoi jing uva ahileh, nangho hi vannoi mite jouse lah a keima dia atumbeh a naum diu; ajeh chu vannoi leiset pumpi hi keima a ahi. \x + \xo 19:5 \xt 1 Pet 2:9\x*
\v 6 Chule keima lenggam a chu nangho na leng chan diu, ka gamtheng nalo ding'u ahi. Hiche thu hi nangman Israel mite heng'a na seipeh tei ding ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 19:6 \xt Rev 1:6; 5:10\x*
\v 7 Chuin Mose molchunga kon'in akumsuh in Israel sung'a upaho akou khom'in Pakaiyin a thupeh chengse abonchan aseipeh sohkei uve.
\v 8 Chuin ama hon adonbut cheh uvin, “Ijakai Pakai thupeh bang'a keihon kabol diu ahi,” atiuve.
\v 9 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Keima naheng'a meilhanga kahung ding, Mose, nangma kahin houpi teng Israel miten ajah cheh diu, chuteng ama hon jong nangma nahin tahsan jing diu ahi,” ati. Mose'n jong Israel miten adonbutna chu Pakai heng'a aseijin ahi.
\v 10 Chuin Pakajin Mose heng'a asei in, “Kumsuh inlang keima kahungna dingin Israel mite gongtup tan, tuni le jing nikhoa din seipeh uvin chule avon jengu jong kisop theng cheh uhen.
\v 11 Nithum lhinnia dingin kigontup sah sohkei uvin, nithum lhin niteng amitmu tah uva Pakai chu Sinai Mol chung'a pat hung kumlha ding ahi tipeh un.
\v 12 Mol kimvel achun gamgi semin. Mipi ho chu gihgah in, 'Kichih theiyun! Koima molchung lam'a kaldoh hih hel'un chujongleh gamgi jeng jong koiman natham khah theilou diu ahi. Koi hileh mol thamkha chan chu thi jeng ding ahi. \x + \xo 19:12 \xt Heb 12:18-20\x*
\v 13 Mihem hihen ganhcha hijongleh gamgi kallhah taphot chu songa se jeng ding, ahilouleh thalpi a kap jengun. Amaho chu tha doh ding ahi. Ahinlah, sumkon ahung kimut ginga pat mipi jong molchung lam'a kal thei ding ahiuve,” ati.
\v 14 Chuin Mose'n jong mipi lam chu ahin jonsuh tai. Aman houkhomna a din mipi thensona aneijin, mipi hon jong ama ama von cheh akisop theng uvin ahi.
\v 15 Aman mipi heng'a aseijin, “Nithum lhin nia dingin ki gotup cheh uvin chule nu le pa kitimatna a jong naki kangse ding'u ahi,” ati.
\v 16 \x + \xo 19:16 \xt Danbu Ni Na 4:11,12\x*Nithum lhinni jingkah khovah lam'in, vah akithing'in kolphe avah in, molchung achun meilhang ahung kum lha jeng tan ahi. Sumkon hatah in ahung ging tan ahile, ngahmun sung lam'a um mipi abonchauvin akihotlhul lhajeng tauve. \x + \xo 19:16 \xt Rev 4:5\x*
\v 17 Mose'n jong mipi abonchauvin Pathen toh kimaito dingin ahin pui uvin, chuin mipi abonchauvin mol bul achun ading gam tauve.
\v 18 Sinai molchunga konin Pakai chu meikhu in ahung kum lhan ahile, lhum sung'a konna mei bangin ahung khudoh jeng tan, liing jong akihot lha jengin ahi.
\v 19 Sumkon gin chu ahat cheh cheh jeng tan ahile, Mose jong akipat in hiti hin aseije, van gin kithong lah a konin Pathen'in ahin houpin ahi.
\v 20 Pakai chu Sinai molchung vum'a kon'in ahung kumsuh tan chuin, Molchung vum'a kon'in Pakaiyin Mose ahin kouvin ahi. Mose jong akipatdoh in molchung lam'a chun akal touvin ahi.
\v 21 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Kumsuh inlang mipi heng'a seipeh loijin, ajeh chu Pakai amunom uva gamgi khu ahin khal uva ahile thigam ding'u ahi.
\v 22 Chule thempu ho Pakai kom nai jing ho jengin jong ama cheh akithenso uva ahile bou Pakaiyin asuhmang lou diu ahi,” ati.
\v 23 “Hinlah Pakai,” tin Mose'n aseijin, 'mipi abonchauva Sinai molchung'a hung kal theilou diu ahi. Ajeh chu nangman nei gihgah u ahitai. Nei seipeh bangin, 'Mol kimvella gamgi sem a athenga umsah dinga nei thupeh sa'u ahiye'” ati.
\v 24 Ahinlah Pakaiyin aseiyin, “Chesuh inlang Aaron gakipuiyin lang hin kilhonpi tan. Amavang thempu ho le mipi ho abonchauvin thupeh neijin lang koimacha gamgi khokhel a Pakai lam'a hung theilou ding'u ahiye,” ati.
\v 25 Chuti chun Pakajin athupeh bangin Mose achesuh in mipi ho heng'a aga seipeh tan ahi.
\c 20
\s1 Thupeh Som
\p 
\v 1 Chuin Pakaiyin mipi ho thupeh hichengse hi apen ahi:
\v 2 Keima Pakai na Pathen'u chu kahi, Egypt gamsung'a nasoh channa uva konna nalhatdoh pau chu keima kahi.
\v 3 Keima tailou Pathen dang nanei louhel diu ahi.
\v 4 Nang hon limsemthu pathen van a ahilouleh leiset a ahilouleh twikhanglen'a um ipi thil hijongleh nakisem theilou ding'u ahi. \x + \xo 20:4 \xt Potdohbu 34:17; Thempu Dan 19:4; 26:1; Danbu Ni Na 4:15-18; 27:15\x*
\v 5 Hicheng ho angsung'a chu naboh khup nahou thei louhel diu ahi, ajeh chu keima, Pakai na Pathen u kahin pathen dang na kisem uva ahileh, keiman nangho heng'a ka lethuh diu napu napa teu le nangma insung cheh chule akhang thum le lina channa lethuh ding kahi. \x + \xo 20:5 \xt Potdohbu 34:6,7; Minbu 14:18; Danbu Ni Na 7:9,10\x*
\v 6 Keima thupeh nit jinga, eingailu mi chu asang aja chung'a kalungset na longlou chu ka umsah jing ding ahiye.
\v 7 Nangman Na Pakai le na Pathen min jeng jong ajeh beija namin phah louding ahi. Ajeh chu Pakaiyin Ama min ajeh beija minphah chung'a themmo achansah ding ahi.\x + \xo 20:7 \xt Thempu Dan 19:12\x*
\v 8 Cholngah nikho hi atheng'a nanit jing ding ahi ti sumil hih hel'in. \x + \xo 20:8 \xt Potdohbu 16:23-30; 31:12-14\x*
\v 9 Natoh ding cheng nigup sungse'a natoh chai ding, \x + \xo 20:9 \xt Potdohbu 23:12; 31:15; 34:21; 35:2; Thempu Dan 23:3\x*
\v 10 hinlah nisagi lhinni hi na Pakaiya dia cholngah nikho, hiche nikhoa hi nangman natoh ima nabol louhel ding chule nangma nahin, na chapa, na chanu, na sohpa, na sohnu, na gancha jouse le na kelkot phung hung sunglha a na kholjin mi na boncha uva ima natoh thei louhel diu ahiye.
\v 11 Ajeh chu Pakaiyin nigup sungsen van le leiset, twikhanglen le asung'a um jouse ana sem in; hiche nikhoa chu Pakaiyin cholngah nikho hi atheng dia phatthei aboh a ana lhandohsa ahitai. \x + \xo 20:11 \xt Semtilbu 2:1-3; Potdohbu 31:17\x*
\v 12 Pakai na Pathen'in napehsa hiche leiset chunga na hinkho asot theina dingin nanu napa ging jingin. \x + \xo 20:12 \xt Danbu Ni Na 27:16; Matt 15:4; 19:19; Mk 7:10; 10:19; Lk 18:20; Eph 6:2; \xt Eph 6:3\x*
\v 13 Toltha nabol louding ahi. \x + \xo 20:13 \xt Semtilbu 9:6; Thempu Dan 24:17; Matt 5:21; 19:18; Mk 10:19; Lk 18:20; Rm 13:9; Jac 2:11\x*
\v 14 Mitoh jon nabol louding ahi. \x + \xo 20:14 \xt Thempu Dan 20:10; Matt 5:27; 19:18; Mk 10:19; Lk 18:20; Rm 13:9; Jac 2:11\x*
\v 15 Guchat nabol louding ahi. \x + \xo 20:15 \xt Thempu Dan 19:11; Matt 19:18; Mk 10:19; Lk 18:20; Rm 13:9\x*
\v 16 Na sopi muda man a thuse pole a napan louding ahi. \x + \xo 20:16 \xt Potdohbu 23:1; Matt 19:18; Mk 10:19; Lk 18:20\x*
\v 17 “Na kinaipi khat inchen chu na thangsetpi louding ahi. Na sopi ji khat chu na deichat louding, chule asohpa ahin, asohnu ahin abongchal ahin, asangan hijongleh na sopi chule na kinaipi kom'a thil ima navetlal louhel ding ahi.” \x + \xo 20:17 \xt Rm 7:7; 13:9\x*
\v 18 Mipi hon van gin nasa tah chu aja tauvin, kolphe jeng jong amu tauvin, molchung lam'a kon meikhu amu tauvin ahile amaho chung'a kichatna alhung tan, kithing pumin gamla tah a ading den tauve. \x + \xo 20:18 \xt Heb 12:18,19\x*
\v 19 Chuin mipi hon jong Mose heng'a asei tauvin, ‘Sei dinga na deisah chan keima ho heng'a seijeng tan, na sei kangai diu ahiye. Ahinlah Pathen'in keiho heng'a thu seikha taleh mohseh a ka thigam lhah jeng ding'u ahi!” atiuve.
\v 20 “Mose'n adonbut uvin hiti hin aseiye, “Kicha hih un,” Pathen na gin diu chule na chonset theilou na diuva, nangho sudet dinga Pathen hung'a ahi joi!” ati.
\v 21 Mipi ho chu gamla thim achun adingun, Mose vang chu mei jing lah a Pathen kom chu anaijin ahi.
\v 22 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin, “Hiche hi Israel mite heng'a seipeh tauvin: vanna kon'in nangho toh kihouna kaneije, tihi namit tah uvin namu tauve,” ati.
\v 23 Geldoh jingun, sana hihen dangka a kisem pathen dang kiti keima douna a nasem loubeh diu ahi.
\v 24 “Keima dinga leiset a konna maicham bolna nasem ding, hiche maicham chung'a chu na kelngoi le keltah chule bongchal pumgo thilto le chamna thilto a nato ding ahi. Hoichan hijongleh Keima geldoh jing na dinga maicham natundoh na a chu naheng'a kahunga phatthei kaboh ding nahiye.
\v 25 Songa konna maicham mun nasem ding le khutthem lutna song naman louding ahi. Ajehchu khutthem lutna a kisem chu kintheng bolna dinga lhinglou ahi. \x + \xo 20:25 \xt Danbu Ni Na 27:5-7; Joshua 8:31\x*
\v 26 Chule kaltouna khochut umna a maicham nanai louding ahi. Chutia chu nabol leh, noiya konin min hinvetou khaleh sagohkeo nahi amudoh ding ahi.
\c 21
\s1 Soh ho chon ding Dan
\p 
\v 1 “Hichengse hi Israel mite chonna ding dan ahiye.
\v 2 “Hebrew mi soh dinga na choh tengleh, ama chun kumgup sungsea soh na chu atoh jing ding, kumsagi ahung lhin teng vang le soh a kivul mi chu chamlhat chang ding che ding ahitai. \x + \xo 21:2 \xt Thempu Dan 25:39-46\x*
\v 3 Soh a pangpa chu ama chang seh seh bou ahileh, ama bou kile ding chule, jineisa ahi khah tah le, ajinu jaona anilhon'a kilhon doh lhon ding ahi.
\v 4 Hiche sohpa chu apupan ji aholpeh a ahile, achate sese leh sohpa jinu chu apupa chang ding, ajona tengleh sohpa chu achangseh a che ding ahi.
\v 5 Ahinlah sohpa chun hitia asei ding, 'kapupa kangailun ahin ka jinu chule ka chate abonchauvin kalha ngaije.’ Chamlhat chang din cheda jeng ing'e.
\v 6 Hitia chu aseiya ahileh, apupan Pathen heng'a ahin puiding, hiche asohpa chu kotphung gei hihen kotphung khom chan hijongleh ahin puija, chuteng apupan thihtul khat a asohpa bilkol a vuhom peh ding ahi. Hiche jouteng chule sohpa chu ahinkhoa apupa kin’a kisalal ding ahiye.
\v 7 Pasal khat bang chun achanu soh dinga akijoh doh dinga ahile, amanu chu soh pasal ho bang'a kisol doh louding ahi.
\v 8 Hiche sohnu chun apupa lunglhaina mong mong aboldoh joulou dinga ahile, apupan jong midang akilhat doh sah thei jeng ding, apupan hiche sohnu chu kitahna nei louvin anabol tan ahile amanu chu apupan jong gamchom a johdoh son na ding ima agel louding ahi.
\v 9 Ahinlah hiche sohnu chu apupan achapa toh kicheng dinga agon’a ahile amanu chu soh a bol louva achanu banga abol ding ahiye.
\v 10 “Mi khat chun sohpa ji chu jia aneiya aman jidang akipuiya kit a ahile, aji masa chu anneh, sil le chen, nupa kitimatna ima nahsah louva akoi louding ahi.”
\v 11 “Aman hiche thum ho lah a nahsah pehlou aneiya leh, amanun ima pelouva adalhah a chamlhat ding ahitai.
\s1 Mithat Michom Dinga Dan Kisem
\p 
\v 12 “Khat touvin midang chung'a akhut alha khah a ahile akhutlha pa chu tha ding ahi. \x + \xo 21:12 \xt Thempu Dan 24:17\x*
\v 13 Hinlah Pathen phatsah a kihetkhelna maimai jeh ahile, Keiman kihuhhingna ding mun kagon a chulaiya chu mi mavopa akihuhhingna dia jamlut thei ding ahi.\x + \xo 21:13 \xt Minbu 35:10-34; Danbu Ni Na 19:1-13; Joshua 20:1-9\x*
\v 14 Amavang, khat touvin midang khat chu gotten’a atha leh, hiche mithat pa chu Ka maicham phunga konna kaidoh a tha ding ahi.
\v 15 Koi hileh, anu ahilouleh apa chung'a khut lha aum'a ahile ama chu tha jeng ding ahi.
\v 16 Mihem gumang aum'a, amiguhpa bang chu ana johdoh tah a chule akom'a ana um nahlaiya, akom'a aum pet hichu ama toh kimudoh khom hijongleh, akimudoh pa chu tha jeng ding ahiye. \x + \xo 21:16 \xt Danbu Ni Na 24:7\x*
\v 17 “Koiman anu apa a engbol thei louding amavang anu engbol mihem chu tha jeng ding ahiye.” \x + \xo 21:17 \xt Thempu Dan 20:9; Matt 15:4; Mk 7:10\x*
\v 18 “Tun, Pasal khat le pasal khat akinah a, khatpan jong khat pa chu song tum'a asuh ham akhut tumma akhet ham ahile hiche amisuhpa chu athipai deh louva ahile jalkhun anga ding ahi.”
\v 19 “Ahinlah alhupa chu ahung kitho doh a tenggol mangcha a avale theiya ahile, ama ana sukhapa chu achung chang kisutheng thei ding, anatna sung'a akijenna phat mansah chengse alepeh ding chule ajen damsel ding ahiye.”
\v 20 “Mihem khat touvin asohpa ham asohnu ham chung'a khut alha a athi khah le, soh neipa chu thina chang ding ahiye.”
\v 21 “Ahinlah hiche soh kijep pen chu nikhat ahilou le nini sung'a adamtheng tah a ahile, soh chung'a khutlha mihem chu thina chang louding ahiye. Ajeh chu soh kivul mi chu ama nei gou khat ahi.”
\v 22 “Tun tekah nan, pasal ni akina tan, numei naovop lai chu asuh khah tah lhonna anaovop chu kisuhmo'a aphat louva ahung potdoh khah tah le, numeinu sukha penpen chu ajipan jong anop channa aman adel khum jeng thei ahi. Ahinlah apeh ding chengse chu thutan vaihom hon aphatsah peh u angaiye.”
\v 23 “Amavang numeinu kisuhkhahna khonung'a ahung nat khah tah le: hiche hinkho khel dinga chu hin kho khat ma lepeh ding ahi.”
\v 24 Mitchang khella michang hi ding, ha khella ha hi ding, khut khel a khut hi ding, keng khel a kengg napeh ding, \x + \xo 21:24 \xt Thempu Dan 24:19,20; Danbu Ni Na 19:21; Matt 5:38\x*
\v 25 meiyin akah a ahile meikah jeh a meiya na le peh ding, kimavo jeh a namavoa chule kijep jeh a chu nale jep jeng ding ahi.
\v 26 “Mihem koitobang khat chun asohpa ahilouleh asohnu ham mit asuh khah peh a ahile, hiche soh chu amit adam tahlou jeh a chamlhat dinga asol doh jeng ding ahiye.
\v 27 Soh goiya pang pan jong asohnu ham, asohpa ham khat chu aha asuhlhoi peh a hile, aha asuh lhoipeh tah jeh a hiche sohpa ham sohnu ham chu chamlhat chansah dinga asol doh ding ahitai.”
\s1 Gancha Chung'a Dan
\p 
\v 28 “Bongchal khat touvin numei ham pasal ham khat chu aki a ahin pihlih khah a ahile, hiche bongchal chu song'a selih jeng ding ahiye. Amavang bongsa chu koiman aneh thei louding chuteng bong neipa dinga achung chang thu kisutheng ahitai.”
\v 29 “Ahinlah hiche bongchal chun masang kisanna mihem dang ana pihlihsa ahileh, aneipa jengin jong anahsah lou ahitah leh, hiche bongchal in jong numei ham pasal ham chu aki a apihlih khah a ahileh, bongchal chu thadoh jeng ding chule aneipa jeng jong anigel la tha teitei lhon ding ahiye.”
\v 30 Amavang athipa chu long lhatna dinga aki peh doh a ahile, aki pehdoh sah jat chu aman jong long lhatna dinga apeh ding ahi.
\v 31 “Hiche bongchal chun numei ham pasal ham khat ahin pih lih khah le, hiche gancha neipa chu dan kisem dungjuiya kitham gah ding ahi.”
\v 32 “Bongchal chun soh numeija pang ham pasal ham khat chu ahin pihlih bang ahileh, bongchal neipan jong soh neipa chu dangka shekel somthum apeh teitei ding chule hiche bongchal chu song'a aselih pai jeng ding ahi.”
\v 33 “Tekah nan, mikhat chun kokhuh khahbit louva adalhah jeng'a sangan ham bongchal ham kokhuh a alhah lut a athiden tah a ahileh,
\v 34 “Kokhuh neipan jong aphat toh kitohchetna asem phat ding, gancha neipa jong sum apeh ding, a gancha pohlih vang chu ama chang ding ahi.”
\v 35 “Mikhat bongchal chun midang khat bongchal asuhkhah a asuh khah bongchal chu athi jeng'a ahile, bong neiten jong hiche bongchal athi loulai chu akijoh doh diu akijohdohna man vang chu kihom lhon ding, hiche bongchal thisa jeng jong chu aman kihom lhon ding ahi.”
\v 36 “Ahinlah hiche bongchal chun masang jeng'a jong gancha dang ana pihlih jeng'a ahile, aneipa jengin jong ahilchahsa ahi a chule ngaisah a akoi louva ahile, anei pan jong bongchal thi chu bongchal khat mama a alesah ding, bongchal thisa vang chu ama chang teitei ding ahiye.”
\c 22
\s1 Nei Le Gou Chung'a Dan
\p 
\v 1 Mikhat touvin bongchal ham kelngoi ham aguhdoh a hichu akitha ham ahilouleh akijoh doh ham ahile bongchal khat chu bongchal nga a ale ding, chule kelngoi khat chu kelngoi li alepeh ding ahi.
\v 2 Gucha chun jankah a inbang aphetvang jeh a ama chu akimatna akivohlih khah tah a ahileh, hiche guchapa hinkho that pa chu tolthat a kisim louding ahi.
\v 3 Ahinlah hiche thilsoh hi sun khovah pet ahivang leh mithat pa chu tolthat a kisim ding ahi. “Ajeh chu gucha kiman chun, athil guhdoh jouse aboncha alesah kit ding ahin, alesah joulouva ahileh ama chu kijoh doh a athil guh ho sahna a kinei ding ahi.”
\v 4 Khat touvin bongchal hihen lang, Sangan hihen, Kelcha hijongleh aguhdohsa khat ama insung nei le gou lah a aga kimatdoh khah a ahileh ajat lenia asah kit ding ahi.
\v 5 Mihem koi hileh loulaija gancha alutsah a lengpi lei ham khat gasoh aneh khah a ahileh gancha chingtup louva loulaija alha thang jeh a hiche pa chun aloulaija gasoh phapen a chu alepeh teitei ding ahiye.
\v 6 Chule loulai meiyin ahinkah khah a ling le khao leilah ahin kah jeng'a, chang aki at-lai leh a ki-at loulai mun lah chule loulai chu akahvam lhah jeng tah a ahile, meihal pen pen chun akahvam chengse aboncha alesah cheh cheh ding ahiye.
\v 7 Tekahnan mi khat touvin aheng akom'a sum ham thil khat koi dinga angensea ahile, hiche thil chu akoipa insung'a konna aki guhmang khah tah a ahile hiche gucha pa chu akimat matna a athil guh chengse aboncha ajat nia alepeh cheh cheh ding ahiye.
\v 8 Amavang hiche guchapa chu akimatdoh khah tah louva ahile aheng akompa chun aguh ham ti hetchetna dinga Pathen angsung'a kipui lut ding ahiye.
\v 9 Tekah in, mini chun bongchal, sangan, kelcha, ahilouleh ponsil ham, thil dang amang khat chu ama nei danin asei cheh lhon tan ahi. Amani chu Pathen anga hung lhon ding, chule Pathenin athemmo chu aphondoh tengleh chuche pa chun khat pa chu ajatni a ale ding ahi.
\v 10 Tun tekahnan mi khat touvin aheng akom khat ngansena aneija sangan ahilou le bongchal ham kelngoi ham gancha khat pen pen apeh a ahile, hichu koima muphah nalou munkhat a akidel mang tai.”
\v 11 Hitia chu aum khah tah le anigel lhonna Pakai angsung'a kihahselna anei lhon ding ahi. Chuteng gancha neipan jong kihahselna chu anganse jeng ding hiche gancha chu asah louding ahitai.
\v 12 Ahinlah akoipa a konna kigumang anahi khah tah le, gancha koipan aneipa chu phatecha alepeh cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 13 Gamsahang in atha khah ahitah le hiche hetchetna chu gancha koipan jong avetsah ding, chuteng gancha koipan asah tah louding ahi.
\v 14 Mi khat touvin asopi khat kom’a gancha manchah dinga alah a hiche gancha chu akisuh khah, ahilouleh athi khah tah a ahile, hiche vang chu alapan aman phatah a lepeh cheh cheh ding ahiye.
\v 15 Ahinlah aneipa umpet toh akito khah a ahile alapa chun asah tah louding, manpeh dinga alah ahi jongleh alahman toh akitosah cheh cheh ding ahitai.”
\s1 Numei Leh Pasal Kijonbol Thu a Dan
\p 
\v 16 Pasal toh kihepha loulai nungah khat chu pasal khat in ajol lhah a alupi khah a ahile, aman jong hiche nungah nu man chu apeh ding chuteng jia anei pai ding ahi. \x + \xo 22:16 \xt Danbu Ni Na 22:28,29\x*
\v 17 Ahinlah nungahnu pan achanu chu hiche pasalpa chu apeh nom hihbeh jeng'a ahileh, amapa chun nungah thengho man kikhum peh jat jat apeh ding ahiye.
\v 18 Nangman numei doithem kiti nahinghoi louding ahiye. \x + \xo 22:18 \xt Danbu Ni Na 18:10,11\x*
\s1 Gancha Toh Jon Thu Leh Chondan Thu a Dan Kisem
\p 
\v 19 Chule koi hijongleh gancha toh lumkhom kiti phot chu tha jeng ding ahiye. \x + \xo 22:19 \xt Thempu Dan 18:23; 20:15,16; Danbu Ni Na 27:21\x*
\v 20 Koi hijongleu chun Pakai kom tailouva kilhaina dang nei mihem chu tha jeng ding ahi. \x + \xo 22:20 \xt Danbu Ni Na 17:2-7\x*
\v 21 Maljin kiti chu adih louva nabol louhel ding, na suhgenthei louhel ding ahi. Ajeh chu nangho jong Egypt gamsung'a maljin ana hisa nahiuve. \x + \xo 22:21 \xt Potdohbu 23:9; Thempu Dan 19:33,34; Danbu Ni Na 24:17,18; 27:19\x*
\v 22 Meithai le chaga jeng jong na ngailut ding ahi.
\v 23 Amaho na suhgim uva ahile amaho kaheng lama hung diu chuteng keiman amaho taona kasan ding ahi.
\v 24 Chuteng ka lungsatna nachung uva hunglhung ding naji teu kasat lhuh gam diu, nacha teu chaga kisoh gam ding ahiuve.
\v 25 Chule naheng nakom'a um kamite khat tou sum le pai nabat sah ahile, vaichapa chung'a chun sumkol vei tobangin umdan lang, sumtong jeng jong ama chung'a chu nadel khum louhel ding ahiye. \x + \xo 22:25 \xt Thempu Dan 25:35-38; Danbu Ni Na 15:7-11; 23:19,20\x*
\v 26 Naheng nakom ponsil khattou tundoh dinga nalah a ahile, nilhum masang'a hiche ponsil chu aneipa nalepeh ding ahi. \x + \xo 22:26 \xt Danbu Ni Na 24:10-13\x*
\v 27 Ajeh chu aman hiche bou chu tahsa ponsilla anei ahin, pondang silla imutpi ding aneilou ahin ipi pon akisil ding ham? Keima heng'a hung tao henlang hile keiman ama chu kangai peh teitei ding ahi ajeh chu keima hi milainatpi jing kahi.
\v 28 Pathen doumah nasei thei louding chule namite lah a vaihompa jeng jong gaosapna nabol louding ahi. \x + \xo 22:28 \xt Act 23:5\x*
\v 29 Na lhosohga le na lengpi gasoh chengse chu lung opkaina neilouhel'a nakatdoh jing ding, nachapa te lah a apeng masapen chu keima nei peh ding ahi.
\v 30 Na bongchal le na kelngoi jeng jong hitia chu nabol ding, hiche gancha nou chu nisagi sung'a api koma umden ding, ahinlah niget lhinni tengleh keima nei pehdoh ding ahiye.
\v 31 Nangho ka mitheng te nahi diu ahi. Chujeh a chu gamlah a sahang'in athasa kiti naneh louhel diu ahi. Hiche tobang ho chu uicha te neh dinga napeh diu ahiye. \x + \xo 22:31 \xt Thempu Dan 17:15\x*
\c 23
\s1 Thudih a Mijouse Bol
\p 
\v 1 Nangman jouthu nasei thei louding, muda jeh a thet umtah hettohsah a napan thei louding ahiye. \x + \xo 23:1 \xt Potdohbu 20:16; Thempu Dan 19:11,12; Danbu Ni Na 5:20\x*
\v 2 Chule thilse bol dinga mihem chele ho jong najui a najop louhel ding, mipi nung najui louva amaho khat le khat kikah a them achan theina diuva jong hettohsah a napan louding ahiye.
\v 3 Vaichaho thu kitanna jenga jong pan nalah louhel ding, sihnei langneina jeng jong nabol louding ahi. \x + \xo 23:3 \xt Thempu Dan 19:15\x*
\v 4 Chule na melma khat sangan ahi louleh bongchal vahmang jong nadon peh louding, hiche gancha chu ama heng'a nahin lekailut peh joh ding ahi. \x + \xo 23:4 \xt Danbu Ni Na 22:1-4\x*
\v 5 Nangma doumah bolpa sangan in apot apohlal tah a aopkhum ma ahile hichu, na dalhah jeng louding, sangan akitho doh theina dinga na panhu teitei ding ahijoi.
\v 6 Vaicha thutanna a adinmun a konna achan ding dolla thudih chu na pampai peh louhel ding ahi. \x + \xo 23:6 \xt Thempu Dan 19:15; Danbu Ni Na 16:19\x*
\v 7 Jouthu phot a kinilna le kihehtona chu na jamsan jeng ding, themmona beija mihem chu natha louding, ajeh chu keiman kahenai agiloupa chu them kachan sah him him louding ahiye.
\v 8 Nehguh chahguh jong nakilah thei louding, ajeh chu nehguh kiti hi vaihom a pangpan amit aselmang jin chule adih a pangte chu akhup athal'a alekhup jeng ahi.
\v 9 Kholjin mi jong na suhgim louding, ajeh chu kholjin mihon ichanna lunggel anei uvem ti nahe tauve, amaho banga chu nanngho jong Egypt gam'a kholjin mi a nana um'u ahiye. \x + \xo 23:9 \xt Potdohbu 22:21; Thempu Dan 19:33,34; Danbu Ni Na 24:17,18; 27:19\x*
\s1 Sabbath Nikhoa Chon Ding Dan
\p 
\v 10 Kumgup sung'a phatah a na gamsung'a ann-ga natu ding, muchi gasoh na kilokhom ding ahi. \x + \xo 23:10 \xt Thempu Dan 25:1-7\x*
\v 11 Kum sagi alhin teng hiche kum sung'a chu na gamsung nakicholdo sah ding hichu nangma miten avaicha ho chun aneh diu, lou natong loubeh a na kichol damsah thei ding, ama hon aneh joulou aneh moh chengseu vang chu gamsa hon aneh diu ahitai. Hiche bang bang'a chu lengpi leilai le Olive chu nabol cheh cheh diu ahi.
\v 12 Nigup sung'a hi natoh ding chan natoh ding, chule nisagi lhinni vang le na sangan jeng jong na choldam sah ding, na bongchal ahin sangan jeng jong choldo thei ding, na sohnu chapa ahin najin ho jong kicholdo thei diu ahi. \x + \xo 23:12 \xt Potdohbu 20:9-11; 31:15; 34:21; 35:2; Thempu Dan 23:3; Danbu Ni Na 5:13,14\x*
\v 13 Naheng uva ka seidoh hi nanit jingjeng diu, chule hichengse hi na kamsung uva jong na potdoh sah louhel diu ahi.
\v 14 Kumkhat sung'a keima dinga kut thumvei chan nabol diu ahi.
\s1 Nehkhomna Dinga Phat Kipe
\p 
\v 15 Chol solou changlhah kut, keiman phat kateppeh dungjuiya hi ding, Abib* lhasung hichu cholsolou changlhah nisagi sung sea naneh ding hiche lhasung hi Egypt gamsung'a konna na hungdohna lha ahiye. Hijeh achu khat cha jong keima angsung'a khutgoh keova hung sunglha thei louding ahi. \x + \xo 23:15 \xt Potdohbu 12:14-20; Thempu Dan 23:6-8; Minbu 28:17-25\x*
\v 16 Loulaija na lhosoh ga amasapen pen chu nangman lholhun Kut a dinga na katdoh jeng ding, hitobang ma a chu loulai pumpia na lhosoh ga nahin chop khom teng jong le kut nabol ding ahi.” \x + \xo 23:16 \xt Thempu Dan 23:15-21; Minbu 28:26-31; \xt Thempu Dan 23:39-43\x*
\v 17 Kum khat sung'a namite ho lah a pasal'a kai lhah kiti phot chu Pakai Pathen keima ansung'a thumvei hung kilah cheh diu ahi.”
\v 18 Keima angsung'a kilhaina gancha kithat chu cholsosa changlhah jaona nahin totha thei louding, kaheng'a kilhaina sathao jeng jong khovah geija nakoi den louding ahi.
\v 19 Na leiset ga soh lah a gamasa pen pen chu Pakai na Pathen heng'a nahin pohlut masat pen ding, kelngoi sa kithat jeng jong chu api noitwi mangcha a nahon louding ahi. \x + \xo 23:19 \xt Danbu Ni Na 26:2; Potdohbu 34:26; Danbu Ni Na 14:21\x*
\s1 Pathen Venbitna Dinga Kitepna
\p 
\v 20 Ven, na chena channa nangma na vengtup ding le na lhonpi jing dingin na masang lama vantil khat ka solpeh in ahi.
\v 21 Vantil khu jabol inlang, athu na palkeh thei louding, ama doumah thei himhim nabol louding ahiye, ajeh chu aman na suhkhel chan u ngaidam intin, ajeh chu ama sung'a khu keima min um jeng'a ahi.
\v 22 Aman asei chan lunglut tah a na ngai jing ding, keiman kasei chan nabol'a ahile, na melmate dia melma a kapan ding, nadou te dinga adouva pang ding kahi.
\v 23 Ka vantil chu na masang lama lamkai jing ding, Amor mite, Hit mite, Periz mite, Canaan mite, Hivi mite, chule Jebus mite jouse abonchauva nahin pui tengleh keima tah in abonchauva ka suhmang hel jeng ding ahi.
\v 24 Chule mihem in asemthu milim doi pathen ho masang kitia na bohkhup louding, hiche ho dinga jong chu na kisahlal louhel ding, anatoh bang bang uva jong ima natoh thei louding aboncha na phuhlhuh ding, a songkhom tincheng jong na lekhup jeng ding ahiye.
\v 25 Naboncha uva Pakai na Pathen nahou uva ama kin jeng nabol diu ahi. Na boncha uva Pakai na Pathen kin jenga na kisahlel diu, ama tah in na changlhah neh diu le na twidon ding jengu jong phatthei aboh ding, chuteng keiman na jalah uva konna phatthei nasatah kahin boh ding ahi.
\v 26 Nangma gamsunga chu koima aching kalval jong um thei louding, amavang nangma hinkho chu kasuh bukim sel joh ding ahi.
\v 27 Na masang tinna mihem ten akichat thei chan kamasol peh ding, kidoupi dinga nahin tup chan lungsung kasuhmol peh jing ding, chuteng nangma nahin doute jam cheh diu nangma nunglam jeng'a bou khodah diu ahi.
\v 28 Na masang'a khoi-ngel te kalha masat peh ding, Hivi mite, Canaan mite, Hit mtie abonchauva khoingel ten adelmang hel diu ahi.
\v 29 Na masang'a vang amaho chu kumkhat sung'a kadel cheh louding ahi, ajeh chu gamsung ahomkeova aum khah le gamsa hungpung lha jeng ding gamsa ten nangma nahin dou khah diu ahi.
\v 30 Nangma na hung punbe jing ding, chuteng amaho khu aloiloija kadel cheh ding ahiuve.
\v 31 Na gamgi chu Twipi San a kipat Mediterranean Dillen chan hop a ka kaipeh ding, solam gammang lah a kipat Euphrates vadung channa kakai peh ding nahiye, ajeh chu hiche gamsung ana lo jouse keiman nangho khut a kapeh doh ding, amaho chu nangman jong nadel cheh jeng diu ahi.
\v 32 Amite jouse lah hihen asemthu u pathen hijongleh kitepna neocha jong nanei thei louding ahi.
\v 33 Amaho jouse khu khat jeng cha jong na gamsung'a cheng theilou diu ahi, ahinlah amaho pathen limsemthu ho kin nabol khah ngai ngaiya ahile vang, hichea chu nasatah a nangma nakipal lhuh ding ahi.
\c 24
\s1 Kitepna Namdet
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin: “Pakai heng lama Aaron, Nadab, Abihu chule Israel upate mi somsagi toh hung kal touvun. Gamla thim'a konna chibai nahin boh diu ahi, ati.
\v 2 Mose bouseh Pakai heng'a hung lut thei ding, adangse vang khat a khat cha jong Pakai heng nahin nailut theilou diu ahiye, hitia chu Mose le mipi aboncha hung kilhon lut thei louding ahi.
\v 3 Chuin Mose jong akumsuh tan Pakaiyin apeh chonna dan thu abonchan mipi ho heng'a aseipeh sohkeiyun ahi. Mipin jong awkhat in adonbut uvin asei uve, “Pakaiyin asei chan chu aboncha kabol diu ahi,” tin asei uve.
\v 4 Mose in jong Pakai thupeh chengse abonchan asundoh sohkeiye. Ajing jingkah matah in athou doh in molbul achun maicham bolna ding mun asemin ahi. Aman maicham phung chu Israel phung dungjuijin som le ni atungdoh tan ahi.
\v 5 Mose'n jong Israel te lah a gollhang phabep asol tan, ama hon abonchauvin Pakaiya din pumgo thilto le chamna thilto din bongchal atohdoh tauvin ahi.
\v 6 Mose'n jong thisan akehkhat pi chu athal in twibel ho sunga chun asunglut in ahi. Chule thisan kehkhat chu maicham maija achap khumin ahi.
\v 7 Chuin Mose'n jong Kitepna Lekhabu chu ahin choiyin mipi angsung'a chun gingtah in asimdoh tan ahi. Mipi'n jong adonbut uvin, “Pakai thupeh chan aboncha kabol kimsohkei diu ahi. Ka jabol diu ahi,” atiuve.
\v 8 Chuin Mose'n jong thisan phasah khat alan mipi ho chu achap khum uvin, aseipeh tauve, “Veuvin, hiche thisan hin Pakai le nangho kah a thupeh ho chu anomdet ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 24:8 \xt Matt 26:28; Mk 14:24; Lk 22:20; 1 Crth 11:25; Heb 10:29; \xt Heb 9:19,20\x*
\v 9 Chuin Mose, Aaron, Nadab, Abihu le Israel upa som sagi ho mol'a akaltou tauvin ahi.
\v 10 Israel Pathen chu abonchauvin aga mutauve. Pathen kengphang noiya chun Sapphire song jeng keng lampi khat ana um in, athen dan jong van chungvum kihohsel'a theng bep bep in anaum in ahi.
\v 11 Chule Pakaiyin Israel mite chung'a chun doumah abol tapon, Pathen loupina chu nasatah in amu tauvin ahile, kitepna anneh jong Ama umpina in aneuvin adon uve!
\v 12 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseipeh in, “Mol chunga khun keima heng'a hung kaldoh in. Chulaiya chun um in, chule Keiman mipi ho ding thupeh ho le gahchahna ho kasutdoh hi kapeh ding chutenteng mipi ho nahil thei ding ahi,” ati.
\v 13 Mose le alhacha Joshua chu apotdoh lhoinin, chule Pathen molsang chunga chun Mose akaltou tan ahi.
\v 14 Mose'n jong upaho heng'a seipeh uvin, “Keini naheng uva kahung kile kah lhona hiche mun a hin ana umun. Aaron le Hur in naumpi nauve. Ka chedoh kah a kibouna nanei uleh amani toh nakijahto diu ahiye,” ati.
\v 15 Mose jong molsang lama akaltou tan ahile meilhang in mol chu ahin tomlha jeng tan ahi.
\v 16 Hichun Pakai loupina chu Sinai molsang chung'a ahung kingam jeng tan, chule nigup sungin meilhang in atom tai. Nisagi nin meibol sunga konin Pakaiyin Mose ahin kou vin ahi.
\v 17 Mol bul langa um Israel te mitmun, molchung vumma Pakai loupina ahung kilah chu meikong bangin amu tauvin ahi.
\v 18 Mose chu akalsang jep jep tan ahileh meibang lah a chun akimu tapoi. Ama nisomli le jan som li molsang lama chun ahung umden tan ahi. \x + \xo 24:18 \xt Danbu Ni Na 9:9\x*
\c 25
\s1 Houbuh Sung'a Thilto Ding Ho
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose henga aseiyin,
\v 2 Israel chate jouse heng'a seipeh inlang, keima henglam'a thilto ding adon khom diu, amichang cheh keima dinga thiltoh nom chanin thil hin dongkhom cheh uhen.
\v 3 Israel chate jousea konna nadon diu thil ho chu hicheng hi hi ding ahi: “Sana, dangka, chule sum eng hi ding ahi.
\v 4 A eng-dup, asan dup, asan thim ho leh kelcha vun hose hi ding,
\v 5 Chule akijut jolsa kelngoi chal vun, kelcha vun jaona thinggi thing hi ding ahiye.
\v 6 Thaomei hoa manchah ding thaotwi jong, kinujolna ding thaotwi tah jaona hi ding ahi.
\v 7 Thempu in aki-O ding leh alengkou chunga akikhai ding songmantam chu hi ding ahi.
\v 8 Chujou teng Israel mite lailunga ka chenna ding muntheng tah khat na semdoh ding ahi.
\v 9 Houbuh le asunga thilkeo ding ho aboncha kavet sah ding hiche dungjuiya chu nabol diu ahiye, ati.
\s1 Thingkong
\p 
\v 10 Israel miten thinggi thinga thingkong khat asem diu hichu, adung inchie 45, avai inchi 27 le atun inchi 27 a asem dingu ahiye.
\v 11 Thingkong chu asung le apo sana a natomjol ding, agei gol jong sana a natomjol ding ahi.
\v 12 Hiche thingkong'a manchah dinga chu sana chaokol li nalhah jun ding, chaokol ni chu thingkong pang langkhat a akeng teni chung'a na khai ding, khat teni machu alangkhat teni chung'a na khai lhah ding ahiye.
\v 13 Nangman thinggi chu mol lhon ni tah nasui ding, hiche mol lhon teni chu anigella sana twiya natom jolsel ding ahi.
\v 14 Hiche mol lhon teni chu kong putna a kimang thing ahin hichu apang lang khat a chaokol teni sung'a chu nathol lut cheh cheh ding ahiye.
\v 15 Mol lhon teni chu thingkong panga chaokol kikhai lha teni sung'a chu aputna dia kikhai den jing ding, hiche mol lhon teni chu koimacha gache a aga sutlhah louhel ding ahiye.
\v 16 Hiche thingkong akichai tengleh asunga chu keiman kapeh ding hettohsahna chu na khumlut ding ahi.
\v 17 Sana touna chu nalah ding hiche a chu ngailut hepi touna khat na semdoh ding, hichu adung inchi 45 chule avai inchi 27 hi ding ahi. \x + \xo 25:17 \xt Heb 9:5\x*
\v 18 Nangman jong sana Cherub ni nasem ding hichu ngailut hepi touna among lang tenia na khetbeh ding ahiye.
\v 19 Amang lang khat a ding chu Cherub khat nasem teitei ding, ngailut hepi touna among lama dinga na boncha uva Cherub nasem cheh cheh diu ahi.
\v 20 Cherub lha teni chun ani gel'a achunglam angat lhon ding, alha teni chun ani gel'a ngailut hepi touna chu alekhu teitei lhon ding ahi.
\v 22 Hiche mun na chu keiman nang kahin kimupi ding, ngailut hepi touna le hettohsahna thingkong chung'a um Cherub teni kikah a chu keiman Israel chate dinga thil manlutah kasei ding hichu keiman thupeh a kapeh ding nahiye, ati.
\s1 Dokhang
\p 
\v 23 Thinggi thing na manchah ding hichu dokhang khat nasem ding, adung inchi 36, avai inchi 18, chule atun inchi 27 hi ding ahi.
\v 24 Hiche dokhang chu sana thengsella phatah a natom khum ding, apam jouse aboncha sana keoseh a natom ding ahi.
\v 25 Dokhang kimvel'a chu inchi 3 a nakaikol ding, hiche akimvel'a kivei kol jong chu sana a kijem lha ding ahiye.
\v 26 Dokhang'a manchah ding sana chaokol li nasem ding, hiche chaokol li chu dokhang keng ningli hosea chu naba peh ding ahi.
\v 27 Dokhang kol kimvel chule chaokol hose chu kimat sohkei ding, dokhang chu akijon tengleh hiche chaokol ho a chu thingjol thillut ding chuteng kipu ding ahi.
\v 28 Thinggi thing phatah a moljol phasahpi khat nasui nam ding hichengse chu sana a natomjol ding, moljol hosese chu dokhang jonlena a kimang ding ahi.
\v 29 Dokhang adia kong hoitah tah sana a kisem ___ lheng ho, khelhei ho, kongtong ho chule twithei ho___atwi thilto a sunlutna dia nasem ding ahi.
\v 30 Hiche bang bang'a chu nangman jong keima kaum jing nai ti photchetna dinga dokhang chung'a keima changlhah nakoi jing ding ahi. \x + \xo 25:30 \xt Thempu Dan 24:5-8\x*
\s1 Thaomei Khom
\p 
\v 31 Sana keu seh a kisem thaomei khom khat nasem ding, thaomei tunna dinga akhom chu sehcha a na khetbeh ding, akhon hose le alulangse chule pahcha a kijem chengse aboncha thakhat chet a kigom khom ding ahi.
\v 32 Thaomei phung ajet le avei apat abah gup hung um doh ding, thaomei pang lang khat a abah thum hung um doh ding chule langkhat ma a chu abah thum hung kisep doh ding ahi.
\v 33 Abah gup ho chu alangtogel’a thaomei khon thum cheh um ding, hichu jonmot pahlhasel’a amum le ana um tobang hi ding ahi.
\v 34 Thaomei khom jong chu jonmot bang bang'a kisem khon li hiding hichu jonmot pahlhasel’a amum le ana um tobang hi ding ahi.
\v 35 Thaomei phung'a kon abah gup chengse dangnoiya chu jonmot mum um ding abah ho chu aphunga konna hung jamdoh cheh diu ahiye.
\v 36 Jonmot mum le abah chu alaiya jol toh thakhat a um ding, hichu apumpia sana thengsel’a konna kikheng hi ding ahi.
\v 37 Hichea det kong dinga thaomei sagi nasem ding, amalam salvah dia hiche thaomei sagi ho chu tundoh cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 38 Ameikong attanna ding choiche ahin adopna kong tong aboncha sana theng'a kisem jol cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 39 Hiche thaomei khom le angaicha danga manchah dinga chu sana theng pound 75 ngai ding ahi.
\v 40 Hiche ho jouse hi aboncha molchunga alim umdan kavetsah bang banga nasem doh tei tei ding ahi. \x + \xo 25:40 \xt Act 7:44; Heb 8:5\x*
\c 26
\s1 Houbuh
\p 
\v 1 Nangman nasah ding Houbuh chu tupat pondal som khat a nasah ding pon'a kikhong hi ding ahi. Pondum chule pon pol them naman khom ding, pondal chengse chu Cherub ho lim hoitah a kisem bang'a nakhai cheh cheh ding'u ahiye. Hichengse a chu Houbuh nasah ding ahi.
\v 2 Pondal som ho chu alet le aneo dan kibang cheh ding – asao dan Feet 42 hi ding chule avai feet 6 hi ding ahi.
\v 3 Pondal nga ho chu pondal sao khat naso ding, adang nga jong chu anina pondal sao naso ding ahi.
\v 4 Pondal masa chengse chu aninggol hoa akol kol'a tampi patdum'a nasem ding, hiche bang bang'a chu pondal golni loi lah a apam nungpen pondal gol lah a chu abil nasut hom ding akol kola tampi nasem doh ding ahi.
\v 5 Pondal kimkhat chu abil navu hom peh ding akol kol somnga nasem peh ding, chule pondal kolni lhinna gollah a jong abil navu ding akol jong somnga jen nasem peh ding ahi. Akol navu hom chengse chu ama cheh lhing'a toding ahi.
\v 6 Sana kol somnga nasem ding, hiche sana sumkol ho a chu pondal chengse chu na kaimat cheh cheh ding, chuteng Houbuh thil ho jouse kigom khoma Houbuh khat a nasah doh ding ahi.
\v 7 Houbuh chung khuna ding nangman kelcha mul'a kikhong pon phabep na manchah ding, agoma dinga pondal som le khat nasem ding ahiye.
\v 8 Pondal khat a feet 45 sao hi ding chule avai tong li cheh hi ding, hiche pondal som le khat se chu aboncha alet le aneo dan kibang chet ding ahi.
\v 9 Pondal nga ho vang chu na kilmat sohkei ding, adang pondal gup jong na kilmat sohkeiya, agup channa pondal vang chu ponbuh maiya chu na khu ding ahi.
\v 10 Chule pondal gol masa pen chu apam chin lah a akol somnga jen nasem ding, pondal golni channa jong chu aninggol ho a akol somnga mama navu hom ding ahi.
\v 11 Nangman sum eng somnga jen nasem ding, sumkol hose chu aboncha pondal kol navu hom hoa chu nathil lut ding, ajeh chu ponbuh chu khat seh a akitundoh na dinga na kaimat sohkei ding ahiye.
\v 12 Chule ponbuh a pondal amoh chengse chu, Houbuh ponbuh nunglam a chu nakailhah sah cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 13 Ponbuh kisahna a amoh chengse ho chu alang khat a hihen khat langa hijongleh Houbuh langto gella dinga inchi 18 cheh kikhai lhasuh ding ahi.
\v 14 Hiche ponbuh khuna dinga chu nangman jong kelgnoi chal vun le kelcha vun nemlai jeng na manchah ding ahiye.
\v 15 Houbuh a manchah thil ho chu nangman thinggi thing jol namsella nasem cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 16 Kol khat a na manchah ding chu feet 15 hi ding, akol khat ding chu avai inchi 27 a sao hi ding ahi.
\v 17 Hiche thing kol khat cheh chu among lang'a abil navu hom peh cheh ding, Houbuh thing kol jouse chu aboncha abil nahoi peh cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 18 Houbuh dinga thing kol nasem peh ding chule lhang lamma dingse chu aboncha thing kol som cheh hi ding ahi.
\v 19 Thing kol khat cheh le among lang suhmatna dinga chu, thingkol som inchung'a pansa dinga abil hom somin nadinga a dangka a kisem abiltom somli nasem ding, thingkol khat among lang'a chu asuhmatna thei ding abil tom ni cheh nasem peh ding ahi.
\v 20 A golni channa Houbuh chunglam kaiya pang ding chu thingkol somni a nasem ding ahi.”
\v 21 Dangka'a kitomjol abil somli hi ding, thing kol khat mong lang'a pang ding chu abil tomni hi ding chule thingkol lang khat a pansa ding jong chu abil tomni mama hi ding ahi.
\v 22 Lhumlam nga a Houbuh nunglama pang ding chu thing kol gup nasem peh ding ahi.
\v 23 Chule Houbuh nunglama'a pang dia abiltom'a dinga ni mama na sem peh ding ahiye.
\v 24 Hiche thing kol teni chu anoi lam douva pang lhon ding, chule alu lam'a vang chu chaokol masapen chutoh adang ho kaimatna a pang ding ahi. Hiche teni chu aning koltenia pang ding mong mong ahiye.
\v 25 Dangka a kisem abil tom ho jouse chu agomma thingkol get hi ding, abil tom aboncha som le get lhing ding ahi; thingkol khat a pang ding chu abilkol tom hi ding, anoija pang ding ma chu abiltom ni mama hi ding ahiye.
\v 26 Houbuh lang khatna thingkol chengsea vang chu thinggi kisui nam kotgol nga nasem ding ahi.
\v 27 Hichu Houbuh lang khat a thingkol hose avaiya pang dinga nga nasem ding, chule Houbuh nunglama lhum lama pansa dinga agol'a jam dinga ngama nasui ding ahi.
\v 28 Chule thing kol chengse chu akimlaija pang dinga alailha pen chu among langto gella dinga pang ding ahi.”
\v 29 Hiche thingkol chengse chu aboncha sana a natom jolsel ding chaokol ho jouse jong chu aboncha sana a na tomjol ding, agola kijam jouse jong chu sana mama a na tomjol cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 30 Molsang chung'a Houbuh na kimu sah bang bang'a na tundoh teitei ding ahi.
\v 31 Chuteng Houbuh chu pondum, ponsandup chule ponsan pol thim na manchah ding ponbuh chu nakhu ding, tupat ponnem a kikhong na manchah tei teija; hiche pon ho chu aboncha khut a kikhong cheh cheh hi ding, Cherub lim bang'a kikhong ding ahi.
\v 32 Chule apon chu sana a kitomjol hi ding thinggi thing'a kisui khom li chung'a hi ding, abilkol a kol li ho a chu nakhai lhah cheh ding ahi.
\v 33 Alukhuh asumkol ho chu na khai lhah cheh cheh ding, hettohsahna thingkong jong chu pon lukhuh noija chu nahin koi ding ahiye; hichu pon lukhuna a konna chu muntheng chungnunga konna chu muntheng lai chu nasem khen diu ahi. \x + \xo 26:33 \xt Heb 6:19; 9:3-5\x*
\v 34 Chuteng hettohsahna thing kong muntheng laiya chu hepi touna khat nado ding ahi.
\v 35 Pon lukhuna polama chu dokhang khat nasem ding Houbuh lhang lama dokhang toh kingato lhon ding akimlai tah a chu thaomeivah natun ding ahi; hiche dokhang chu sahlam sanga nado doh ding ahi.
\v 36 Ponbuh kot maiya ding chu pondum leh ponsandup chule ponsan pol thim. Tupat ponnem a heojang pahcha jem kijepna hoa bou nasem peh ding ahi.
\v 37 Pondah na dinga thinggi khom nga nasui ding, hichengse chu aboncha sana a natom jolsel ding, akikhai lhahna ding thihkol chengse jong sana twiya kisem jeng hi ding, abil tom nga jong chu sum eng jenga nasem cheh cheh ding ahiye, ati.
\c 27
\s1 Maicham
\p 
\v 1 Chule maicham dinga thinggi thing na manchah ding, maicham chu bempel'a kisem hi ding, hichu tong nga a sao hi ding, maicham chu abempel'a kisem hi ding, asan lam vang chu tong thumma kisem ding ahi.”
\v 2 Maicham gol'a pang dinga aki li nasem ding, aki sese chu maicham toh kigom khom cheh ding, hiche aki chengse chu sana a natom jolsel ding ahi.
\v 3 Vutvam lodohna ho, khekeh ho, twibel ho, sumkhe ho, khangbel ho jouse chu sum eng jeng a kisem hicheh ding ahi.
\v 4 Maicham'a pansa ding chu kipheh chah kheh khat nasem ding, hichu len pheh a kipheh chah kheh banga nasem a achunga chu sum eng koli jen nakoi ding ahiye.
\v 5 Hichu maicham thinggi jol noija chu nakoi ding, hitia chu lenpheh a kipheh chah kheh chu akimlai tah a hung kijunglha ding ahiye.
\v 6 Maicham putna dinga moljol ni nasem ding hichu thinggi jenga nasem ding aboncha sana a natom jolsel ding ahi.
\v 8 Hichu thingpel tobang'a nasem ding, alai nahom sah ding, molsang lama na kimusah banga aboncha nabol sohkei ding ahi.
\v 9 Houbuh munlaise chu pal naget khum cheh cheh ding, lhang lama pang ding pondal kikhailha chengse chu tupat ponnem a kikhong hi ding hichu pondal tong jakhat a sao na manchah ding ahi.
\v 10 Aki khailhahna ding khom jong agomma somni hi ding, abonchakeiya sum eng jeng'a kisem hi ding ahiye. Akhompia pang ding le aning lah a chengse vang chu aboncha dangka a kisem cheh cheh hi ding ahi.
\v 11 Pal kigen sahlamse a chu pondal nakhai lhungkei ding, aboncha sum eng jeng jakhat a kikhailha a nasem ding, akhom ning dung'a pang thihkoi chengse le alutom ho jouse aboncha dangka a nasem peh ding ahi.
\v 12 Nilhum lama pang pal kigen avaiya um chengse chu somnga jeng na khailhah ding, khompi somkhat se chu atunlutna dinga somkhat cheh kisem ding ahi.
\v 13 Nisom lama pal kigen maiya chu avai lang pang tong somnga nasem ding ahi.
\v 14 Kelkot a pat alang khat sese a pondal vang chu tongsom le tongnga a sao ding, atunna ding khom phung thum toh khomko thum hitha teitei ding ahi.
\v 15 Alangkhat a pang ding pondal jon chu tongsom le tongnga hi ding, akhompi phung thum jaona atunna ding thum toh hitha ding ahi.
\v 16 Kelkot a pang ding pondal chu tong somni jen hi ding, pon san-ao thim leh pondup chule ponsandup thim hichu tupat ponnem a kikhong hi ding, hichu phatah a na jeppol cheh cheh diu ahiye.
\v 17 Pal kigetna a pang khom jouse chu aboncha dangka jeng'a na jep ding, khom phung chengse vang chu sum eng'a kijem hi ding ahi.
\v 18 Pal kigen chu tong jakhat lhing ding, availam chu tong somnga jen hi ding, asan lam vang chu tong nga hi ding ahiye; hichengse chu aboncha tupat ponnem a kikhong jeng kikhai lha ding ahi.
\v 19 Hiche thil manchah jouse chu abonchakeiya, thil khaina jouse hihen lang, pal geiya kikhailha ding jouse hijongleh abonchakeiya sum eng jeng'a kisem na manchah diu ahiye.
\s1 Houbuh meivah
\p 
\v 20 Nangman Israel chate ho thu napeh ding, ama hon Olive a kiladoh thaomei thengsel chu ahin choi uva; a imatih channa kivah vah jeng dinga thaomei chu ahin tundoh diu ahi.
\v 21 Kikhopna ponbuh sung ahin, chule hettohsahna ponbuh mailam a Aaron le achapa ten hiche thaomei chu nilhah lama pat jingkah khovah chan geiya, Pakai angsunga akisahlalpi diu ahi.” Hichengse hi aboncha Israel chate dinga akhang akhang lhungkei uva anit jing diu le chonna dan a anei jing diu ahiye.
\c 28
\s1 Thempuho Kivonna
\p 
\v 1 Na sopipa Aaron le achapa te, Nadab, Abihu, Eleazar chule Ithamar koudoh un. Israel mite a konin chomkhenin ka lhacha na atoh uva ka thempu te hi diu ahi.
\v 2 Na sopipa Aaron dinga khu nangman aloupina ding le amel-hoina dinga akivonna ding thengsel na gonpeh ding ahiye.
\v 3 Keiman nangma lungthim ahin chule tha kapeh chengse aboncha thilbol theina jousea chu thu nasei doh ding, chuteng ama hon Aaron kivon na dinga von tamtah akhon diu, ama chu keima themmo pua pang dinga thensona um ding ahiye.
\v 4 Akivon na dinga akhon peh diu pon chu hicheng hi ahiye: Ompho a ding khat, konggah na ding khat, sangkhol chol khat, thempu natohna dinga sangkhol achol khat le aponunga ding khatma, delkop a ding khat, taigahna ding khat jaona hichu keima ding mong mong'a thempua pang ding na sopipa Aaron le a chapa te ding von theng chu kimsel a agon peh diu ahi.
\v 5 Sana jong, pondum chule ponsandup jaona ponsan pol thim hichu tupat ponnem a kikhong chu amanchah diu ahi.
\v 6 Konggah a pang dia sana, patdum, ponsandup, patsan polthim khutthemna neitah a kikhong hichu tupat ponnem a asempeh cheh cheh ding'u ahi.
\v 7 Hichu aki jotmatna dinga among lam teni alengkouva hung kikhailha thei jong asempeh ding'u ahi.
\v 8 Khutthemna neitah a kikhong pat chu ahin, kong'a kigah ding jong, konggah a kigah dinga kisem kimangcha jat chengse chu akisem bang bang'a khutsoh tah mong'a kisem hi ding, sana jaona, pat dum, patsan dup chule pansan pol thim, hichengse chu aboncha tupat ponnem a kikhong cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 9 Nangman songmantam ni nalah ding, hiche songmantam ni chung a chu Israel chate ama ama phung min cheh nakhet lut ding ahi.
\v 10 Songmantam khat cheh a chu phung gup cheh na khet ding chule, hichea chu amin jouse ama ama cheh pen dungjuiya nakhet peh cheh diu ahi.
\v 11 Sana kheng them pan khut jem hoa thil hoitah a akhet them bang'a nangman jong songmantam chung'a chu Israel chate min jouse na khet peh sohkei uva, na khet chan chu aboncha sana twiya nasun jol cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 12 Hiche songmantam teni chu Israel chate dinga hetingna dinga konggah teni among geiya agen tenia chu na suhbeh den ding; Aaron in jong Israel chate hetjingna dinga amin jouseu alengkou chung vumma apoh a Pakai heng'a apohlut peh diu ahi.
\v 13 Sana khutthempa a konna jong nasem ding sana thengsel'a kisem sana jangni jong khaokol veija kivei bang'a nasem ding ahi.
\v 14 Hiche khao veija kivei sana chu na jopmat cheh cheh ding ahiye.
\s1 Thempuho kivonna ompho
\p 
\v 15 Nangman thutanna munna akivonna ding ompho jong chu khutthem tah a nasem peh teitei ding, konggah kisemna bang bang'a nasem ding ahi; sana jong, patdum, patsan dup, patsan polthim chule hiche jong chu tupat ponnem a kisem'a na sempeh cheh cheh ding ahiye.
\v 16 Nangman ompho khat nasem ding hichu, aning li chule hichu thoni hi ding adung khapkhat chule avai jong khap khat ma hi ding ahiye.
\v 17 Akimlaija gol lia song nagol ding chule amasa a nagol ding chengse chu Sardis song hi ding; Topaz song, aiha song jong hi ding ahi.
\v 18 Gol nina a pang ding ho chu ahile, emerald song, sapphire song chule diamond song hi ding ahi.
\v 19 Gol thum lhinna pang ding ho chu ahile; jacinth song, agate song chule amethyst song hi ding ahi.
\v 20 Golli channa ding chu ahileh, beryl song, onyx song, jesper song hicheng chu ahiye; aboncha sana twija chap nou ding ahi.”
\v 21 Song som le ni chu ama ama min cheh dungjuiya Israel te khat khat cheh toh umtha ding; hiche bang banga chu Israel phung som le ni ho chu songkhat cheh chutoh mohor kinam den tha ding ahiuve.
\v 22 Nangman jong omphoa manchah dingin sana thengsel khao jang bang'a kiheh a nasem ding ahi.
\v 23 Ompho a manchah dinga sana khaokol ni jong nasem ding, hiche chaojang teni chu ompho ning a bupeh ding ahi.
\v 24 Hiche chaojang kol teni sung'a chu sana khaojang chu nathil lut ding ahiye.
\v 25 Hiche chaokol teni among lam akolsung'a patjang nathil lut ding; konggah teni masang lama chu um ding ahi.”
\v 26 Sana chaokol ni nasem ding; hiche chaokol ompho agei tenia ompho sung lama kon ageichin a konggah bantah a nathil lut ding ahi.
\v 27 Hitia chu sana chaokol ni jong nasem tha ding, hiche chaokol teni konggah lengkouva kikhailhahna noilang chule amasang lama na suhmat peh ding; konggah dinga kisem hoitah chunga chu kikhai mat ding ahiye.
\v 28 Ama hon patdum amanchah diu hichu omphoa chaokol sung tenia chu athil doh paijel dingu ahiye; hiche konggah a chaokol teni toh chun athil mat ding u, khutthemna tah a kisem konngah chutoh asuhmat chat diu, ompho le konggah chu kikhen louva um jing ding ahi.
\v 29 Hichu Aaron in jong Pakai angsunga alut teng, Israel chate asuhmil louva, thutanna a kivonna ompho achu Israel chate mincheng apoh jing ding ahi.
\v 30 Hiche thutanna ompho theng sunga chu Urim le Thummin chu hetlut ding, Pakai angsunga alut teng hiche teni chu Aaron lungsunga um ding, Aaron in jong hichu Israel chate thutanna Pakai angsunga alut teng apoh ji ding ahi. \x + \xo 28:30 \xt Minbu 27:21; Danbu Ni Na 33:8; Ezra 2:63; Nehemiah 7:65\x*
\s1 Thempuho Konggah
\p 
\v 31 Thempu hon konggah amanchah cheng chu pondum jenga nakhon peh ding ahi.
\v 32 Hiche sangkhol chol alaiya chu luchang hetlutna ding ahomkhat nasem ding ahi. Sangkhol dang bang'a angaija angong kol kimvelse chu aset louna dia phatah a kipheh chah ding ahi.
\v 33 Sangkhol gei jouse aboncha ajem asan le adup hi ding, asan-ao thim hichu kolbuthei ga bang banga nasem ding; kolbuthei lim a kisem chengse chu aboncha sana jenga nasem a agei mongse a naum sah ding ahi.”
\v 34 Sana chao khat nabana munna chu kolbuthei lima kisem khat cheh um ding, sangkhol chol geilhung keija sana chao chu naba peh ding hichu kolbuthei ga limma kisem khat cheh hi ding ahi.
\v 35 Aaron in Hou-In sunga kin anei teng hiche sangkhol chol chu akiah ding, Pakai angsunga alut pet hihen ahung potdoh hijongleh hiche chao jang chu agin kija jeng ding, hichu akijah khah louva ahile athi a hi ding ahi.
\v 36 Sana thengset a apheng khat nasem ding, achung'a chu mohor kijem bang'a Pakaiyin athenso ahitai tia ajem khat nakhet ding ahi.
\v 37 Sana pheng chu patjang adum khat a delkop a na kan chah peh ding, adelkop chu amailam ama sang lang'a aki tah ding ahi.
\v 38 Sana pheng chu Aaron chalpang'a kitah jing ding, Aaron in jong Israel chaten thil theng ato ding chengse'u athensoa chule themmona hung lut kha photphot chu hichu ama cheh in mona atahsa chunga akipoh ding, Pakai angsung'a santhei dol ahina dinga Aaron in jong achalpanga akitah jing ding ahi.
\v 39 Hiche sangkhol chol chu tupat ponnem a nakhon peh ding, delkop jeng jong tupat ponnem a na khon peh ding konggah jeng jong heojang khatna khutthemna neitah mi khat in apheh peh ding ahi.
\v 40 Chuteng nangman Aaron chapa te jouse chu aloupina diu le avet hoina diuva sangkhol ahin, konggah ahin, lukhuh ho jong na gonpeh cheh cheh diu ahi.
\v 41 Hiche von hose chu na sopipa Aaron ahin chule achapa te chengse na vonpeh ding, thempua pang diu keima kin'a akisahlalna diuva thao na nu sohkei ding ahi.
\v 42 Nangman jong amaho se chu atahsa gohkeovu akidalna diuva sangkhol chol na choh peh cheh cheh dingu ahiye; hiche sangkhol chol sese chun akong uva pat akhu jal chan u akhu khum cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 43 Aaron le achapa te ho chu kikhop khomna pon sunga ahunglut u hihen, muntheng munna kinbol maicham phung ahin nailut pet u hijongleh hiche delchol chengse chu a ki-ah sohkei diu ahi; achuti louva ahile amaho le amahon themmo akipoh lut uva hicheng toh chun thina ato tha khah diu ahi. Hiche dan chengse hi Aaron le ama nunga ason achilhah te ding geija chonna dan hi jing ding ahitai, ati.
\c 29
\s1 Thempuho Thensona
\p 
\v 1 Nangman keima thempua pang dia hite ho hi na thenso tengleh hicheng hi nabol peh cheh cheh ding ahi. Bongchal khat le kelngoi chal khat nahin mat ding ahi.
\v 2 Chuteng cholsolou changlhah lhon phabep jaona hi ding, hicheng chu thao toh kihelsa jeng hi ding ahi. Chule cholsolou changlhah neldisel thao thoh kihel tha hi ding hiche ho chu aboncha suhlou changbong akon na lahdoh cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 3 Hiche ho jouse chu aboncha pucha khat a nakhum lut cheh cheh ding, apucha puma chu Houbuh sunga nahin todoh ding chuteng bongchal golpai le kelngoi chal nahin kailut tha pai pai ding ahiye, ati.
\v 4 Chule nangman Aaron le achapa te chengse abonchauva kotpi phung maiya nahin puilut sohkei uva, abonchauva twiya nasil ngim sohkei ding ahi.
\v 5 Chuteng nagman ponsil ho chu nalah ding, Aaron chu sangkhol chol a kisem chule konggah chu navon peh ding; hitia chu konggah chu nagah peh ding, ompho jong navon peh ding, konggah ding a khut themna tah a kipheh chu napeh ding ahiye.
\v 6 Aluchang'a delkop nakop peh ding, hiche delkop chunga chu lukhuh theng nakhuh peh ding ahi.
\v 7 Chuteng tahsa chunga nuding thao chu nalah a Aaron chu nanu khum ding ahi.
\v 8 Chule hichu nabol chai tengleh a chapa te ho chu nahin puilut pai dng abonchauva sangkhol chol chu na ahpeh sohkei diu ahi.
\v 9 Amaho chengse jong chu konggah nagah peh cheh cheh ding, hichu thempu hina beitih nei louva ama hon achonna dan a ahinpi jing diu ahi. Nangman Aaron le a chapa te chu thempua pang dinga na suh det ding ahi.
\v 10 Chuteng nangman kikhopna inmaiya chu bongchal nahin kailut pai ding, hiche bongchal luchunga chu Aaron le achapa te chengin akhut angap lhah cheh diu ah.
\v 11 Hiche bongchal chu Pakai angusnga natha ding ahiye.
\v 12 Chule bongchal thisan a chu na khutjung na dekot ding hichu selki hoa chu naloi nat cheh ding ahiye, gan thisan amoh chengse vang chu maicham maiya chu nasun lhah ding ahi.
\v 13 Bongchal sathao jouse ahin, chule athin, akal tenia athao jouse jong nalha doh ding hichengse chu aboncha maicham chunga na govamhel ding ahi.
\v 14 Hiche bongchal sa chu avun ahin chule a eh chengse chu pamlam a meiya na govam mang ding ahi; ajeh chu chonset kithoina ahiye.
\v 15 Chujou teng nangman kelngoi achal sang nei khat na in kailut paipai ding, Chuteng Aaron le achapa te ho jousen hiche kelngoi achal luchung'a chu akhut angap lhah cheh dingu ahi.
\v 16 Chuteng nangman kelngoi chal chu natha ding, athisan phabep khat nalah ding maicham maiya akimvel lah a chu nathe khum sohkei ding ahi.
\v 17 Kelngoi chal sa chu nasem ding, asung jouse jaona akeng jeng jong nasop ngim soh ding chule hitia chu asa na semsa chengse leh a luchang jaona hichengse chu kitupchet a nakoi ding ahi.
\v 18 Hiche kelngoi chal sa chu aboncha maicham a na govam hel ding ahiye. Hichu Pakaiya dia pumgo thilto ahin, chule agimnam tuisel hichu lung lhaisahna ding ahin, Pakaiya dia meiya govam hel ding ahi. \x + \xo 29:18 \xt Eph 5:2; Philp 4:18\x*
\v 19 Hichu akichai chai le kelngoi chal khat ma na kailut kit ding Aaron le achapa ten jong kelngoi chal chunga chu akhut angap lhah cheh diu ahi.
\v 20 Chuteng kelngoi chal chu na tha ding, athisan phabep nalah doh ding, Aaron bilkol jet lama nanu nat peh ding, chule akhut jetlam a akhutpi chense jaona akeng jetlam akhutpi chung jousea jong nanu nat peh cheh cheh ding ahi; chuteng athisan moh chengse chu maicham maiya nathe khum ding ahi.
\v 21 Maicham chunga thisan phabep le thao kinu thei chu nalah ding Aaron ponsil cheng chunga chu nasun khum ding ahi; hitia chu Aaron le aponsil chengse kithenso a athenga um ding, ama ahin chule a chapa te jeng jong kithenso na chang ding athenga um jing ding ahi tauve.
\v 22 Nangman jong kelngoi chal sathao chengse ahin, chule amei thao ahin asung thao le amei thao ho ahin amei jetlam toh nalah tha ding ahiye; hichu kisuhdetna dinga kelngoi chal ahi.
\v 23 Changlhah phengkhat ahin thao toh kihelsa changlhah khat nalah ding, changlhah pheng khatma toh nalah tha ding, hichu Pakai angsunga cholsolou changlhah pucha sunga umho a konna chu nalah doh ding ahi.
\v 24 Hichengse chu Aaron le achapa te khutna napeh doh ding, aboncha chu Pakai angsunga thilpeh dinga nakoi jing ding ahi.
\v 25 Chuteng Aaron ahin chule achapa te ho a konna na lelah doh kit ding, Pakai angsung maicham chunga chu nale halvam cheh cheh ding ajeh chu Pakai adia govam thilpeh khat a kisim ahi.
\v 26 Chule Aaron kisuhdetna kelngoi chal op-phang chu nalah ding, hichu Pakai angsunga thilto dinga na todoh ding, hichu nangma na chanvou a um ding ahi.
\v 27 Hiche thilto chu thempu ho chan ding chule amal toh chule kisuhdetna dinga kitoh doh ding chengse jaona Aaron le achapa te chan ding ahijeh a thensona na sempeh ding ahi.
\v 28 Hichengse chu Aaron le a chapa te jouse dinga akhang akhanga Israel chaten apeh cheh ding uva bat a anei cheh diu ahi, ajeh chu Israel cha ten chamna thil ahin todoh dingu hichu Aaron le achapa te chan ding ahi. Hichu amaho jouse dia Pakaiya thilto ding ahiye.
\v 29 Aaron kivonna ponsil chengse chu ama khang akichai teng achapa te chanvou ding ahin, thaonu le khutngap anei nung uva akivonna dingu ahi.
\v 30 Aaron umna munna achapa thempua pang ding pen pen chun kikhopna ponbuh sunga ahung sunglhah ding teng nisagi sungsea hiche vontheng a chu kivon jing ding ahi.
\v 31 Nangman jong thaonuna kintheng a ding kelngoichal chu nahin puiya, asa chu muntheng lai khat a naga hon min ding ahi.
\v 32 Chuteng Aaron le achapa ten kelngoichal sa le pucha sunga kikoi changlhah chengse chu aneh khom diu ahi.
\v 33 Amaho bouvin sa le changlhah chu kisuhthengna kinthenga chu athenna diuva aneh diu ahi. Hiche ho chu athenga kikoichom ahijeh a koima dangin hiche sa chu anehlou diu ahi.
\v 34 Chujongleh kisuhdetna sa amoh ham changlhah amoh ham khat jingkah khovah geiya aum khah a ahile nangman hiche ho chu meiya na govam cheh ding ahiye, hichu koiman aneh thei louding ahi.
\v 35 Keiman nangma ka thupeh bang banga hi Aaron le achapa ten abolna diuva na hilchah sohkei diu ahi, nisagi sungse amaho chu na suhdet ding ahi.
\v 36 Aniseh le kisuhdihna dinga chonset thilto a pang dia bongchal khat na katdoh jing ding, hichu nabol teng nangman maicham sunga konna chonset suhmang theina dinga maicham chu thao nanu cheh cheh ding, thensona nanei ding ahiye.
\v 37 Nisagi sungsea nangman maicham mun nasuhtheng jing ding, hichu maicham lah a atheng chungnung penna kisim ding ahin; ipi hijongleh hiche maicham sukha phot phot chu athenga um jing ding ahi.
\v 38 Maicham chunga na thilto ding chu hicheng hijing ding ahiye: Anisih a tang louhel dinga kumkhat lhingsa kelngoichal ni na katdoh jing ding ahi.”
\v 39 Kelngoinou chu jingkah simma na katdoh jing ding chule kelngoinou dang khat chu nilhah langa na katdohji ji ding ahi.
\v 40 Kelngoinou kikatdoh masa pa chu changbong nel hopkhat a kitena hopsom jaona akiheh lhasa thaotwi khon dimkhat hopli a kihom hopkhat jaona, kilhaina dinga khon dimkhat hoplia kihom khat jaona hi ding ahi.
\v 41 Jingkah lama nato bang bang chu nilhah lamma jong kelngoinou, changbong le lengpitwi na todoh ding ahin; hichu Pakaiya dia gimnamtui tah pumgo thilto a kimangcha ding ahi.
\v 42 Hichengse hi na khang khang uva pumgo thilto a naman jing dingu ahi. Hichu kikhop khomna ponbuh maiya nabol jing diu ahin, chuteng keiman nangma hiche kotpi phung maiya chu najah a thu kasei peh ding nahiye.
\v 43 Hiche mun laitah a chu keiman jong Israel chate ka kimupi ding, keima loupi nan amun chu asuhtheng ding ahi.
\v 44 Keiman jong kikhop khomna ponbuh leh maicham ka suhtheng ding, Aaron leh a chapa te ahin thempu a pang dia ka suhtheng ding ahiye.
\v 45 Hiche tengleh Israel chate lah a kachen ding, amaho dinga keima hi a Pathen u kahi jing ding ahiye, ati.
\v 46 Chuteng keima hi amaho jouse Pakai le Pathen kahi jing ding, alah uva ka chen jing na dinga amaho hi keiman Egypt gam'a konna kahin pui galkai uva ahi; ti ahin hetdoh diu ahi, ajeh chu keima hi Pakai dihtah amaho hin puidoh pa chu ka hi, ati.
\c 30
\s1 Gimnam Tui Maicham
\p 
\v 1 Nangman gim-namtui kihalnam jinga maicham nasem ding ahiye, hiche maicham chu thinggi thinga nasem ding ahi.
\v 2 Maicham chu adung tongkhat a sao ding chule avai jong tongkhat a sao hi ding, a ning li um ding; a tunjong tongni a sao ding, hiche a kimang saki ho jong chu maicham toh thakhat a um tha cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 3 Maicham chung lang chule ajet le avei akimvel sese ahin saki ho jaonan, aboncha sana thengsel'a na tomjol ding, akimvel jouse chu sana a na jeppah thet ding ahi.
\v 4 Hiche maicham a manchah dia chu sana chaokol nijen nalhah ding, hiche chaokol teni chu maicham alang alanga sana kijeppah na noiya abil nasem a naba peh cheh cheh ding ahiye. Hiche chaokol teni sunga chu moljol ki thillut ding hichu maicham putna ding ahi.
\v 5 Hiche maicham putna dinga moljol teni jeng jong chu thinggi thing nasui peh ding, ania chu sana a na jep pah ding ahi.
\v 6 Chule hiche hettohsahna thingkong maicham kikhaina pondal maija chu, hettohsahna hepi laltouna mai laitah hichu keiman nangma toh ka kimutona dinga ka lhendohna munna chu maicham na sem ding ahiye, ati.
\v 7 Aaron in jong jingkah sim le hiche maicham kilhutna ho chu asuhtheng jing ding chule hiche munna chu gimnamtui ahal nam jing ding ahi.
\v 8 Hiche bang achu nilhah lam jong le Aaron in gimnamtui chu ahal nam jing ding, na khang lhum kei uva Pakaiya dia hiche gimnam tui chu na halnam jing diu ahi.
\v 9 Hiche maicham chunga chu athenglou ahin, chule gimnamtui hihen pumgo thilto hijongleh na tothei lou diu ahi; don thei thilto jeng jong nasun khum louhel diu ahi, ati.
\v 10 Kum khat sungsea Aaron in jong sakiho chunga chu suhthengna abol ding, chule hiche na dinga chu suhthengna chonset thilpeh gan thisan amanchah ding ahiye; na khang lhumkei uva kumseh le khatvei cheh nabol diu, hichu Pakaiya dia thil theng chungnung penna pang ding ahi.
\s1 Houbuh Sung'a Thilto Ho
\p 
\v 11 Pakaiyin Mose henga thu aseijin ahi,
\v 12 Nangman Israel chate na simma aminbu u na sempeh tengleh ama mimal cheh in along lhen diu akipoh cheh cheh diu ahi. Hitia chu nabol a amin u nasim teng achung uva natna hoise hung lang louding ahitai,” ati.
\v 13 Amin hung kisim ding jousen muntheng chunga chu longlhen manchah dinga shekel keh khat cheh ahin kipoh uva akoi diu ahi. Hiche shekel khat chu Gerah dim khat toh akibangin, shekel keh khatma chu Pakaiya dia kikatdoh a ahi. \x + \xo 30:13 \xt Potdohbu 38:25,26; Matt 17:24\x*
\v 14 Hiche min simna pang kum somni a lhah chunglam sen, Pakai heng'a thilpeh ding chengse chu apehdoh cheh diu ahiye.
\v 15 Na boncha uvin Pakaiya dia thilpeh napeh tengu leh ahao avai khentum na beihel a shekel keh khat cheh napeh dingu ahi.
\v 16 Israel chaten kisuhdetna dinga athilpeh chengseu chu aboncha na lahkhom ding, hiche a sum ho chengse chu kikhopna ponbuh thil le loa na manchah ding ahi. Hichea konna chu Israel chaten a natohna uva konna Pathen'in ahet jing dingu, hichu amaho jouse longlhenna dinga kibol jing ding ahi, ati.
\s1 Kinu Ding Gimnamtui
\p 
\v 17 Pakaiyin Mose henga aseijin,
\v 18 kisilna dinga sum eng kong khat nasem ding, atunna ding jong sum enga nasem peh ding ahi. Hiche sum eng kong chu kikhop-khomna ponbuh le maicham kikah a natun ding asung'a chu twi nasun dim ding ahi, ati. \x + \xo 30:18 \xt Potdohbu 38:8\x*
\v 19 Hiche twiya chu Aaron le achapa te jousen akhut ule akengu akisil ngim diu ahi.
\v 20 Maicham a kin bolna dinga ahung nailut teng'u hijongle Pakaiya dinga thiltoh dinga hungu ham thil halnam dinga ahungu hijongleh, abonchauva twiya chu kisil ngim sohkei dingu ahiye. Achuti louva ahile thina chang jeng ding ahiuve, ati.
\v 21 Ama hon akengphang jouseu le akhut jouseu akisil ngim cheh cheh diu ahi. Ajeh chu hitia chu abollou uva ahile thina chang ding ahiuvin; achateu jouse ding hihen Aaron a ding hijongleh ason achilhah jouseuva ding hijongleh hiche hi akhang akhang lhumkei uva chonna dan a achepi jing diu ahi.
\v 22 Pakaiyin Mose henga thu aseijin, \x + \xo 30:22 \xt Potdohbu 37:29\x*
\v 23 “Nangman gimnamtui lah a anam tuipen na kilah ding, gimnamtui lah a Myrrh chu shekel ja-nga man nalah ding, agimnam tui lah a ahoipen thingnam tui chu kehkhat nalah ding, hichu shekel jani le somnga alhingin, thingnam tui lah a jong anamtuipen shekel jani le somnga mama nalah ding ahiye.
\v 24 Lingnamtui ga jing jong chu shekel kisim dungjuiya janga ma hi ding, chule Olive thao jong khon dimkhat ma nalah ding ahiye.
\v 25 “Hichengse a konna chu thao namtui semthem hon abolngai bang banga, kinu thei dinga thao namtui nasem ding, hiche thao chu aboncha thao thenga kimang jing ding ahi.”
\v 26 Hiche thao chu kikhopna ponbuh a na nunam ding hettohsahna thingkong a jong chu na nunam ding ahiye.
\v 27 Dokhang ahin, thil manchah ahin, thaomei khom ahin chule amanchah ho jouse jaonan, gimnamtui halna maicham jong aboncha nanu sohkei ding ahiye.
\v 28 Hichu pumgo thilto le maicham thilto ahin, chule twikong ahin akitunna jeng jong chu nanu sohkei ding ahi.
\v 29 Thil hichengse chu aboncha atheng ahi jing na dinga na thenso ding, ipi hijongleh hiche thil tongkha chan chu athenga um jing ding ahi.
\v 30 Keima thempua pang dinga Aaron le achapa te jouse chu na thenso ding ahi.
\v 31 Chuteng nangman Israel chate henga na seipeh ding, hiche thao hi keima kinu dinga kasem ahin chule hichu akhang akhanga nakoi jing diu ahiye.
\v 32 Hiche thao theng chu moh mi chunga kinu khum thei louhel ding, hiche thao theng kihal khom bang chu thao dang toh nahal tha louhel ding, hiche hi thao theng mong mong ahin, nangho jouse dia athenga um jing ding ahiye.
\v 33 Koi hileh hiche thao theng chu adang ho bang'a kihal chop ma aum ngai ngaija chule kholjin mi ham hetlou mikhat chung'a nanu nat ngai ngai uva ahile ama chu amite lah a konna kidelmang jeng ding ahi.”
\v 34 Pakaiyin Mose henga aseiyin, thilnamtui ho chu kilah inlang, Stacte le Onycha chule Galbunum, thilnam tui ho jaonan Bego thengsel'a kihal ho chu kilah tan ati.
\v 35 Thao namtui sempa sem bang bang a na sem ding, chi naso khum ding thengsel'a nakoi ding ahi.
\v 36 Ahalneo khat phabep khat alum lumma nasem ding hichenga konna chu akeh khat nakhen doh a keiman nangma ka kimupina ding munna chu, hettosahna maicham maiya nakoi ding, hichu nangho jouse dia thil theng chungnungpen hi ding ahi.
\v 37 Nangman hiche na sem ding thao namtui chu nangho manchah ding maimaiya na kisem jeng lou diu ahiye; ajehchu nangma dinga Pakaiya dia atheng ahi.
\v 38 Koi hijongleh nalah uva hiche gimnamtuija kisem thil theng kihal mangcha aum khah a ahile ama chu amite lah a konna delmang a um jeng ding ahi.
\c 31
\s1 Natong Dinga Thensona
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose henga aseijin,
\v 2 “Vetan, Keiman atum tah in Judah phunga konin Uri chapa Bezalel, Hur tupa chu kalheng’e.
\v 3 Keiman jong Bezalel chu Pathen lhangao ka dimsah in, chule thil boltheina le chihna khutthemna jong kapetai.
\v 4 Thil lim jat chom chom a semna ding sana, chule sana dangka ahin sum eng khen themna tah ahi.
\v 5 Chule song tampi jong ahin, thingthem boltheina agoma Bezalel kapeh ahitai, ati.
\v 6 Tun vetan, Bezalel kitipa hi Dan phunga kon Ahisamach chapa Oholiab toh kakitho khomsah ahiye, hiche chung chonna keiman nangma ka thupeh chengse hi asuh bukimselna dingun, Keima mi ahi jal a bolthei chan abolna ding kapeh ahi, ati.
\v 7 Kikhop khomna ponbuh ahin, hettohsahna thingkhong chule achunga hepi touna le asunglam a thil jouse aboncha hi ding ahi.
\v 8 Dokhang chule manchah jouse jaonan, thaomei khom le amanchah chengse le gimnamtui kihalna jong hi ding ahi.
\v 9 Pumgo thilto maicham semna manchah ahin, kisilthengna kong le amanchah jong hi ding ahi.
\v 10 Phatah a kikhong ponsil chule hichu thempu-kin abolna diuva kikhong hi ding Aaron thempu chule achapa te dinga akivonna diu atheng jong hi ding ahi.
\v 11 Tahsa a kinu ding thao namtui akibol sohkei uva hitia chu ka thupeh chengse banga aboltei tei diu ahi.
\s1 Sabbath Nikho
\p 
\v 12 Hicheng jouse nung hin Pakaiyin Mose henga asei kit tan:
\v 13 Israel chate henga seipeh tem in, nang hon keima cholngah nikho nanit teitei diu ahi, hiche cholngah nikho hi na khang lhumkei uva keima le nangho kikah a melchihna a pang jing ding ahin; ajeh chu keima na Pakai uvin nangho jouse kathenso nau nahin hetjing diu ahi, ati.
\v 14 Na boncha uva cholngah nikho nanit teitei diu ahi, ajeh chu cholngah nikho hi nangho dinga atheng ahin; koi hile hiche cholngah nikhoa atheng louva kikum kha chan chu thina chang ding ahiye. Chule cholngah nikhoa na tonga aum jongleh hiche mipa chu amite lah a konna paidoh a um jeng ding ahi.
\v 15 Nigup sungsea toh thei chan natoh ding, nisagi lhinni teng hichu nikho theng cholngah nikhoa na manchah diu ahin, ajeh chu Pakai nikho theng ahi. Koi hijongleh cholngah nikhoa natong pen pen chu thina kichan sah ding ahi, ati. \x + \xo 31:15 \xt Potdohbu 20:8-11; 23:12; 34:21; 35:2; Thempu Dan 23:3; Danbu Ni Na 5:12-14\x*
\v 16 Hijeh a chu Israel chate jousen cholngah nikho theng hi beitih nei louva nanit jing diu, cholngah nikho chu aman jing diu, beitih nei louva anit jing jeng diu ahiye.
\v 17 Ajeh chu nigup sung chun Pakaiyin van le leiset ana semin; nisagi lhin nin akicholdo in ahi. Hiche laitah jeh a hi nangman Israel chate jouse henga keima leh amaho kikah a melchihna a pang jing ding ahi tin aheng uvah seiyin, ati. \x + \xo 31:17 \xt Potdohbu 20:11\x*
\v 18 Chuin Pakaiyin Sinai molsang chunga Mose henga hichengse asei chaisoh phat in hettohsahna songpheng teni Pathen a kon khutjih chu Mose apetai.
\c 32
\s1 Sana a Kisem Bongnou
\p 
\v 1 Mose chu Sinai Molsang a kon'in ahung kumlha vah tapon ahile, Israel mipi abonchauvin Aaron henga ahung uvin ajah a asei tauvin ahi; Nagman keiho eilam kai diuvin milim pathen'in neisem peh uvin, Mose Egypt gam'a kon'a eihin puidoh pau ageina lam ka hepha tapouvin, ama chung chang thua ima kahepouve tin aseiyuve. \x + \xo 32:1 \xt Act 7:40\x*
\v 2 Aaron in jong aheng uva aseiyin, naji na chateu bilba jouse sutlha uvin lang ka henga nahin lhut sohkei diu ahi, ati.
\v 3 Chuin mipin jong abilba chengseu asutlha uvin Aaron henga ahin choi sohkei uve.
\v 4 Aaron in jong sana ho chu alan, sana khenna manchah khat a akhengin, hichu bongnou khat limin akheng doh tai. Chuin mipin jong “Vo! Israel, Egypt gam'a konna nahin puidoh uva Pathen chu hiche hi ahi, atiuve”. \x + \xo 32:4 \xt 1 Lgt 12:28; Act 7:41\x*
\v 5 Aaron in jong bongnou kilhajol chu aven, hiche lim kisemna maiya chun maicham asemin, Aaron in hitin aseiye; “Jing nikho tengleh Pakaiya ding kut khat um ding ahi,” ati.
\v 6 Mipi jong chu jingkah matah in atou tauvin pumgo thilto le chamna thilto ding ahin choiyun ahi. Mipin jong neh le don ding ahin tohdoh un, hiti chun ama ama malam cheh a nopsah nan aumpai kit tauve. \x + \xo 32:6 \xt 1 Crth 10:7\x*
\v 7 Pakaiyin Mose henga thu aseikit in, ajah a, “Kinon! Chen lang na mite lam jon suh tan, ajeh chu nangman Egypt gamsunga konna nahin puidoh na mite khu ama ama lam cheh a achonun mangthah ding ahitauve, ati.
\v 8 Keiman jui ding a kapeh jousea kon'in amaho achemang gam tauvin, amachamun bongnou lim asemun, chibai aboh un kithoi nan amang uvin hiti hin asei uve, “Vo Israel mipite, Egypt gam'a konna nahin puidoh uva pathen chu hiche ho hi ahi, tin asam uve, ati.”
\v 9 Pakaiyin Mose henga aseijin, “Amaho chung chang thua keima kaki kum ding ahiye, ahi nau abonchan kahesoh keijin milouchal te ahiuve.
\v 10 Keima kaki kum ding, achung uva kalung souna ka buhlhah ding abonchauva kabah gamhel ding ahiuve, amavang keiman nangma hi nam lentah a katun ding nahi, ati.
\v 11 Mose jong Pakai henga atao jing tan hitin aseije, “Ka Pakai! Na lungsatna Egypt gam'a konna nahin puidoh namite chunga nalhun sah kigot jeng hitam? ati. \x + \xo 32:11 \xt Minbu 14:13-19\x*
\v 12 Egypt miten hiti hin sei unte, Pakaiyin amaho hi thagam dinga ahin puidoh a, Pakaiyin amaho hi molsang chunga pat a ahin puidoh uva thagam hel ding ati ahi tin gel unte, tia aseina thei diuva nabol kigot hitam? Na lunghanna a kon'in lungset tah in na lung heijin lang hiche mite chunga hin suhgamna lhun sah hihbeh jengin!
\v 13 Nalhacha masa Abraham, Isaac chule Israel chu avelin geldoh kit temin, aheng uvah kihahselna nana neiyin hitin naseiye, “Nason na chilhah teu kapunsah ding van'a ahsi jat kaphah sah diu chule keiman katepsa hiche gam pumpi hi nang hon naluo soh hel dingu ahi, hichu nang hon atonsot tonsot geija ding ahi tia nasei chu avelin geldoh kit temin, ati. \x + \xo 32:13 \xt Semtilbu 22:16,17; 17:8\x*
\v 14 Chuin Pakaiyin amite chunga abol ding thil chu bol talouvin alung ahei tan ahi.
\v 15 Mose jong molsang apat chun ahung kumsuh tan ahile, hettohsahna songpheng teni amailam a Pathen khutjih kijih teni chu ahin choiyin ahi. Hiche songpheng teni chu anunglam ahin chule amalam a jong anigel a lekha jem kisun ahi.
\v 16 Hiche songpheng teni chu Pathen'in asem ahin, ajem kisun jeng jong chu Pathen sut ma ahi. Hichu asong pheng teni chunga chu kijih sa ahiye.
\v 17 Chuin mipi awgin chu akithong jeng tan ahile Joshua in jong Mose henga aseitai, “Ngahmun sunglam a khu gal kisat a hitam awgin khu ngaitiem in” atin ahi.
\v 18 Mose'n jong adonbut in aseije, “Galjona awgin jong ahideh poi chule gal lalna jeh a awgin jong ahipoi. Keiman kajah danin lakisa awgin joh ahiye” ati.
\v 19 Mose jong ngahmun lailung ahung lhun tan ahile, bongnou lim kisemthu chu amu tan chule mipi abonchauva alam ujong chu amun ahile ama alungsa lheh jeng tan ahi. Chuin akhut tenia ahin choi songpheng teni chu tolla aseplha jeng tan ahile ani gellin akeh jeng tan ahi.
\v 20 Mose'n jong bongnou lim kisem chu alan meiyin ahalvam lha jeng tan chuin tollham'a jong agoidi jelin chujouvin avutvai chengse chu twija asunglut in hiche twi chu hunamin mipi chu adonsah in ahi.
\v 21 Achainan, Mose'n jong Aaron henga aseiyin, “Hiche mite hon na chunga ipi lomlom ase abol uva nangman amaho chung chang thu jeh a hichan loma hi chonset nabol jeng hitam?” tin aseijin ahi.
\v 22 Aaron jeng jong chun aseijin ipi lom a nalung satna na lhunsah jeng hitam kapu atin, amaho hi thilse bol dinga kipedoh ahi tauve tin aseijin ahi.
\v 23 Ama hon ka henga aseiyun, ei lamkai thei diuvin pathen lim semthu tampi eisem peh un ajeh chu Mose kiti pan Egypt gam'a kon'in eihin puidoh uvin tun ama hoiya uma iti ham keihon ama chung chang imacha kahe tapouve, tin asei uve.
\v 24 Keiman jong aheng uva ka seijin, sana bilba neichan in sutlha uvin katin ahile hichu kahenga ahin choijun, chuin keiman jong sana bilba jouse chu meilhum sunga kalhah a ahile bongnou lim in ahung soh doh tan ahi, ati.
\v 25 Aaron in hitia mipi anabol tah jeh chun Mose'n jong hiche mite hi akijumso ding mong monga kilha thang ahi tauve ti ahechen tai.
\v 26 Mose jong achen ngahmun kelkot achun adingin, Pakaiya dia pang jing koikoi nalah uva um'em, kaheng lama hungun tin aseitan ahile, Levi chapa te jouse chu Mose heng lama ahung tauvin ahi.
\v 27 Mose'n jong amaho henga aseijin, Pakai Israel Pathen'in aseije, pasal kiti phot in chemcha kilah cheh uhen, ngahmun nung le ma a pasal kiti phot in asopiho, agol ho, aheng akom ho chu that jeng hen,” tin aseiye, ati.
\v 28 Chuin Levi chapa ten jong Mose thupeh bang bangin mi athat tauvin ahile, hiche nikho chun mihem sangthum jen athi tauvin ahi.
\v 29 Mose'n jong hiti hin aseyin, tunia kipat nang hon na maicham cheh uva Pakai kin nabol theina diuva mi abangin achapa atha a, chule asopipa ham atha ahi, ajeh chu tuni nikhoa hi nangho jouse chunga Pakaiyin nachung cheh uva thensona anei ahi, ati.
\v 30 Mose'n jong ajing nikho in japi henga chun aseijin, nang hon chonsetna thanghoi tah nabol doh tauvin, keima tua hi Pakai henglama chetou ding kahin, hiche chonset nabol uchu thoidamna na kisem peh diu ahiye, ati.
\v 31 Mose jong Pakai henglama akilen aseitai, “Hiche mipite jouse hi abonchauvin thanghoi tah in chonset abol tauvin ahi. ama macham in pathen lim semthu tamtah ana kisem doh tauvin ahi.
\v 32 Hijongleh Pakaiyin nalung ahile a chonset nau jouse ngaidam teiyin, ngaidam theilou dinmun ahitah le vang, na henga kahung taove, nangman na jihdohsa hiche songpheng a kon chun keima hi nei sugam hel jeng tan tin atao tan ahi. \x + \xo 32:32 \xt Labu 69:28; Rev 3:5\x*
\v 33 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga aseijin, “Koi hijongleh keima doumah bol'a chonse pa bou chu hiche ka lekhasut a konna chu keiman jong ka suhgam hel jeng ding ahi.
\v 34 Tun nangma kipatdoh in, keiman ka seipehna mun, hiche mun channa chu mipi naga lamkai ding ahiye. Ka vantil chu na masang lama masa ding, keiman nangma kahung vil tengleh koi hile hiche mite lah a achonse pen pen chu keiman lethuhna kapeh cheh cheh ding ahi,” ati.
\v 35 Aaron in mijouse bong lim ana sempeh tah jeh in Pakaiyin jong gamsunga natna hoise alansah tan ahi.
\c 33
\s1 Kitepna Athah Beh a Kisem
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose henga “Egypt gam'a konna nahin puidoh mite jouse toh kipatdoh uvin lang chetouvun, tin aseije. Abraham, Isaac chule Jacob henga kana kihahselna gam achun chetouvin. Amaho jah a, “Nangma chule nason na chilhah te kapeh ding ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 33:1 \xt Semtilbu 12:7; \xt Semtilbu 26:3; \xt Semtilbu 28:13\x*
\v 2 Keiman na masang lama vantil khat kasol ding, chuteng keiman Canaan mite, Amor mite, Hit mite, Periz mite, Hivi mite chule Jebus mite abonchauva ka deldoh gamhel ding ahiuve.
\v 3 Bongnoi le khoiju lonna gam khu jon tauvin lang, ahin ka tahsa tah a ka lhonpi louding nahi. Ajeh chu na louchal jeh a lampi a kamoh suhgam jeng thei nahi.
\v 4 Mipin jong thu kisei awgin chu ajah doh phat uvin akaplha gam tauvin ahi. Mipi jouse khat jeng cha jong akivonna ngaiyin akivon tapouvin ahi.
\v 5 Pakaiyin Israel chate henga dingin Mose henga thu aseijin, “Mi louchal te nahiuvin, bongkah khat na lhonpiu jongleng na louchal jal uva ka suhgam hel thei nahiuve. Nangho ilo ding kagel laihin na chung uva kai sana le vonlu cheng koidoh uvin, ati.”
\v 6 Chuin Horeb molsang a konin Israel chaten achung uva kai akivon na jouse'u akoidoh tauvin ahi.
\v 7 Mose'n jong ponbuh chu ngahmun apat kigamla thim khat a ana sonji ahiye. Ponbuh chu kikhop khomna ponbuh ahin, miho lah a koi hijongleh Pakai holnom chan chu ngahmun pamlama ponbuh kisong lama chu gache teitei ding ahi, ati.
\v 8 Mose jong chu ponbuh a konna ahung potdoh teng mipi abonchauvin ading doh jiuvin, mijouse jong chu ama ama kotpi phungbul a ding den sohkei jiuva, Mose jong ponbuh a asung lhah kahsea mipin jong avet mang kei jiu ahi.
\v 9 Chuin Mose jong ponbuh sung alutji teng meibol chu ahung kitollut jin, kotpi phunga chun akitang den jin, chuteng Pakaiyin Mose chu akihoulimpi jin ahi.
\v 10 Mipiho jousen hiche meilhang kotpi phunga ahung kitan den amuji teng ule mipi jong abonchauvin ading doh uvin, amimal cheh in ama kotpi phung bul cheh a chibai aboh jiuvin ahi.
\v 11 Mikhat in aloipa ahoulimpi bang bangin Pathen'in Mose chu ahoulimpi jin ahi. Mose jong ponbuh sunga ahung sunglhah kit teng, ama lhacha a pang leji Nun chapa Joshua jong hiti chun aum den jitai.
\v 12 Nikhat chu Mose'n Pakai henga aseijin, “Nangma tah in kajah a nasei ahi, 'hiche mite ho hi Gamtep Gam a hinpui touvin tin naseiye.' Ahinlah amaho lah a hi koipen toh neisol ding ham ti nei seipeh pon ahi. Ahinlah nangman naseiyin, keiman nangma hi hetsahna kapeh nahin chule nangman naseijin keima lunglhaina vang nachang e nei tinai, ati.
\v 13 Tun nangma mitmua lunglhaina kachan tah a ahile nahenga kahung taove, nangma kahetthem jinga chule namitmua jong lunglhaina kachan jing theina dingin, lamdih a kipuina ding jouse abonchan neihil inlang, amaho jong hi nangma mite ahiuve tijong hin sumil hih hel in,” ati.
\v 14 Pakaiyin aseijin, kami umpina chun nalhonpi jing ding ahi. Hiche a konna chu nangma choldamna kachan sah tei ding nahiye, ati.
\v 15 Mose'n jong Pakai henga aseijin, ahinaije, nangma umpina chun nei lhonpi jing louva ahile hiche mun apat hin nei puidoh da jeng tauvin ati.
\v 16 Keima kahin chule namite jouse ahin nangma mitmua lunglhaina kachang uve tihi iti kihetdoh thei ding ham? Nei lhonpi teng ule keima ho hi atumbeh a neigel na'u ahin, keima kahin chule namite abonchauva leiset chunga midang jouse a konna atumbeh mong mong kahi tauve tihi ka hetdoh theilou diu ham, ati.
\s1 Mose heng'a Pathen loupina
\p 
\v 17 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga aseijin, “Na seidohsa hi keiman kabol ding ahi. Ajeh chu ka mitmu a lunglhaina nachan ahin, hiche jeh chun keiman nangma ka hetchen set nahi tai,” ati.
\v 18 Mose'n jong aseijin, “Na loupina ka heng'a kilah sah tei teijin,” atin ahi.
\v 19 Pakaiyin adonbut in ajah a, “Ka loupina aboncha na masang lama kakitol sah ding, na masang lama Pakai min ka sapphong peh ding, chule ka lungsetna chu na chan jing ding, hepina jong nangma ka chansah ding nahiye,” ati. \x + \xo 33:19 \xt Rm 9:15\x*
\v 20 Chuin aman aseijin, “Ahinlah kamai vang namu thei louding ahiye, ajeh chu mihem koi hileh kamai muchan chu thijeng ding ahi,” ati.
\v 21 Pakaiyin aseijin, Ven! “Ka kom'a a onglaija hin hung dingin lang, hiche songpi chunga hi nadin ding ahiye.”
\v 22 “Ka loupina ahung kitol tengleh keiman songpi kikah a kasel ding, hiche lai munna chu kasel jing ding keiman ka dalhah tengleh bou ka hodoh kit ding ahi,” ati.
\v 23 “Ka dalhah tengleh keiman kahin hodoh ding, chuteng kanung lam bou namu ding, itinama jongleh kamai vang namu thei louding ahi,” ati.
\c 34
\s1 Ani Channa Songpheng
\p 
\v 1 Pakayin Mose henga thu aseijin, “Masang ngaiya bangin songpheng ni suiyin lang, hiche songpheng tenia chu masang'a nangman nasekeh songpheng teni chung'a kijih thucheng chu keiman kahin sut kit ding ahi.
\v 2 Kigo inlang jingkah tengleh Sinai molsang lam'a nahung kaltou ding, molsang vum'a kaheng'a nahung din ding ahi.
\v 3 Koima dang nahin kilhonpi thei louding, hiche molsang jousea khu koimacha dang kilah thei louding ahi. Kelngoi hon ahin gancha kiti phot khat jeng cha jong molsang lah a khu nalhat sah louding ahi,” ati.
\v 4 Mose'n jong masang'a bang bang chun songpheng ni asuiyin, ajing jingkah matah in athoudoh in Pakai thupeh bang chun Sinai molsang chungvum'a achetou tan, songpheng teni achoijin akaltou tai.
\v 5 “Molvum lama kon'in Pakai chu meibol in ahung tan chuin Mose toh ading khom lhonne. Chuin Pakai min chu sangtah in akouvin ahi.”
\v 6 Pakai jong Mose masang lama chen, aseipeh in, “Yahweh! Pakai! Hepithem le lunghang vahlou! Mi lungsetthem le dihna dimset jeng, lunghang vahlou kahi. \x + \xo 34:6 \xt Potdohbu 20:5,6; Minbu 14:18; Danbu Ni Na 5:9,10; 7:9,10\x*
\v 7 Mihem asang asang chung'a lungsetna nei jing, themmona le suhkhelna jouse jong ngaidam jia, amavang themmona alem a umsah lou, mipa le chate kikah atute channa natong jing ding; chule khang thum le li channa natong theiya kahi,” ati.
\v 8 Mose jong tol lhamma akun'in chibai aboh paijin ahi.
\v 9 Mose'n aseijin, “O Pakai, nangma mitmua lunglhaina kachan a ahile, nahenga kataove, Pakai hi kalah uvah hung um henlang, ka themmo nau le ka chonsetnau jouse ngaidamin, nagoulo thei din neisem tauvin,” ati.
\v 10 “Chuin Pakaiyin aseijin, “Tua hi keiman nangma toh ikah a kitepna kasem ding ahi. Na mite lah a keiman thil nasatah tah kakilah sah ding, hitobang thil kidang ho hi leiset a ana umkha loulai ahin, chule nam dang te lah jenga jong anasoh khalou lai ahi. Na chenna chan uva mihem hon Pakai thilbol kidang ahin mudoh diu, ajeh chu keiman kahin bol ding thil hi thil kidang tah ahi.
\v 11 Tunia ka thupeh hi na suhmil louding ahi. Neihin ven, keima tah in na masang lama Amor mite, Canaan mite, Hit mite, Periz mite, Hivi mite le Jebus mite abonchauva kajam gamsah diu ahi.”
\v 12 “Tun nangma kichih theiyin, na chenna gam mite toh kitepna hinsem khan nate, achuti louva ahile hitobang kitepna chu kipallhuhna a hung pang ding ahi.
\v 13 Hijeh chun nangman hiche gam mite maicham jouse chu na suhset gamhel ding, akhompi jouseu jong nasuh lhuh sohkei ding ahi, chule Asher doi jong chu na phuhlhuh ding ahi. \x + \xo 34:13 \xt Danbu Ni Na 16:21\x*
\v 14 Nangman pathen dang nahou louding ahi, ajeh chu Pakai hi amin jong Thangthip ahin, pathen dang nahou jeh a thangthipna nei thei Pathen ahi.
\v 15 Hijeh a chu agamsung cheng te toh kitepna nasem thei louding, hiche mite chun a pathen'u um chan atho diu amaho le amaho kah a jonthanhoi apat diu, hiche pathen semthu ho heng'a kilhaina asem teng ule nangma jong nahin tep diu ahin, hiche a na hinkou pen pen kilhaina sa chu naneh thei louding ahi,” ati.
\v 16 Na chapa te ji dinga agam cheng numei na puipeh thei louding, a chanu teu jousen a pathen'u um chan atho uva akijoh bang uva khu, na chapa te jeng jong hung kijohlo ding'u ahi.
\v 17 Chule nangma macham'a pathen lim semthu kiti mong mong nahou louding ahi. \x + \xo 34:17 \xt Potdohbu 20:4; Thempu Dan 19:4; Danbu Ni Na 5:8; 27:15\x*
\v 18 Chol solou Changlhah Kut jong kumsih a naman jing ding ahi. Ka thupeh bang bang'a nisagi sunga chol solou changlhah naneh ding ahi. Hiche kut hi nipi kipattil Abib lha sunga nangma Egypt gamsung'a kon a nahung doh ahijeh a naman diu ahi.\x + \xo 34:18 \xt Potdohbu 12:14-20; Thempu Dan 23:6-8; Minbu 28:16-25\x*
\v 19 Chule ahung peng doh masa jouse chu keiya ding ahi. Achal'a kailhah kiti phot chu gancha lah a bong ahin, kelngoi hijongleh keija ding ahi. \x + \xo 34:19 \xt Potdohbu 13:2\x*
\v 20 Sangan hung pengdoh masa jong chu nangman kelngoi khat a na lhatdoh ding, itiham a na lhatdoh jou louva ahile hiche sangan nou chu angong chang naheboh peh ding ahi. Na chapa te lah a ahung peng doh masa pen jong lhatdohna na sempeh tei ding ahi. Nalah uva koima kaheng'a khutgoh keova hung kilah thei louding ahi. \x + \xo 34:20 \xt Potdohbu 13:13\x*
\v 21 Nigup sungsea nangman tohthei chan natoh ding, nisagi lhinni tengleh na kicholdo ding ahi. Lou natoh lai hihen lholhun lai hijongleh nangma nakichol teitei ding ahi. \x + \xo 34:21 \xt Potdohbu 20:9,10; 23:12; 31:15; 35:2; Thempu Dan 23:3; Danbu Ni Na 5:13,14\x*
\v 22 Nisagi lhinnia Lholhun Kut jong nabol jing ding nanit teitei ding ahi. Chule suhlou chang kut jong nabol jing ding, kum lhun tengleh muchi ga soh khop tup kut jong nabol cheh cheh ding ahi. \x + \xo 34:22 \xt Thempu Dan 23:15-21; Minbu 28:26-31; \xt Thempu Dan 23:39-43\x*
\v 23 Kum khat sung'a na mite lah a pasal'a kailhah jouse Israel Pakai, Pathen heng'a hung kilah cheh ding'u ahi.
\v 24 Ajeh chu keiman namtin vaipi jouse masang'a ka huhdoh a hitia chu na gamgi kasuh let ding ahi. Ajeh chu nangma kumkhat sung'a Pakai heng'a thumvei kilah dinga nache tengleh koiman na umlou kah a na gamsung lah ding lung aken louhel ding'u ahi.
\v 25 Ka heng'a kilhaina sa kiti phot cholsosa toh naneh tha louding, Kalchuh Kut a dinga sa kithat chan jong jing khovah geiya na koiden theilou diu ahi. \x + \xo 34:25 \xt Potdohbu 12:10\x*
\v 26 Na gamsung'a ga soh jouse jong na Pakai leh na Pathen heng'a nahin pohlut cheh cheh ding ahi. “Kelngoi nou jeng jong api noitwija nahon min thei louding ahi.” \x + \xo 34:26 \xt Danbu Ni Na 26:2; \xt Danbu Ni Na 14:21\x*
\v 27 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a thu asei in, “Ka thupeh chengse abonchan sundoh cheh cheh in, Ka thupeh chengse dungjuiya hi Israel toh na kikah a kitepna ka semdoh ding ahi,” ati.
\v 28 Hiche lai mun achun Pakai le Mose chu nisom le jan somli jen aum khomin ahi. Hiche phat sung'a hin Mose'n twi jong donlou an jong nelouvin aum'in ahi. Chule Pakaijin kitepna-Thupeh Som-chu songpheng teni chunga chun ajihlut tan ahi.”
\s1 Mose Maivah
\p 
\v 29 Sinai molsang lam'a kon'in Mose jong ahung kumsuh in ahile hettohsahna songpheng teni chu ahin choiyin ahi. Mose mai chu avahlha jeng'e ajeh chu Pathen toh aga kihoulim jeh ahin hinlah aman ahedoh pon ahi. \x + \xo 34:29 \xt 2 Crth 3:7-16\x*
\v 30 Chuin Aaron le Israel chate jousen Mose maivah chu amudoh tauvin ahile akicha lheh jengun anailut ngam tapouve.
\v 31 Mose'n ahin kouvun, chuin Aaron le khopi sung'a lamkai jouse Mose henga ahungun, Mose'n jong amaho chengse chu akihoupin ahi.
\v 32 Israel chate ho jousen jong ahin nailut cheh uvin, Sinai molsang chungvum a Pakaiyin Mose ahoupina bang bangin Mose'n jong Israel mite jouse chu ahoulim pi'n thu jouse chu ajah uva aseipeh tan ahi.
\v 33 Mose'n jong thupeh jouse aheng uva asei chai soh phat in amai dal dingin pon khat akilekhu sah tai.
\v 34 Mose jong Pakai to kihoulim dinga achelut jiteng ahung potdoh kit kahsen amai dalna dinga ponkhu chu akilahdoh kitji tan ahi. Mose jong ahung potdoh a Pakaiyin ipi thupey ahin seipeh chu Isreal mite heng'a aseipeh jin,
\v 35 chule Israel chaten jong Mose maivah chu amu jiuvin ahi. Hijeh chun Mosen jong Pakai toh kimuto dinga achelut kit kahsen amai dalna pon chu akikhu jin ahi.
\c 35
\s1 Sabbath Toh Kitoh a Jui ding Ho
\p 
\v 1 Mose'n jong Israel insung abonchauvin akou khom sohkeiyin ajah uva aseipeh in ahi. “Hichengse hi Pakaiyin nangho jouse jui dingin aseiyin ahi.
\v 2 Nang hon hapta sung'a tohthei chan natohna dingun nigup nanei uvin, nisagi lhinni hi nangho dia nikho theng ahin, hiche nikhoa hi nakichol sohkei diu ahi. Ajeh chu Pakaiya dia thenso ahitai, koi hile hiche nikhoa natong chan chu thina chang jeng ding ahiye. \x + \xo 35:2 \xt Potdohbu 20:8-11; 23:12; 31:15; 34:21; Thempu Dan 23:3; Danbu Ni Na 5:12-14\x*
\v 3 Cholngah nikhoa hi nangma insung cheh a mei jong nati kong louhel ding'u ahi.”
\s1 Pakaiya Thilpeh Ding
\p 
\v 4 Chuin Mose'n Israel chate jouse heng'a a seipeh in, “Hiche hi Pakaiyin athupeh ahi:
\v 5 Pakaiya din na thilpeh theng kichoi cheh un. Amahon anei cheh ami chan cheh in Pakai dinga hongphal tah in hicheng hi pehen: sana le dangka chule sum eng;
\v 6 a engdum ahin, asandup hichu hoitah a kikhong hi ding; kelcha mul jaona hi ding ahiye;
\v 7 aki nam-sel kelngoi chal vun chule kelcha vun ahin thinggi thing jaona hi ding ahi;
\v 8 thaomei dinga Olive thao hi ding; chule kinu ding thao namtui jong halnam thei thao twi jao cheh cheh ding ahi;
\v 9 songmantam, chule tun ding song jong konggah omphoa manchah ding jong ahi.
\v 10 “Koi hileh nalah uva khutthem natong thei jouse hung'un. Tundoh dinga Pakai thupeh chengse sauvin:
\v 11 aponbuh ding, achungvum'a khu ding, athil manchah jouse jaonan, ajol le akhompi jouse jaona hi ding ahi;
\v 12 thingkong chule aputna ding moljol teni jong; hepi touna, chule pon akhu khumna a kimang jong hi ding ahiye;
\v 13 chule dokhang ahin amoljol ho jaona; manchah chengse le changlhah kikatdohsa ho jaona hi ding ahi;
\v 14 meivah thaomei khom le amanchah chengse; chule Olive thao vah ding jaona hi ding;
\v 15 gimnamtui lhutna ding; chule amoljol chengse kinu ding; thaotwi le halnam thei thao twi chengse jong; chule Houbuh a manchah ding pondal chengse jong hi ding;
\v 16 pumgo thilto maicham; chule athilkeo jouse kisilna kong le atunna jong ahi;
\v 17 amunna khai ding ho jong; akhailhahna ding khom ho jaonan; chule kotbulla khai ding pondal jong jaona hi ding;
\v 18 Houbuh kilmatna ding ahom ho ahin, akhao jouse jong jao cheh ding;
\v 19 muntheng'a manchah dinga kikhong von jouse leh thempu kin bol'a apan teng ule amanchah diuva kikhong Aaron vontheng chengse ahin chule achapa te von chengse jong hi ding ahi.”
\s1 Houbuh Sung'a Dia Thilto Ho
\p 
\v 20 Chuin Israel insung pumpi Mose adalha uvin aponbuh cheh akijot tauvin ahi.
\v 21 Chule alungthim'a kitilkhouna nei chan le lhagaova haldoh chan chu ahung khom uvin, kikhopkhomna ponbuh sung'a manchah ding ahin, kinbolna a manchah ding chule kivonna athenga manchah ding abonchan Pakai heng'a ahin lhut tauvin ahi.
\v 22 Numei le pasal ani gel'in ahung khom tauvin ahi. Chuin heojang ahin, khutjem, bilba, chaokol le sana a kisem thil jouse jong ahin choikhom sohkei uvin ahi. Ama ama michan cheh in sana thilpeh jouse ahin choi sohkei uvin ahi.
\v 23 Ama cham'a kipedoh chan chun hichengse hi ahin choiyun ahi: pondum, asandup, asanpol, tupatpon, kelcha mul, kelngoi chal vun, kelcha vun chengse jong anei channu ahin choi khom sohkei uvin ahi.
\v 24 Amitakip in Pakaiya thilpeh ding ama ama cheh in ahin choi uvin ahi. Chule ipi thil'a kimang hijongleh Pakaiya din ahin choi khom sohkei un ahi.
\v 25 Ajou chanin ama cheh khut themna tah in pat akhongun, chuteng hiche pat kikhong jouse chu asan hihen asandup hijongleh asanpol jaonan tupat ponnem'a hijongleh ahin choi khom sohkei uvin ahi.
\v 26 Numei ho jouse lah a alungsung'a konna kipehdohna nei chan chun kelcha mul'a kon'in abol cheh uvin ahi.
\v 27 Japi lamkaija pang chengsen jong konggah ding le omphoa beh dingin songmantam jatchom cheh ahin choi khom uvin ahi.
\v 28 Chule ama hon gimnamtui ahin, meivah a pang ding thaotwi ahin, kinu ding thaotwi chule gimnamtuiya halnam thei jong ahin choi khom uve.
\v 29 Isreal chate lah a numei ahin chule pasal ahin, Pakaiyin Mose heng'a athupeh bangin bol inge tia alungthim a konna kitilkhouna nei chan chu Pakai heng'a kipah le thanom tah in ipi hijongleh apehnom chan'u chu ahin choi khom uvin ahi.
\v 30 Chuin Mose'n Israel mite heng'a aseijin. Juda phung'a kon Hur chapa Bezalel chu Pakaiyin alheng doh tan ahi.
\s1 Natong Ding Ho Kikhom
\p 
\v 31 Pakaiyin Bezalel chu Pathen Lhagao adimset sah jeng tan, amapa jong chihna le lungthim hattah thilbol thei tah ahung hidoh tan ahi.
\v 32 Amapa chu thil jep dan jong them tah, sana le dangka jaonan thil ijakai sem dan jong amachamin ahin hedoh theiyin ahi.
\v 33 Amapa chun tun ding song tamtah asemin, thing jong ajat jat in ajem theiyin, khutthemna jouse achang theiyin ahi.
\v 34 Pakaiyin Bezalel chule Dan phungkai akon'in Ahisamach chapa Oholiab ahin, ani tah lhon'in mijouse kihilna thei dingin asemdoh lhon tan ahi.
\v 35 Pakaiyin amani chu natoh ijakai thepna ape lhon tan ahile, thilsem themna neijin, thembol in apang lhonin, thil lim gon dan jong, pon jeppol dan jong, adum, asanpol, chule tupatpon khui themna jong apeh lhon ahi. Bezalel le Oholiab jong thil ijakai boltheina chu achang lhon tan ahi.
\c 36
\s1 Mijousen Avalset Apeh
\p 
\v 1 “Pakaiyin Bezalel le Oholiab chule midang jong thilbol theina apeuvin chule muntheng tun dohna mun chu chihna le ijakai bol ding jouse hetthem theina apeuvin ahi. Pasal'a kailhah kiti phot in Pakai thupeh bang bang'a abol diuvin aseiyin ahi.”
\v 2 Mose'n jong Bezalel le Oholiab Pakaiyin thilbol theina apieh lhon bang chun adang ho jouse jong natong dingin ama cheh in thanopna aneiyun ahi.
\v 3 Mose in jong muntheng sahdohna ding le amun theng tundohna ding chun Israel mite'n thil manchah ding adondoh chengseu chu natong ho ape tauvin ahi. Hijongleh ama hon jingkah simin Mose heng'a thil le lo ahin choijun atohdoh jing uvin ahi.
\v 4 Ajonan thilbol them ho chun muntheng munna anatoh banjom dalhan ache tauvin ahi.
\v 5 Ama hon Mose heng acheuvin hiti hin asei uve, “Mipi hon kaheng uva Pakaiyin toh ding eipeh chengse'u sang'a tamjo eipe tauvin ahi!” tin aga sei uve.
\v 6 Chuin Mose'n jong aum nau ngahmun achun thu athot tauvin ahi: “Muntheng natohna dingin pasal hihen numei hileh thil ima hin pehbeda jeng tauvin, tin thu ahil uve, ajeh chu thil ijakai aninglhing'e!” tin aseiyin ahi. Chuin mipin jong thil ijakai ahin choiyu chu anga tauvin ahi.
\v 7 Thil le lo ahin choijeh uchun ijakai adimlha jeng tan, tohgon ding kalval'in manchah aum tan ahi.
\v 8 Natong them ho chun pondal somkhat cheh amang uvin ponbuh akison tauvin ahi. Bezalel in jong ponbuh a kimang chu tupat ponnem kikhong ahin, adum le asandup le asanpol ho chu ahin, thilbol theina tah a Cherub limbang bang kisemho se chu amangchan ahi.
\v 9 Pondal khat cheh chu adung tongsomli le tongni asaovin, availam'a pang pondal ho chengse vang chu tong gup alhingin ahi.
\v 10 Hiche Pondal ho lah a nga chu khat in akigomin adang pondal nga chengse jong chutima chun akigomin ahi.
\v 11 Chule amasang lam'a pondal kigol chengse chu abil homkol tampi dum thimin asem peh in chule pondal kikhai ageigol'a chengse jong chu abil hom tampi asem'in ahi.
\v 12 Pondal masa joa abil hom somnga asem peh in, ani chana pondal chengse jong somnga ma asemin ahi. Aki kilmatna ho chu khat le khat kimai ngatto cheh ahiuve.
\v 13 Aman sana kol somnga asemin, sana kol ho chun pondal khat le khat akilmat in, chuin Houbuh chu pondal buh khat ahung sodoh tan ahi.
\v 14 Chuin aman Houbuh chungvuma khu dingin kelcha vun ho chu amang chan, pondal jong som le khat asemdoh in ahi.
\v 15 Pondal khat chu adung somli le nga cheh alhingin, chule adang pondal availama chu tonggup alhingin ahi.
\v 16 Bezalel'in jong pondal nga ho chengse chu akilmat sohkeiyin, chule amoh pondal gup chengse chu anichanna achun apansah in ahi.
\v 17 Aman pondal hoa chun abil hom somnga asempeh in, hichun pondal saotah a akilmat sah cheh cheh ahi.
\v 18 Chuin aman ponbuh khat seh a akisondoh theina ding le akilmatna dingin sum eng kol somnga asemin ahi. Hiti lamdol chun, ponbuh chu akhu khumna asempeh in ahi.
\v 20 Chule Houbuh semdohna dingin Bezalel chun thinggi thing phabep asemdoh in ahi.
\v 21 Hichu asan dan feet som le nga alhingin, avai chu inchi somni le sagi alhingin ahi.
\v 22 Thingtun khat cheh chun atun na ni aneiyin ahi. Chule atunna jouse chu abonchan asemhoi sohkeiyin ahi.
\v 23 Aman thingtun somni asemdoh in hichu lhanglam Houbuh a amangchan ahi.
\v 24 Aman jong atunna dangka in somli asem'in chule atunna khat abil'a pang ding chu abil hom jong asempeh cheh in ahi.
\v 25 Houbuh solam'a pang ding chun atun somni ma asem peh in ahi.
\v 26 Atunna dangka somli a kisem khomkhat na atunna chu ni asempeh cheh in ahi.
\v 27 Aman Houbuh nunglama pansa dingin ajol gup asem'in
\v 28 Houbuh nunglama pang ding chun atun ni ma asempeh in ahi.
\v 29 Hichea kimang atunna ho jouse chu abul lang achom cheh ahin, alulamse vang chu anunglam a chu kikaimat cheh a ahiuvin, aninggol'a pang dingin atunna teni jong chu asemin ahi.
\v 30 Akitunna dangka chutoh asemtha in ahile som le gup alhingin ahi. Ajol'a pang ding chun atunna ni cheh alhingin ahi.
\v 31 Chuin aman thinggi thing amang chan avaiya pang ding asuiyin, Houbuh solam'a pang ding chun agolvai nga asemin,
\v 32 chule lhanglam'a pansa dingin agolvai nga ma asem'in ahi. Hichengse chun lhumlam angan ahi.
\v 33 Aman alaigol lah a pansa din among lang khat a konna alang khat mong golla pang ding chun ajol khat asemkit in ahi.
\v 34 Atunna chengse chu abonchan sana in atomjol sohkeiyin, sanakol jouse jong chu agolvai ho manchah din asempeh in, agolvaiya ho jouse jong chu sana mama in atomjol sohkeiye.
\v 35 Houbuh chunglam'a pansa ding chun Bezalel in pondum, ponsandup le asan-ao tupatpon mang chan ajemin, hiche pon chu khutthemna in Cherub limin akhuijin ahi.
\v 36 Hichea pansa ding chun thingggi thing li asemdoh in chule akhom jong sana li in abolnamsel in, akol asempeh in akhom li ding ma chun sana jong lijen asem'in ahi.
\v 37 Chule aman ponbuh kot phung lam'a pansa ding chun adum, asandup, asan-ao chule tupatpon jeng'a ajemin ahi.
\v 38 Akikhaina chengse chu sana jeng'a kisem atunna nga asempeh in ahi. Akhom chengse ahin chule atomna chengse chu sana jengin atomjol sohkeiyin akhom nunglam'a pansa ding vang chun sum eng jeng mangchan asem'in ahi.
\c 37
\s1 Thingkong kisem
\p 
\v 1 Chuban'in Bezalel chun thinggi thing mangchan thingkong asem tan; adung tongni le akeh ahin, avai tongkhat le akeh chule atun tongkhat le akeh ma alhingin ahi.
\v 2 Aman jong asunglam le apolam ani gellin sana in atom jolsellin, akimvel jouse jong sana mama in atom'in ahi.
\v 3 Aman jong aning gol'a pansa ding chun sana kol-li asemin pang langkhat achun kol-ni asem'in ahi.
\v 4 Chuin aman moljol ni thinggi thing mangchan asuiyin, sana mama in atomna in ahi.
\v 5 Thingkong putna dingin moljol teni chu thingkong geiya chaokol teni achun athillut in ahi.
\v 6 Chuin aman sana thengsellin thingkong khuna asemin, chule hepi touna jong asemin adunglam chu tongni le akeh ahin, availam chu tongkhat le akeh alhingin ahi.
\v 7 Chuin aman sana a kikheng Cherub lim bang'a um ni asemdoh in hepi touna among lam'a chun hiche teni chu apansah in ahi.
\v 8 Chule aman Cherub khat aning lam khat achun apansah in among langkhat ma achun Cherub khat ma apansah in hichengse chu khat in asemdoh in ahi.
\v 9 Cherub teni chun chunglang anga lhon'in chule alha ajap lhon'in hepi touna chu alhaving tenin avengbit lhonin ahi.
\s1 Dokhang Le Meivah Khom
\p 
\v 10 Chuin Bezalel in jong thinggi thing mangchan dokhang asemin ahi. Adunglam chu tongni in asemin, avai chu tong khat ahin chule atun lam chu tong khat le akeh alhing'in ahi.
\v 11 Aman akhom ho jouse chu sana in atomjol sohkeiyin ahi.
\v 12 Akimvelse chu khutphang tebep a saovin akhuna asemin chule ageikol jouse jong sana in atomjol sohkeiyin ahi.
\v 13 Chuin aman dokhang'a manchah dingin sana chaokol li asemin, dokhang kengli lama chung apansah in ahi.
\v 14 Chaokol chengse chu abonchan kinai chan aumsah sohkeiyin, chaokolho se chu dokhang domin akimang chan ahi.
\v 15 Aman hichengse chu thinggi thing jeng mangchan asuiyin, abonchan sana in atomjol sohkeiyin ahi.
\v 16 Chule dokhang'a manchah ding chun sana kong thengsel phabep asem'in lhengkong ahin, gimnamtui halna ding chule lengpitwi chapna ding jong abonchan sana in atomjol sohkeiyin ahi.
\v 17 Chuin Bezalel in thaomei khom asem'in hichu sana thengsel a asem ahi. Thaomei khom tunna ding ahin aputna ding, ani gellin phatah in sehcha'n akheng in ahi. Hichea pahcha kijem'a pang le alutom ijakai jouse chutoh thaomei khom jaonan khat in asemdoh tan ahi.
\v 18 Thaomei khom chu gup ahin, aning ho a kon'in abah thum cheh ahin jamdoh in ahi.
\v 19 Alang alanga abah gup ajamdoh ho akon chun thaomei vah khon bangin ajamdoh in alu ajumin apah jeng jong ahung um doh in ahi.
\v 20 Hiche thaomei khom chu almond pah bangin aning li aum'in ahi.
\v 21 Thaomei khom a konna hung jam doh abah gup chengse chutoh anoilam'a chengse jaonan khat in asemdoh tan ahi.
\v 22 Almond bah hung jamdoh chengse chutoh abonchauvin khat ahung sohdoh theiyin, hichengse chu sana thengsel a kikheng jeng seh ahi.
\v 23 Aman jong thaomei sagi asemin amei khao chetan na chengse jaonan sana thengsel in asemdoh in ahi.
\v 24 Thaomei khom chu ahin, amanchah jouse jaonan sana thengsel dangka somsagi le nga mangchan asemdoh in ahi.
\s1 Maicham Gimnamtui
\p 
\v 25 Bezalel chun gimnamtuiya dingin maicham khat thinggi thingin asem'in ahi. Hichu adung tong khat chule atun tong khat ahi. Chule hichea kimangcha saki chengse chutoh khat in ahung umdoh in ahi.
\v 26 Aman maicham chu sana thengsel in atom namselin, achung vumlam ahin chule ajet le avei jenga jong, chule a saki jouse jong abonchan sana in atom namselin ahi. Hiti chun aboncha'n akimvel jouse chun sanan ajemin ahi.
\v 27 Sana kijempah noiya akol a pang dingin aman sana chaokol ni asemdoh in, khat cheh chu aki ngatto sah in akhaiyin, maicham putlena manchah dingin asemdoh in ahi.
\v 28 Aman amoljol jouse jong chu thinggi thing jengin asemin sana in atomnam sohkeiyin ahi.
\v 29 Chuin aman kinu thei dingin thaotwi asemdoh in gimnamtui jeng jong chu halnam thei dingin asemin ahi. Hichengse chu abonchan thao sem them hon asemdoh bang bangin asem tan ahi. \x + \xo 37:29 \xt Potdohbu 30:22-38\x*
\c 38
\s1 Govam Ding Maicham
\p 
\v 1 Chuban in Bezalel in jong thinggi thing amangchan, pumgo thilto maicham asemin ahi. Hichu atun feet sagi le akeh ahin asaodan jong feet sagi le akehma alhingin chule asan dan tongli le akeh alhingin ahi.
\v 2 Aman aningli chengse achun saki-li asem'in hiti chun saki chengse le maicham chu khat in aumdoh theiye. Aman maicham chu sum-eng in atomin ahi.
\v 3 Chule aman maicham'a manchah dingin sum-eng amangchan - bel, khekeh, khangbel, kong le sumkhe asemin ahi.
\v 4 Chujouvin aman sum-eng jengin lhuhkhuh asemin ahi.
\v 5 Aman hiche dopna ding chun ningli asem'in ajol toh tho a pansahna ahin, hichengse chu sum-eng jeng mangcha a alhah ahi.
\v 6 Aman thinggi mangcha'n thingjol jouse chu sum-eng jengin atom'in ahi.
\v 7 Aman maicham putna dinga akol-li asem ho chun moljol chengse athillut in ahi. Chuin maicham chu aumna ding asemtoh in ahi.
\v 8 Bezalel chun ponbuh kotphung'a lhacha a pang numei ho kisilna kong ahin chule atunna ding jong chu sum-eng jeng'a asem'in ahi. \x + \xo 38:8 \xt Potdohbu 30:18\x*
\v 9 Chuin Bezalel'in pal agenkim sohkeiyin, pal'a khai ding pon jouse chu tupat ponnem a kisem jeng ahi. Chule lhanglam'a khai ding pondal se chu feet jakhat to somnga alhing'in ahi. Hiche pal lhanglama khai ding pondal chengse jong chu tupat ponnem jenga kikhong ahin agom chun tong jakhat jen alhing e.
\v 10 Apal khom somni ahin, aboncha sum-eng jeng'a kisem ahi. Pal khom'a akol kisem chengse jong dangka jeng'a kisem ahi.
\v 11 Aman pal sahlam'a pansa dingin feet jakhat toh somnga chule akhom somni jaona hichengse chu sum-eng jeng'a asem ahi. Pal khom ahin, akhaina kol aboncha sana le dangka jeng ahi.
\v 12 Chule lhumlam'a pondal pal chengse chu feet somsagi le nga alhing'in akhom ahin, akol kisem jouse chu sana le dangka jeng ahi.
\v 13 Mailam'a pansa pondal chengse jong chu tong somsagi le nga sao ahi.
\v 14 Kelkot polam'a pondal khat chu tong somni le ni le akeh alhingin, chule atunna khom jong thum ahi.
\v 15 Chule kelkot langkhat a pansa jong chu kibangin asem'in tong somni le ni ahin, chule atunna khom jong thum ahi.
\v 16 Pal kigetna a pansa pondal jouse chu tupat ponnem jeng'a kisem ahi.
\v 17 Palkhom ahin atunna khom aboncha sum-eng jeng'a kisem ahi. Akhom'a kimang ho jouse jong chu sana le dangka jeng'a kisem ahi.
\v 18 Aman palmai kot phung'a ding chun pondal asem'in ahi. Hichu tong somthum in asaovin, asandan tong sagi le akeh ahi. Aboncha pal'a kigen chengse chutog kibang ahi.
\v 19 Akhom chengse chu li ahin, atunna jouse jong chu sum-eng jeng ahi. Chule atunna, akhaina kol jouse jong chu sana le dangka jeng ahi.
\v 20 Houbuh ahin chule akimvella pondal jouse jong sum-eng jeng ahi.
\v 21 Hichengse Houbuh ahin, chule hettohsahna Houbuh hichu Mose thupeh dungjuiya kisem, thempu Aaron chapa Ithamar ngaisahna dungjuiya Levi te natohna dinga kisem ahi.
\v 22 Chule Juda phung khaiya kon Hur chapa, Uri chapa Bezalel in jong Pakaiyin Mose athupeh bang chu abol sohkeiyin ahi.
\v 23 Amapa chu Dan phunga kon Ahisamach chapa Oholiab chule khut themna neitah le ijakai thilbol them - patdum ahin, ponsandup chule tupat ponnem bol them'a jong pang ahi.
\v 24 Houbuh le muntheng sahdohna dingin sana Shekhel somni le ko leh jasagi leh somthum ahin choi khom uve.
\v 25 Israel pumpi'n dangka talent jakhat toh Shekel sangkhat toh jasagi leh somsagi leh nga jaonan apedoh uvin muntheng sahna a kimangcha shekel dungjuiya kisim ahi. \x + \xo 38:25 \xt Potdohbu 30:11-16\x*
\v 26 Hiche dangka kidongkhom chengse hi min kisim dungjuiya hung kipelut chu ahi. (Hichu beka khat, shekel kehkhat toh kibang ahin, muntheng laiya manchah ding ahi). Pasal Kum somni apat chunglamsea konna kidong sangjagup le sangthum le janga le somnga alhing'in ahi. \x + \xo 38:26 \xt Matt 17:24\x*
\v 27 Muntheng chung khuna ding, chule atunna ho aboncha'n sana le dangka sangsagi le janga alhingin atunna khat cheh chu dangka somsagi le nga a kisem ahi.
\v 28 Amoh chengse dangka somli le nga chu akhom ahin, akhaina dinga kisem akol chengse tomnan amangin ahi.
\v 29 Chule mipi chun sum-eng a kisem dangka sangnga le jathum le somkhat ahin choijun ahi.
\v 30 Hichengse chu akhomho chule Houbuh semnan amang'in maicham achun sum-eng apansah in chule sum-eng chu thil ijakai semnan jong amang'in ahi.
\v 31 Sum-eng mangchan pal kikai jouse, kelkot chule Houbuh sung'a thil ijakai jouse semnan aneiyin ahi.
\c 39
\s1 Thempuho Von
\p 
\v 1 Muntheng'a natong ding hon amanchah diuvin asandup chule asanpol a kikhong pon akhui uvin—Aaron'in muntheng'a na atoh teng akivonna ding chu Pakaiyin Mose heng'a athupeh ahi.
\v 2 Bezalel chun sana mangcha'n konggah asem'in hichu asandup le asan-ao patnem jaonan asem'in ahi.
\v 3 Aman sana khat lim'in hoisel in khutthem tah in asem'in ahi. Hichu asandup, asan-ao patdum mangcha'n sehcha'n akheng tuoh'in asemdoh in ahi.
\v 4 Chule konggah akon chun akhaina ding anung le amalam'a aumto'n lengkou chan geijin akhailhahna aum'in among lam chu akijopmat in ahi.
\v 5 Hiche jong hi angaija bangin hoisel'in asem'in: phatah a kipheh, adum, asan-dup, asan-ao sana jeng'a kitom ponnem mangcha a kisem, hichu Pakaiyin Mose heng'a athupeh dungjuiya kisem ahi.
\v 6 Chule Onyx song chu ni amangcha uvin chuin sana alhon'in agoltoh sohkeiyun ahi. Song ho chu Israel mite ama ama insung dungjui cheh in amin'u mohor kinam khum bangin agoltoh sohkei uve.
\v 7 Aman hiche song agol chule konggah lengkou vumma kikhailha a kon chun Israel mite geldoh jing na dingin asemtoh sohkeije. Hichengse jong hi Pakaiyin Mose athupeh bangin abol sohkei uve.
\s1 Thempuho Kivonna Ompho
\p 
\v 8 Bezalel chun khutthem tah in Ompho asem'in ahi. Aman konggah bang bang chun asemdoh in hichu sana ahin, adum chule asandup ponnem jaonan asem'in ahi.
\v 9 Aman ompho chu lheptup theiyin asemdoh in akilhep teng adung avai inchi ko ahiye.
\v 10 Ama hon songmantam chu golli in agolsang uve. Amasan Carnelian song-san apansah uvin, a engthim, chule emerald song ahi.
\v 11 Golni channa dingin blue lapis lazuli, chule songgil ahi.
\v 12 Golthum channa dingin aiha song, khipi chule umbel song ahi.
\v 13 Golli channa dingin song-eng, Onyx song chule songmantam-eng apansah uve. Hichengse hi abonchan sana twiyin akaimat sohkeiyun ahi.
\v 14 Song golkhat cheh chun Israel mite ama-ama kailhah dungjuijin amin jouse toh akijih tha'n songkhat cheh a chu Mohor kisem ahiye.
\v 15 Ompho le konggah kijopmatna ding chun sana thengsel a kisem khao bangin akhuiyun ahi.
\v 16 Chule sana patjang'a kisem le sana akolni jong asem uvin sana kol teni chu ompho ning lama chun akaimat uvin ahi.
\v 17 Ompho tenia kikhai sana kol teni chu akhitmat uvin ahi.
\v 18 Chule sana patjang teni le sana gol teni chu ajopmat uvin ahi. Konggah khaina lengkou tenia kon chun agen kikhailha teni chu ompho maiya chun abehpeh peh uvin ahi.
\v 19 Chuin ama hon sana kolni asemkit uvin, ompho geilam hichu konggah toh chun akaimat uvin ahi.
\v 20 Chule sana patjang kolni asemdoh kit uvin ani tah chun lengkou vumma konggah kikhaina achun akaimat uvin ahi.
\v 21 Chuin ompho chu patjang khat mangcha'n akolsung'a chun athilmat uvin konggah a beh akol chengse toh athilmat uvin ahile phatah a kipheh bangin aumdoh tan ahi. Hitia abol phat uchun konggah le ompho chu achah kheh jeng tan ahi. Hichengse chu Pakaiyin Mose athupeh bangin abol sohkei uvin ahi.
\v 22 Bezalel chun adum'a kikhong kivonna dingin sangkhol asem'in,
\v 23 hichu Aaron'in aki-ah ding chule hiche sangkhol chol chu a-ehlouna dingin agei gol akhui cheh cheh in ahi.
\v 24 Ama hon sangkhol-chol chu kolbuthei jem'in asem uvin patdum, asan-ao chule ponnem mangcha'n asemdoh uvin ahi.
\v 25 Chuin ama hon sana thengsel'in chaojang asem uvin hichengse chu abonchan kolbuthei jem le sangkhol golla chun akoiyun ahi.
\v 26 Chaojang khat khaina achun kolbuthei jem khat in akiba cheh-cheh in ahi. Hiche sangkhol-chol thempu khat chun na atoh teng hoilai mun hijongleh Pakaiyin Mose athupeh bang'a kivon ding ahiye.
\v 27 Ama hon Aaron le achapa te ho jouse dingin sangkhol chol len tupat jengin asempeh uvin ahi.
\v 28 Delkop chule lukhuh ding jong jaonan tokachol jong pon phatah in asem uvin ahi.
\v 29 Kigah ding jouse chu ponnem asandup, asan-ao phatah a heojang'a kisem jeng, hichu Pakaiyin Mose athupeh bang'a kibol ahi.
\v 30 Achaina'n lal lukhuh sana thengsel in asem uvin ahi. Mohor kinam den bangin aum khum uvin: Pakai athenge, ti thucheng akoi un ahi.
\v 31 Ama hon lukhuh chu adum khat Aaron delkop dingin asem uvin, hichu Pakaiyin Mose athupeh bang'a abol ahi.
\s1 Houbuh Kisah Chai
\p 
\v 32 Hiti chun ajona lamin kikhop khomna Houbuh* chu sahchaiyin aumtai. Pakaiyin Mose athupeh bangin Israel mite'n jong atong chai sohkeiyun ahi.
\v 33 Chuin ama hon Mose heng'a Houbuh chule thil-le-lo ijakai abonchan ahin choijun: akhaina-kol ho, agol ho, akhomho, akhom noi nung'a ho hiti chun abonchan ahin choi sohkeiyun
\v 34 ponbuh khuna ding chun kelngoi chule kelchal vun; hichengsea chu khu ding;
\v 35 hettohsahna thingkong; thingkong putna dinga moljol teni; chule hepi touna mun;
\v 36 dokhang le thilkeo ho; chule changlhah thilto chengse jaona ahi;
\v 37 sana thengsel'a kisemdoh thaomei-khom chule thaomei-khon chengse jaona, amanchah chengse le athaotwi jaona jong ahi;
\v 38 sana a kisem maicham, chule kinu ding thaotwi; gimnamtui jaona le pondal jouse jong;
\v 39 sum-eng'a kisem maicham; chule aputna dinga sum-eng jol ho jaona; kisilna kong le atunna jouse jong;
\v 40 bangpheija kigol pondal ho; pal khom chengse ahin; chule Houbuh lutna lam; Houbuh a kimang thil le lo jouse jaona ahi;
\v 41 thempuho dinga hoitah a kikhui hichu muntheng laiya na atoh teng ule akivonna diu Aaron thempu chule achapa te hon thempu kin abol teng ule akivonna diu ahi.
\v 42 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a athupeh bang chun Israel mite'n jong abonchan ajuikim sohkeiyun ahi.
\v 43 Chuin Mose'n anatoh jouseu abonchan avelhan ahi. Ama hon toh ding ijakai Pakai thupeh bangin atongkim sohkei uve ti amuchet phat chun phatthei aboh tauvin ahi.
\c 40
\s1 Houbuh Thensona
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose heng'a aseijin,
\v 2 “Kumthah nikho masapen nia Houbuh natundoh ding ahi.”
\v 3 Chule Houbuh sung'a chu hettohsahna thingkong nakoi ding, hiche thingkong chu muntheng chungnung mun ahin, hichu pondal nakhu ding ahi.
\v 4 Dokhang hinpu'n lang, manchah thil-le-lo ho jong jaonan, chule thaomei khom ahin thaomei vah chengse jong na hinchoi ding ahi.
\v 5 Hettohsahna thingkong maija chu gimnamtui lhutna maicham nakoi ding ahi. Chuteng Houbuh kotphung'a chu nakhai ding ahi.
\v 6 Kikhop khomna ponbuh lutna maiya chu hiche pumgo thilto maicham chu nasem ding ahi.
\v 7 Kikhop khomna ponbuh le pumgo thilto maicham kimlai kom'a chu kisilna kong nakoi ding, adimset a twi nadip ding ahi.
\v 8 Chule ponbuh kimvel jousea pal kaiyin lang, kelkot lutna chu pondal nakhai cheh cheh ding ahi.
\v 9 Kinu thei thao chu choiyin lang Houbuh sung'a thil-le-lo ijakai nanu sohkei ding, aboncha atheng dinga nathenso ding ahi.
\v 10 Chule pumgo thilto maicham ahin athilkeo jouse jaona a thao nanu ding, atheng dinga thensona nanei ding ahi. Chuteng hiche maicham chu atheng chungnung'a pang ding ahi.
\v 11 Chujou teng, kisilna kong le atunna ho aboncha thao nanu ding, thensona nanei ding ahi.
\v 12 “Aaron le achapa te chengse kikhop-khomna ponbuh sung lam'a hinpuijin lang, kong'a kilui twiya chu nasil diu ahi.
\v 13 Aaron chu thao nanu ding chule ponsil thengpen a navon ding, ajeh chu keima kinbol thempu a pang diu ahi.
\v 14 Chule achapa te chengse jong hinpuijin lang abonchaova sangkhol-chol na ahpeh ding ahi.
\v 15 Apau Aaron thao nanu bang chun, amaho chengse jong thao nanu sohkei ding ahi. Ajeh chu abonchauva keima kinbol thempua pang diu ahi.”
\v 16 Pakaiyin athupeh bang chun Mose'n jong atongkim sohkei tan ahi.
\v 17 Kumkit kumthah lhamasa nikho masapen'in Houbuh chu atungdoh tan ahi.
\v 18 Mose'n hichengse jaonan Houbuh chu ana tungdoh tan ahi; akhom ho, amoljol ho, pal khom ho abonchan atongkim sohkeiyin ahi.
\v 19 Chuin aman Houbuh chung lam'a pon akhu'n Pakai thupeh bangin abol'in ahi.
\v 20 Aman hettohsahna songpheng chengse chu alan thingkong sung lam'a chun akoiyin ahi. Chuin aman thingkong chungvum'a chun moljol chu akoilut in thingkong chungvum'a chun hepi touna akoiyin ahi.
\v 21 Aman thingkong chu Houbuh lailung'a ahin pu'n pondal kikhu chu ahohdoh paijin, Pakaiyin athupeh bang chun abolin ahi.
\v 22 Chuban in Mose'n Houbuh sung lam'a chun dokhang akoiyin, polam pondal kilanna achun akoiyin ahi.
\v 23 Chule aman dokhang chung'a chun Pakai angsung'a dingin changlhah akoiyin ahi. Hichu Pakai thupeh bang'a abol ahiye.
\v 24 Aman Houbuh lhanglam dokhang chule muntheng laiya chun thaomei atung doh tan ahi.
\v 25 Chuin aman thaomei chu Pakaiyin athupeh bangin avah in.
\v 26 Aman sana gimnamtui jong chu Houbuh sunga pondal sungnung maiya Muntheng achun akoijin ahi.
\v 27 Achunga chun Pakaijin athupeh bangin gimnamtui chu ahal e.
\v 28 Aman Houbuh kotphung achun pondal akhaijin,
\s1 pondal akhaijin ahi.
\p 
\v 29 chule aman Houbuh lutna kotbul'a chun pumgo thilto maicham chu akoiyin ahi. Achung'a chun Pakaiyin athupeh bangin pumgo thilto atohdoh in ahi.
\v 30 Chubanin Mose'n Houbuh le maicham kimlaija chun kisilna-kong chu akoiyin ahi. Aman kong dimset chun twi adip tan, ajeh chu thempu kinbol'a pang hon kisilna a amanchah ding ahi.
\v 31 Mose chule Aaron le achapa te'n kong sung'a twi chu kisilna a amanchah diu ahi.
\v 32 Houbuh maicham lam ahin jotlut teng ule, kisil ngimna a aman jing ding'u ahi. Ajeh chu Pakaiyin Mose heng'a athupeh ahi.
\v 33 Chuin aman Houbuh le maicham kimvel chengsea chun pondal akhaiyin ahi. Chule kelkot lam'a jong pondal akhaijin ahi. Ajonan Mose'n natoh ijakai atongkim sohkeijin ahi.
\s1 Pakai Loupina
\p 
\v 34 Chuin meibol'in ponbuh chu ahin khu jeng tan ahile, Pakai loupina chu kikhop khomna ponbuh adimlha jeng tai. \x + \xo 40:34 \xt 1 Lgt 8:10,11; Isa 6:4; Ezekiel 43:4,5; Rev 15:8\x*
\v 35 Mose chu Houbuh sung lam'a chun alut thei tapon akiting den tai, ajeh chu meibol lom chu kiheh jeng ahitan, chule Pakai loupi na chun Houbuh chu atomlhah jeng ahitai.
\v 36 Tun meibol jong chu Houbuh akon'in ahung kitol tan ahile, Israel mite jeng jong meibol che dungjuijin akitolthaji tauvin ahi.
\v 37 Amavang meibol aum den laisen, amaho jong aumden jitauve.
\v 38 Pakaiya konna meibol chun nilhum keijin Houbuh chu atomlha jeng tan, janteng mei-kong in akilah jin ahile Israel mite'n amittah uvin amuthei jun ahi. Hiche hin akholjinna chan uva ahin juipeh ahi. 
